\id ACT ACT- KAPIN 
\h Sinale 
\toc2 Sinale 
\toc1 Qapiya wei Sinale yo 
\mt2 Qapiya wei 
\mt1 Xuk wei Sinaleyeiw 
\mt2 o 
\imt1 Qayeeng wei la tax o 
\ip Qapiya tiwei Xuk wei xel Sinale eno byex wou qayeeng wei Xoulek Nimza wei Lukas byex o. Lukas venaxow byex qapiya tine is. Eivek qapiya tine eno xey a xei Laweeng Vambuing talex sakwaing wou xel sinale me xel neil Yesu xe Xoulek Nimza nanghei "Yerusalem me Yudia me Samaria me e la teyei lek tembuing sapa" (wei 1.8). 
\ip Qapiya wei Sinale eno tul pavulek en xel (sios) wei Yesu eno qandi senghoing eivek xel Yuda, dekakom la wo ngandoung me la eivek tembuing danghei danghei nei is. Lukas embei talex is ambei nyon, xuk wei Yesu me mapieing wei xomaxoneing wei mi betiwou e yo eno la teyei lek qayeeng zonghek wei Anutu neil wou Israelyeiw takwei yo. 
\ip Lul ngandoung ti qapiya wei Sinale eno neil, inye xuk wei Laweeng Vambuing o, inyon Anutu xe Laweeng Vambuing on. Myaxeeng eno Laweeng Vambuing lam wou Yesu xe xel betiyeing lek bouk wei Pentikos o. Dekakom Laweeng Vambuing pepyawexe woueing nalei wei xel o me wong nikanzek wou xel. 
\ip Eivek qapiya tine eno xey a xei qayeeng ding a ding ngenong wei xel sinale neil gyeik ingwei xel embei neil wou xel amba en Xoulek Nimza wei Yesu xe yo. De xey a xei bei xomaxoneing ngenong betiwou Xoulek Nimza ne me xel wei Yesu eno (sios) nale nikanzek. 
\ip Qapiya wei Sinale eno pavulek wei sinaleyeiw ngenong eno di yeip eivek, ekom qayeeng ngenong di yeip eivek en lulul wei Petele me Paulus wong o. Petele yon xel betiyeing ti wei mi la is Yesu yo. Ekom myaxeeng eno Paulus se mi betiwou Yesu. Ma. Moxo mi wo xuk nikanzek me wo nol wou xel wei Yesu yo (sios). Ekom Yesu taxe Paulus me wong e wong ambei xukxe tiwei myaxeeng wei emi bong e xe xuk o. 
\ip Eivek qapiya danghei valu eno Lukas embei tul pavulek en lul wei qandi wou Paulus o, moxo neil lulul wei ''xa'' mi wong o. Xel wei lupeyei eno ngenong wou naleind bei Lukas mi ghavineeng bouk valu is Paulus, om neil embei "xa" eivek danghei tine. 
\c 1  
\s1 Yesu lek me la eivek tyoung gheyapu 
\p  
\v 1 Tiopilas, 
\p Eivek a xe qapiya nge tax, a byex myaxeeng en lulul dalus wei Yesu wong a tax me teyoxe xel o  
\v 2 me elam tyip bouk wei Anutu qou e lek la tyoung gheyapu nei, me eivek Laweeng Vambuing eno neil wou sinaleyeiw wei e beyal en xuk leimalei wei xel a mi bong o.  
\v 3 Ka e qou nimaying woy eno moxo talex xow yeip yaing wou moux ti beimambei ne bei toundei mapieing. Moxo belup wou xel lumama teyei lek bouk mepyeiyuw (40) me luk wou xel en tete lalei wei Anutu xe yo.  
\v 4 Ka e nanghei toundei is xel, me ya is xel eno moxo peti xel, “Xam sim ghe na veil Yerusalem, qe xam a mi mendei inye me daxe lul xeilala wei Mang neil zonghek bei bong o. Wei xam ghe ngo ingwei a luk en o.  
\v 5 Yoan lipek moux alis vex en memiing, ekom bouk di lam paviy en ingwei tyek xam ghe zipek en Laweeng Vambuing o.” 
\p  
\v 6 Om gyeik xel sinale me Yesu qekuma, xel teling wou e, “Tambiy Ngandoung, gweimbeeng lek bouk tine eno tyek wang nox me na piyexe tete lalei wei Israel o no?” 
\p  
\v 7 Moxo neil wou xel: “Inye se yeip wou xam bei xam ghe boulek seivma o bouk wei Mang venaxow lax angya emaxow nikanzek o.  
\v 8 Ekom tyek xam a qou nimkanzek gyeik Laweeng Vambuing nam lek xam o, me vati wei xam ghe wei mamim wou woy eno tyek xam a neil a teyei eivek Yerusalem, me ena eivek Yudia dalus me distrik Samaria, me ena tyip wou tembuing myasepu nei.” 
\p  
\v 9 Ka Yesu neil qayeeng tine woy, Anutu qou e lek la gheyapu wou xel mendghalus de laxap sevun e om xel se yei e no. 
\p  
\v 10 Xel anghei di yei ingwei e la punei eivek tyoung gyeik e di la yo, lutika eno tambiy yuw byex teimb teleing me nale lip wou xel.  
\v 11 Luw neil wou xel, “Xam moux wei Galili yon, xam ghe toungale inye me ghe di domamim la wou tyoung en va? Yesu tiwei, Anutu qou veil xam me la eivek tyoung gheyapu nei, eno tyek noum me nam eivek sakwaing ambei kawei xam ghe wei e la eivek tyoung o.” 
\s1 Xel beyal Matias bei e qou Yudas nimbeeng 
\p  
\v 12 Woyom xel betiyeing la veil lukendu wei xel mi taxe bei Oliv, me lox me la Yerusalem wei toundei paviy lukendu Oliv o, teyei lek ambei kilomita ti.  
\v 13 Gyeik xel la tyip, xel la gheyapu eivek xomek lalei wei xel embei mi mendei eivek o. Eti yeiw wei lam eno leind ambei nye, Petele, Yoan, Jems, me Andrias, Pilip me Tomas, Batolomiu me Matai, Alpias neu moux Jems me Simon wei Selot me Yudas on Jems neu moux.  
\v 14 Xel xouing dalus mi qekuma me toung laleind lekti de mi zeimemend taxombouk, xel vex lam is me Maria wei Yesu ta, me liyeiw moux is. 
\p  
\v 15 Eivek bouk tiyon Petele nale eivek xel wongeingis on senghoing (xel on teyei lek 120)  
\v 16 me neil, “Xam lingyeiw, xoulek wei yeip eivek qapiya ne eno embei bong neing lek ambei ingwei Laweeng Vambuing luk takwei nei eivek Dawit mya en Yudas tiwei talex sakwaing wou xel wei embei zeimaxoun Yesu yo.  
\v 17 Yudas on tambiy wei xey yo ti, me mi wo xuk is xey.” 
\p  
\v 18 (Yudas qou malew en sewokeing wei talex Yesu teyei yo, me moxo la xouv tembuing ti en inyon woy. Woyom moxo teibouyek lek tembuing me leis bambou tek de xeixay qapyex lam myayaing.  
\v 19 Xel dalus eivek Yerusalem eno ngo tine, om xel taxe tembuing tiyon lei eivek vyend bei Akeldama qes ambei nye bei Tembuing wei Gyand o.) 
\p  
\v 20 Petele neil, “En inye xel byex eivek qapiya lalo bei, 
\q1 “‘Teyeimbei e beeng on mendei bandaing en xomaxoneing ti se mendei lek inyon,’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 69:25\rq* 
\m me, 
\q1 “‘teyeimbei tambiy nge e qou e nimbeeng en xuk wei la tax en xel o.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 109:8\rq* 
\m  
\v 21 Om inyon nimza bei xey a beyal moux wei mi la me loum is xey bouk sapa gyeik Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu mi dei is xey yo,  
\v 22 lek bouk sapa wei Yoan lipek xel me elam tyip gyeik Yesu lek la gheyapu veil xey o. Om xey a beyal tambiy wei yeimawou woy eno nge en e neil Yesu xe qandieing lek teyei.” 
\p  
\v 23 Om xel beyal moux yayuw: Yosep wei xel mi taxe bei Balsabas (lei nye bei Jastus) me Matias.  
\v 24 Woyom xel zeimemend, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wang woulek xomaxoneing titi laleind. Talex wou xa bei luyuw ne nge na wang beyal,  
\v 25 bei e gyeiteyei xuk sinale, wei Yudas ghanaw me la wou e maxow xe sakwaing o.”  
\v 26 Woyom xel nex qakous dee, om qakous teila wou Matias, om moxo la is sinaleyeiw xoumeeng ti yon. 
\c 2  
\s1 Bouk Pentikos wei Laweeng Vambuing lam o 
\p  
\v 1 Gyeik bouk wei Pentikos eno lam, om xel wongeingis dalus qekuma eivek xomek ti.  
\v 2 Se denlek en nindenduing nambei laweeng nikanzek ti lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei me pup eivek xomek lalei wei xel toundei eivek on.  
\v 3 Xel yei lulti nambei nenyex, xok ambei ghas eno dembuma me la dei lek xel on titi.  
\v 4 Laweeng Vambuing lam pupexe xomaxoneing on lek om xel luk vyend leimalei nambei ingwei Laweeng Vambuing wong wou xel o. 
\p  
\v 5 Gweimbeeng inyon xel wei toundei eivek Yerusalem on Anutu xe xel Yudayeiw wei mi yaleeng en Anutu xe petieing me betiwou e yo, eno lam anghei beyeeng tambak wei mindei xeinghembi en tyoung gheyapu.  
\v 6 Gyeik xel ngo nindenduing tine, moux alis vex ngenong on lam qekuma is etekeing, en nambei xel titi yon ngo xel di luk eivek xel venaxow titi vyend.  
\v 7 Xel etek niseikeing, om xel teling: “Beip xel moux alis vex dalus tine eno se Galiliyeiw?  
\v 8 Woyom nambei nya ekom xey titi ngo qayeeng eivek xe venaxow vyend?  
\v 9 Xey wei Patia me Midia me Elam me Mesopotamia me Yudia me Kapadosia me Pontus me Esia,  
\v 10 me Prigia me Pampilia me Izip me ela valu wei Libia paviy Sairini, me xe valu lam anghei Rom me na lam a toundei inye.  
\v 11 (Xel on valu Yudayeiw me xel ba wei mi betiwou petieing wei Mose yo). Me xel valu wei Krit me Arebia, eno xey a ngo xel di neil xuk nimza maseim wei Anutu xe yo teyei eivek xemaxow vyend.”  
\v 12 Xel etek me wou naleind ngenong, de teling wouma, “Tine qes nambei nya?” 
\p  
\v 13 Xel valu eno luk seloukeing en xel me neil, “Xel num wain ngenong o.” 
\s1 Petele neil qayeeng wou xel qendu ngandoung on 
\p  
\v 14 Woyom Petele nale is sinaleyeiw xoumeeng ti yon, de luk me vya lekla dom neil qayeeng wou xel qendu ngandoung on bei, “Xam Yudayeiw me xam dalus wei ghe mindei eivek Yerusalem o, xam wong a neil qayeeng tine wou xam, xam a ngo embo nimza en vati wei ambei neil ne yo.  
\v 15 Moux ti beimambei ne eno se num me wo nol, nambei ingwei xam ghe di wou naleimim en o. Inye nanghei seivma limvey wei satiboukeing o!  
\v 16 Ma, inye vati wei poropet Yoel neil o: 
\q1  
\v 17 “‘Anutu neil, “Eivek bouk loxyus, 
\q2 tyek a qapyex a xe Laweeng Vambuing lek xomaxoneing dalus. 
\q1 Xam neumim moux me xam neumim vex tyek baluk ambei poropet, de 
\q2 xam neumyeiw ghavis tyek mendghalus pekwi me gyei lul leimalei, 
\q2 de teivateiv wei xam o tyek gyei maviing. 
\q1  
\v 18 Eivek bouk tiyon eno tyek a qapyex a xe Laweeng Vambuing lek a xe xukxe moux alis vex dalus, 
\q2 me tyek xel a neil qayeeng ambei poropet. 
\q1  
\v 19 De tyek a talex lul nelu nelu eivek tyoung gheyapu nei, 
\q2 me dee wei lulvako eno lek tembuing axone, 
\q2 gyand me nenyex me nenyex lu ngandoung tyek na tyip. 
\q1  
\v 20 Sayeiv tyek pekwi me bo mapetok 
\q2 de dentouk tyek bong ambei gyand 
\q2 natax en bouk ngandoung wei Tambiy Ngandoung nam is xeiyaing ngandoung me nikanzek wei e yo. 
\q1  
\v 21 Me xel dalus tiwei tyek taxe 
\q2 Tambiy Ngandoung lei yo eno tyek Anutu devind xel noum veil meyeing.”’ \rq Yoel 2:28-32\rq* 
\p  
\v 22 “Xam xomaxoneing wei Israel o li nenyamim wou qayeeng tine, Yesu wei Nasaret on, Tambiy wei Anutu talex wou xam bei wong Yesu lak wou xam is lul nikanzek is dee wei lulvako yo wei xam ghe boulek bei Anutu wong e lam eivek xam senghoing eivek e maxow mema nambei ingwei xam ghe woulek o.  
\v 23 Yesu ne Anutu wou eivek xam memamim betiwou qes me ingwei wounalei en o pyap woy, eivek xel amba wei se mi betiwou qayeeng petieing o memend ekom xam ghe tuw e lek xax pepeeng me ghe leis e mey.  
\v 24 Ekom Anutu piyexe e qandi lek veil myavanei me tul e veil meyeing, en meyeing se teyeimbei zeimaxoun e.  
\v 25 De Dawit neil ambei nye lek e, 
\q1 “‘A xei Tambiy Ngandoung mindei paviy ay taxombouk, en moxo toundei wou a memang payeiv 
\q2 om tyek a se detek. 
\q1  
\v 26 Nambei nyon a laleing mi wo nimza me a myang mi sanghoxe, 
\q2 me tyek a neing a mi mendei me na toung mang en inyon. 
\q1  
\v 27 En tyek wa seng bong a nung na toumendei eivek beyeeng wei meyeing o, 
\q2 o tyek wa xe Tambiy Tiwei Vambuing eno se daxe pataleing. 
\q1  
\v 28 Wang talex sakwaing wei a mi mendei mapieing eno wou ay 
\q2 me tyek wang bong xeilala e pup ay, wou wa mamghalus.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 16:8-11\rq* 
\p  
\v 29 “Xam lingyeiw, a neil neing wou xam en xe bund Dawit bei moxo mey me e xe eeng toundei inye is xey me elam tyip gweimbeeng ne.  
\v 30 Woyom tambiy on poropet ti om woulek ingwei Anutu neil neing is inya punei bei tyek bong e buyeiw ti mendei lek siaking wei e xe yo.  
\v 31 Dawit yei tax me neil en qandieing wei Kilisi yo, de Anutu nalei se ma e me wong e toundei eivek leiveeng wei meyeing o, me tyek xel se gyei e neing on patal.  
\v 32 Yesu tine Anutu piyexe e qandi lek me xa dalus a xei lek mami.  
\v 33 De woyom Yesu lek me la gheyapu woy me la dei wou Anutu mema payeiv me qou Laweeng Vambuing wou Ma, nambei ingwei neil zonghek o. Moxo qapyex tine lam me xam ghe di wei me ghe ngo yo.  
\v 34 En Dawit se lek me la eivek tyoung gheyapu, qe emaxow neil embei, 
\q1 “ ‘Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou a xe Tambiy Ngandoung, 
\q2 “Lam dei wou a memang payeiv. 
\q1  
\v 35 Deka a toung xel wei mi wo vevek wou wang eno na kwanghembi eivek wa vaxam 
\q2 bole.” ’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 110:1\rq* 
\p  
\v 36 “Nambei nyon xam xomexomek dalus wei Israel o ghe bongis bei Anutu wong Yesu tiwei xam ghe tuw lek xax pepeeng eno wo Tambiy Ngandoung me Kilisi.” 
\p  
\v 37 Gyeik xel xomaxoneing ngo tine, xel laleind wo nimaying me neil wou Petele me sinaleyeiw bei, “Xam lingyeiw, tyek xa bong vati?” 
\p  
\v 38 Petele neil elox bei, “Xam dalus on titi pekwi xow me xel zipek xam en Yesu Kilisi lei, en tyek semaleeng xam xe nilul sapa veil, dom tyek Anutu bong Laweeng Vambuing wou xam nambei byeind wei xam o.  
\v 39 Qayeeng wei neil zonghek ne eno inye wou xam me xam neumyeiw me inye wou xel dalus wei mindei dingta yo, me inye wou xel dalus wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe xe Anutu taxe yo.” 
\p  
\v 40 Petele peti xel en qayeeng ngenong. Me byexaxoun xel, “Xam a mi devind ama veil xel nilul wei bouk ti gweimbeeng ne.”  
\v 41 Om xel wei mi lewexe lek e xe qayeeng me lipek eno teyei lek 3,000 eno tendulek xel lek bouk tiyon. 
\s1 Lalei tixemou wei xomaxoneing o 
\p  
\v 42 Xel moux alis vex wo ninkanzek bei ngo sinaleyeiw xe teyoxeing me toung laleind lekti me wounaleind en Yesu eivek ingwei xel dembu belet o me zeimemend.  
\v 43 Me sinaleyeiw wong lul nelu nelu ngenong me dee wei lulvako yo ngenong om xel dalus on etek.  
\v 44 Xel dalus wei mi wongis Yesu eno mi dei is ama me wong lulul dalusateiv on is laleind tixemou.  
\v 45 Xel mi wo vateivek lek tembuing me lulul wei xel xe yo, de mi wong wou xel wei lulul maeing o.  
\v 46 Bouk tambak eno xel mi qekuma eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing wei qekueing ama yo. Xel mi dembu belet eivek xel xe xomek me ya lekti is laleind nimza me laleind vevopeing.  
\v 47 Xel mi sanghoxe Anutu me mi wo xeindlala en xomaxoneing sapa laleind mi wo nimza wou xel. Me bouk titi eno Tambiy Ngandoung qou xomaxoneing valu is no, me xel wongis e me tendulek xel bamba me xel wo ngenong. 
\c 3  
\s1 Petele luw Yoan wong tambiy tiwei vaxa nol eno wo nimzalek 
\p  
\v 1 Bouk ti Petele luw Yoan la xomek vambuing, lek seivma wei zeimeing mema yo, lek soukeing wei seivma yal o.  
\v 2 Nanghei nyon eno moux wei vaxa wo nol eivek ta veis eno xel qalei e me la toung paviy xomek vambuing on mya wei xel mi taxe bei Nimza yo, xel toung e nanghei inyon me e mi teling xomaxoneing wei mi eivek la tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o en malew.  
\v 3 Tambiy on yei Petele luw Yoan embim na eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o, om moxo teling luw bei luw bo malew ti wou e.  
\v 4 Ekom Petele luw Yoan domend wou e me neil, “Wei uw!”  
\v 5 Om moxo yei luw, de e beiknge tyek na qou malew valu wou luw.  
\v 6 Woyom Petele neil wou e, “A selewa o ghol wei ambei bong wou wang eno ma, ekom vati wei a xe eno tyek a bong wou wang. Lek Yesu Kilisi wei Nasaret o lei, a neil wou wang, qandi lek me la.”  
\v 7 Om Petele zeim lek e mema payeiv me vind moxo nale gheyapu, lutika eno e vaxa qatu me vaxalambes wo nimzalek.  
\v 8 Moxo vyeip me nale me ghavineeng eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing is luw, la ghavineeng me wo vyeip vyeip me sanghoxe Anutu lei.  
\v 9 Xel xomaxoneing dalus yei ingwei moxo di ghavineeng me sanghoxe Anutu lei yo.  
\v 10 Xel woulek bei inyon tambiy kawei mindei wou xomek vambuing mya wei xel mi taxe bei Nimza yo, me mi teling lulul wou xel, om xomaxoneing dalus on etek niseikeing en ingwei moxo wo nimzalek o. 
\s1 Petele neil qayeeng eivek xomek vambuing 
\p  
\v 11 Moxo zeimaxoun Petele luw Yoan omva, xomaxoneing sapa nun la me etek dom tup me la wou lal lek xomek palanda wei xel mi taxe bei palanda wei Salomo yo.  
\v 12 Ekom Petele yei ingwei xel qeku lam o, om neil wou xel bei, “Xam lingyeiw Israel, xam ghe etek enva? Me xam ghe domamim wou uw enva? Beip uw a wong tambiy ne wo nimzalek angya nikanzek wei uw maxow o, o nangya ingwei uw a mindei nimza wou Anutu manghalus o?  
\v 13 Anutu wei Apraham me Isaka me Yakop o, inye Anutu wei xe mendyeiw me bundyeiw eno wong e xe xukxe Yesu lei wo ngandoung, inyon tambiy tiwei xam ghe pesek me ghe toung e eivek Pailat mema bei xel nyeis e mey, gyeik Pailat embei bong ena bandaing o.  
\v 14 Ekom xam ghe pesek xomaxoneing wei Vambuing me Bombek ayang o, dom ghe teling Pailat en tambiy wei mi leis xel mey o bei embong e noum wou xam.  
\v 15 Dom xam ghe leis tambiy wei mapieing lukes, ekom Anutu piyexe e qandi lek veil meyeing. De xa maxow a xei tine lek mami.  
\v 16 Moux tine tiwei xam ghe wei me ghe woulek eno wo nimzalek nangya e xe wongeingis lek Yesu lei. Om tambiy tiyon wongis Yesu lei me wong e wo nimzalek, nambei xam dalus ghe wei yon. 
\p  
\v 17 “Gweimbeeng, xam lingyeiw, a woulek inyon bei xam seng woulek om xam ghe wong tiyon, nambei kwa wei xam xe xel gyovaxa yo.  
\v 18 Ekom lulti beimambei yon, Anutu neil atax eivek xel poropet dalus myend, bei e xe Kilisi, tyek na qou myavanei, om wo neing lek eivek sakwaing wei xam ghe wong on.  
\v 19 Woyom xam pekwi xow, de pekwi me ghe nox wou Anutu, en kandek Anutu e semaleeng xam xe sewokeing veil, dom Tambiy Ngandoung tyek bong nikanzek vako wou xam,  
\v 20 me inyon tyek Anutu bong Kilisi, tiwei e beyal wou xam o nam, inyon Yesu.  
\v 21 Moxo mindei eivek tyoung gheyapu deka bouk wei Anutu embei bong lul dalus bo vako eno nam le, nambei e neil zonghek eivek mya; is e xe xel poropet vambuing atax o.  
\v 22 En Mose neil, ‘Xam xe Tambiy Ngandoung Anutu tyek beyal xam xe poropet ti nambei ay, eivek xam venaxow limyeiw senghoing, xam a ngo lul tambak wei embei neil wou xam o.  
\v 23 Xelti embei se ngo e, eno tyek semaleeng e veil e xe xel xomaxoneing.’ \rq Petieing 18:19\rq* 
\p  
\v 24 “Nambei nyon, xel poropet dalus eivek bouk wei Samuel me e lam eno xel ngenongakes luk, me eti yeiw wei lam yus eno luk me neil qayeeng en bouk wei di lam gweimbeeng ne yo.  
\v 25 Me xam on poropet neuyeiw, me xam on ingwei Anutu qokatu is xam bumimyeiw o. E neil wou Apraham, ‘Eivek wa neumambum xomaxoneing lek tembuing sapa tyek na qou mata.’  
\v 26 Woyom Anutu piyexe e xe xukxe qandi lek, de wong moxo lak atax wou xam, bei bong mata wou xam me pekwi xam titi veil xam xe sakwaing wei nilul o.” 
\c 4  
\s1 Petele luw Yoan nale wou xel kanzol mendghalus 
\p  
\v 1 Luw di neil xoulek wou xomaxoneing bembeeng on, de lumukiyeiw is beyeiv wei mi yeiteyei xomek vambuing o, me xel Sadyusi xel xouing lam wou Petele luw Yoan gyeik luw di neil qayeeng wou xel xomaxoneing on.  
\v 2 Xel laleind wo vanei ngandoung wou luw en xel woulek bei luw di teyoxe xomaxoneing sapa yon en ingwei Yesu qandi lek veil meyeing o.  
\v 3 Xel zeimaxoun Petele luw Yoan bei na toung luw na eivek xeitueing deka yanyeing le, en inye souk.  
\v 4 Ekom xel ngenong wei ngo xoulek eno wongis. Me xel moux nyouk teyei lek ambei 5,000. 
\p  
\v 5 De yanyeing eno xel leitata me teivateiv me xel putoung wei petieing o qekuma nanghei Yerusalem.  
\v 6 Anas lumuki lukanzek toundei inyon is Kaiapas, me Yoan, me Aleksanda me xel moux valu wei lumuki lukanzek nipapu eno is.  
\v 7 Om xel qou Petele luw Yoan me lam lax luw wou xel mendghalus dom teling wou luw bei, “Eivek nikanzek vati, me eivek eti lei eno muw ghe wong lulti beimambei yon nangya?” 
\p  
\v 8 Woyom Laweeng Vambuing pupexe Petele, om neil wou xel, “Xam leitata me teivateiv wei xel xomaxoneing o,  
\v 9 beip xam ambei teling uw en tambiy tiwei uw a wong e vaxa wo nimzalek o, me xam ambei teling bei, e vaxa wo nimza lek ambei nya.  
\v 10 Woyom xam ghe bouk lek qayeeng tine, xam me xomaxoneing sapa wei Israel o dalus ghe boulek bei, eivek Yesu Kilisi wei Nasaret o lei, tambiy tiwei vaxa wo nol ne eno wo nimza lek me nale wou xam mamim. Xam ghe tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng. Ekom Anutu piyexe e qandi lek veil meyeing.  
\v 11 Yesu yon 
\q1 “‘qakous tiwei xam kamunda ghe pesek, 
\q2 eno wong ambei qakous lukanzek wei mi byexaxoun xomek o.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 118:22\rq* 
\m  
\v 12 Tambiy ti se teyeimbei devind xey veil meyeing qe Yesu venaxow, en, eivek tyoung gheyapu xeinghembi eno Anutu se neil lei bange wei xelti yo teyei bei devind xey a noum veil meyeing.” 
\p  
\v 13 Xel teivateiv on yei Petele luw Yoan luk is nikanzek de se yaleeng, om xel woulek inyon bei luw xouing se wevek xomek qapiya, luw on moux bandaing, xel etek me wou kwend bei yuw on mi la is Yesu.  
\v 14 De xel yei tambiy tiwei luw wong e wo nimzalek o toungale inyon is luw, om xel se teyeimbei neil qayeeng ti nox wou luw.  
\v 15 Om xel neil wou luw bei luw na veil xomek kanzol, luw la veil de woyom xel luk wouma.  
\v 16 Xel teling, “Tyek xey a bong vati wou moux yuw ne? En xel sapa wei toundei eivek Yerusalem ne eno woulek bei luw wong xuk dee ne inye nimza, om xe se teyeimbei daxvun.  
\v 17 Ekom tyek xey a peti luw en luw se neil qayeeng tine na bo sapa wou xomaxoneing en lei tine no.” 
\p  
\v 18 Woyom xel lox me la taxe luw me luk nikanzek wou luw bei luw se baluk o teyoxe xomaxoneing en Yesu lei no.  
\v 19 Ekom Petele luw Yoan neil elox bei, “Xam teling ama, beip inye nimza wou Anutu manghalus bei xa betiwou xam de se Anutu?  
\v 20 Ekom uw se teyeimbei tip lukeing en lul sapa wei uw a xei me na ngo woy yo.” 
\p  
\v 21 Xel kanzol on neil qayeeng nikanzek valu no wou luw dom wong luw la, de xel se wo nimaying ti wou luw, en nambei xomaxoneing sapa yon di sanghoxe Anutu lei en vati wei belup on.  
\v 22 En tambiy tiwei luw wong e wo nimzalek eno xe vakovek qes ghanaw xoumeeng vey (40). 
\s1 Xel wongeingis xe zeimeing mema 
\p  
\v 23 Xel kanzol tul Petele luw Yoan woy, woyom luw lox wou luw maxow xe xomaxoneing, me neil qayeeng dalus wei xel lumuki leitata me teivateiv neil wou luw o.  
\v 24 Xel ngo qayeeng tine woy, xel xouing toung laleind lekti eivek zeimeing mema wou Anutu. Xel neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung nikanzekta, wang toung tyoung me tembuing me mamileeng, me lulul sapa wei toundei eivek o.  
\v 25 Myaxeeng eno wang luk eivek xa mami Dawit, wa xe xukxe mya nangya Laweeng Vambuing bei: 
\q1 “ ‘Nambei nya xomaxoneing sapa laleind wo myavanei, 
\q2 xomaxoneing beimambei ne tup qayeeng bandaing bei bong kwa nilul enva? 
\q1  
\v 26 Xel king wei tembuing eno yeiwou xow en embei bo vevek. 
\q2 Me xel gyovaxa qekuma en xel embei bo vevek wou Tambiy Ngandoung 
\q3 me embei bo vevek wou Kilisi is.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 2:1-2\rq* 
\m  
\v 27 Xa woulek bei vati wei wang neil atax takwei eno wo neing lek zonghek. En Herot aluw Pontias Pailat qeku is xel ba me xel wei Israel, eivek beyeeng ngandoung bei bong nimaying wou Yesu, wa xe xukxe vambuing tiwei wang beyal o.  
\v 28 Gyeik xel wong lul tine, xel betiwou kwa me wamaxow laleim en nikanzek wei wang o. Takwei eno wang tup qayeeng atax bei lulti beimambei ne eno neing a tyip.  
\v 29 Gweimbeeng, Tambiy Ngandoung wa bounaleim en xel xe qayeeng wei xel neil me wo yalenyeing wou xa yo, de wa devind xa wei wa xe xukxe yo, bei xa neil wa xe xoulek is nikanzek dom xa se ghaleeng.  
\v 30 De wa ni memam na lek xel wei vanei yo en xel bo nimzalek me wang bong dee wei lulvako yo eivek wa xe xukxe vambuing Yesu lei.” 
\p  
\v 31 Ka xel zeimemend woy, beyeeng kawei xel di qekuma lek on wo pimapi. Me xel dalus pup en Laweeng Vambuing me neil Anutu xe xoulek nikanzek, dom xel se yaleeng. 
\s1 Xel wongeingis vind ama en lulul 
\p  
\v 32 Xel wongeingis laleind me lundpeyei eno la tixemou, xelti se neil embei lulti yon inyon emaxow xe, qe xel vind ama en lulul dalus wei xel xe yo.  
\v 33 Sinaleyeiw di tetulexe qayeeng neileing en ingwei Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu qandi lek o is nikanzek ngandoung me Anutu xe lalei xeiles wei ghanaw veil eno toundei is xel.  
\v 34 Inyon xel wei kanyo eno ti se toundei eivek xel senghoing, en eivek bouk titi xel eti yeiw wei xe tembuing, o xomek eno wo vateivek lek, me qou malew lek,  
\v 35 de toung ela wou sinaleyeiw vaxend, me xel pum malew on wou xel wei lulul maeing o.  
\v 36 Yosep, wei Livai nanghei Saiprus, xel sinale mi taxe e lei nge bei Banabas (qes ambei nye bei tambiy wei mi vind xomaxoneing en qayeeng nimza yo)  
\v 37 eno wong vateivek lek e xe tembuing de qou malew me toung ela wou sinaleyeiw. 
\c 5  
\s1 Ananias aluw Sapira 
\p  
\v 1 Tambiy ti lei Ananias, de venei lei Sapira, luw wong vateivek lek tembuing wei luw eno danghei ti me tambiy nge xouv,  
\v 2 De venei woulek is ambei nyon om luw toung malew veweeng wou lumaxow, dom veweeng dalus eno luw qou me la toung wou xel sinale. 
\p  
\v 3 Woyom Petele neil, “Ananias, nambei nya ekom wang wong Sandang pup wa laleim lek, me wang tyoxe Laweeng Vambuing, de ghe toung malew valu wou xow wei wang qou lek tembuing o?  
\v 4 Myaxeeng wei wa seng ghei wo vateivek lek tembuing on, eno inyon wa xe zonghek. Deka wang wo vateivek lek, eno malew on inye wa xe. Om wang wou eivek naleim en kwa nilul on enva? Wa seng tyoxe xomaxoneing venaxow qe wang tyoxe Anutu is.” 
\p  
\v 5 Ananias ngo qayeeng tine eno moxo teibouyek lek tembuing de mey. Me xel dalus wei ngo qayeeng ne eno yaleeng ngandoung mouyo.  
\v 6 Woyom xel moux wei ghavis eno lam me beliv e neing eivek qaeing, de xel qalei e neing on me la ev. 
\p  
\v 7 Seivma yal lak veil, Ananias venei lam lalei, ekom vexo se woulek vati wei belup wou leya yo.  
\v 8 Om Petele teling wou e, “Neil wou ay bei malew wei muw ghe qou lek tembuing eno dalus inye?” 
\p Vexo neil, “Ee, malew dalus inyon.”  
\v 9 Petele neil wou vexo, “Nambei nya muw leyam ghe tyoxe Tambiy Ngandoung xe Laweeng? Wei! Xel moux wei qalei leyam me la ev eno vaxend toungale wou xomek mya yon, om tyek xel qalei wang me na myayaing is ambei nyon.”  
\v 10 Lutika eno vexo teibouyek lek tembuing wou Petele vaxa dom mey. Woyom xel ghavis lam lalei me yei bei vexo mey, om xel qalei e me la myayaing me la ev e paviy leya.  
\v 11 Om xel wongeingis dalus me xel amba dalus wei ngo qayeeng en vati wei belup on eno xel yaleeng ngandoung. 
\s1 Sinaleyeiw wong xel ngenong wo nimza lek 
\p  
\v 12 Sinaleyeiw wong lulvako me dee ngenong eivek xel xomaxoneing senghoing. Me xel wongeingis dalus mi toung laleind lekti me qekuma eivek xomek palanda wei xel mi taxe bei palanda wei Salomo mi dei lek o.  
\v 13 Xel bamba wei se ghei wongis Yesu eno yaleeng bei se na mindei is xel wei wongis o. Ekom xel ngenong mi sanghoxe xel wei wongis o nambei xel on nimza.  
\v 14 Dekalekom moux alis vex ngenong wongis Tambiy Ngandoung me lam tendulek xel wei wongis o me xel wo ngenong.  
\v 15 Sinaleyeiw di wong lulvako nimza, om xomaxoneing mi qalei liyeiw wei wo vanei me la eivek sakwaing mema nayak o me liw xel lek lelek me ghus en kandek Petele nak ond e tenu liw la lek xel.  
\v 16 Xel qendu ngandoung wei mi qekuma eno lam anghei beyeeng wei vivekwou Yerusalem o, me mi qou xel xe xel wei vanei me eti yeiw wei laweeng nol wo nol wou xel, eno dalus wo nimzalek. 
\s1 Sinaleyeiw la xeitueing 
\p  
\v 17 Woyom lumuki lukanzek me e xe xel dalus wei mi la lekti, xel on inyon Sadyusi, eno laleind mi wo nilul wou xel.  
\v 18 Xel zeimaxoun sinaleyeiw me toung xel eivek xeitueing wei beyeeng o.  
\v 19 Ekom eivek boukeing eno angela wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe yo tax xomek mya wei xeitueing o, dom qou xel me la myayaing.  
\v 20 Moxo neil, “Xam la, nale eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing wei qekueing ama yo me neil wou xomaxoneing en qayeeng dalus en mapieing vako tine.” 
\p  
\v 21 Xel ngo inye woy, de yanyeing eno xel eivek la tete lalei wei xomek vambuing wei qekueing ama yo, me teyoxe qayeeng wou xomaxoneing. 
\p De xel lumuki lukanzek me e xe xel lam tyip, xel taxe xel kanzol, me xel leitata wei Israel o lam qekuma, me wong xel la xomek xeitueing bei na qou sinaleyeiw me nam.  
\v 22 Xel belimbo la tyip xomek xeitueing ekom xel se yei xel sinale. Om xel lox me la neil wou teivateiv bei,  
\v 23 “Xa xei xomek xeitueing mya ekom xel toung zeyi, de xel belimbo toungale wou xomek mya. Ekom gyeik ingwei xa tax qapomb eno xa se xei xelti eivek xomek lalei.”  
\v 24 Woyom beyeiv wei mi yeiteyei xomek vambuing me xel lumuki leitata ngo qayeeng tine eno etek, me wounaleind ngenong bei lul tine nambei nya? 
\p  
\v 25 Woyom tambiy ti lam me neil, “Wei! Xel moux wei xam ghe toung eivek xomek xeitueing eno toungale eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing wei ngoeing qayeeng o me di teyoxe xomaxoneing.”  
\v 26 Om beyeiv tiyon la is xel belimbo me qou sinaleyeiw. Xel se wo lulti wou xel, en nambei xel yaleeng en xel xomaxoneing on tyek banex xel angya qakous. 
\p  
\v 27 Om xel la qou sinaleyeiw, me la lax xel wou xel kanzol mendghalus, bei lumuki lukanzek teling xel.  
\v 28 E neil, “Xa wong qayeeng petieing nikanzek wou xam bei, xam se teyoxe xel lek lei tine, ekom xam ghe wong beyeeng Yerusalem ne pup en xam xe teyoxeing me ghe di byex qayeeng lek xa bei xa leis e mey.” 
\p  
\v 29 Petele is sinale bamba neil elox wou xel bei, “Tyek xa betiwou Anutu de se xomaxoneing!  
\v 30 Xam ghe teyu Yesu lek xax pepeeng me ghe leis e mey. Ekom Anutu wei xe bundyeiw eno piyexe Yesu veil meyeing,  
\v 31 me toung e la dei wou emaxow mema payeiv, nambei gyovaxa me Tambiy wei vind xey veil nilul o. E wong ambei nye en kandek xel Israel pekwi xow veil nilul de e semaleeng xel xe sewokeing.  
\v 32 Xa xei mami wou lulti beimambei ne dalus woy, me Laweeng Vambuing byexaxoun qayeeng ne is ambei nyon bei lul beimambei ne neing ayang, wei Anutu wong wou xel wei mi betiwou e yo.” 
\p  
\v 33 Xel kanzol ngo qayeeng tine eno xel laleind wo vanei ngandoung om xel embei nyeis xel amey.  
\v 34 Ekom Parisi ti lei Gameliel, Putoung wei petieing o, wei xomaxoneing mi sanghoxe e lei yo, eno nale gheyapu wou xel kanzol dalus mendghalus me wong qayeeng nikanzek bei xel a qou sinaleyeiw me na myayaing nayaka le.  
\v 35 Woyom moxo neil qayeeng wou xel, “Xam moux wei Israel, xam ghe bounaleim bo nimza en vati wei xam ambeing bong wou xel moux ti beimambei ne yo.  
\v 36 Bouk valu la tax veil ekom Teudas lam tyip, me neil embei e lei ngandoung, me moux 400 eno mi betiwou e. Eno xel seyap leis e mey, de e xe xel betiyeing pek, om xuk dalus on wong ambei lul bandaing.  
\v 37 Ka bouk wei seyap qou xel xomaxoneing leind, Yudas wei Galili eno dandiy xomaxoneing ngenong la wou xow. E is ambei nyon xel leis e mey, de e xe xel dalus pek me vu ama lala.  
\v 38 Nambei nyon, gweimbeeng a neil wou xam, xam memamim tena xel moux beimambei ne na! En wangwei xel xe xuk wei xel di wong ne inye xomaxoneing xe, on tyek neing ama veil.  
\v 39 Ek wangwei inye lam wou Anutu, on xam seng teyeimbei bale zeyi xel moux beimambei ne, tyek xam venaxow gwei bei xam ghe di wo vevek is Anutu.” 
\p  
\v 40 Xel ngo Gameliel xe qayeeng me lewexe lek. Om xel kanzol taxe sinaleyeiw la lalei me wong beyeiv sesa xel. Woyom xel luk nikanzek wou xel bei, “xam seng nox a neil qayeeng lek Yesu lei no,” dom wong xel la. 
\p  
\v 41 Xel sinale ghanaw xel kanzol, me wong xeindlala en Anutu wounalei bei xel ne nimza teyei bei qou niyalenyeing en Yesu lei.  
\v 42 Teyei lek bouk sapa, xel mi la tete lalei wei xomek vambuing me xomek titi wei xomaxoneing o me teyoxe xel, de xel se tip neileing xoulek Nimza. Ma. Xel neil teyei bei Yesu yon Kilisi. 
\c 6  
\s1 Xel beyal moux lim yuw 
\p  
\v 1 Eivek bouk ti beimambei yon eno xel betiyeing di nyouk, xel Yuda valu wei mi luk Grik vyend eno wo veweeng is xel Yuda wei mi luk Hibru yo. Me neil embei xel Yudayeiw mi pum yaeing wou kanyo yeiw de xel se mi vind xa xe vexeiv wei Grik o en yaeing teyei lek bouk.  
\v 2 Om xel sinale xoumeeng yuw qeku xel betiyeing dalus lekti me neil, “Inye se teyei lek bei xa saing Anutu xe xoulek neileing de na bo xuk lek pumeing lul yaeing.  
\v 3 Xam lingyeiw, xam beyal moux lim yuw eivek xam senghoing on wei xam ghe woulek bei Laweeng Vambuing pup xel me xel lundpeyei nimza yo. Tyek xa bong xuk tine e nox mena wou xel,  
\v 4 de tyek xa bale ding lek zeimeing mema me xuk wei neileing Anutu xe xoulek o.” 
\p  
\v 5 Qayeeng tine wong moux alis vex dalus laleind wo nimza, om xel beyal Setepan, moux wei pup en wongeingis me en Laweeng Vambuing, me Pilip, Plokolas, Nikanor, Timon, Palmenas, me Nikolas nanghei Antiok, wei mi betiwou qayeeng wei Yudayeiw o.  
\v 6 Xel qou xel moux ti beimambei ne me la wou xel sinale, me xel zeimemend wou xel de liw memend lek xel. 
\p  
\v 7 Om xoulek wei Anutu xe eno la wo sapa. Xomaxoneing ngenong wei Yerusalem eno wong ambei betiyeing me nyouk daing, me lumukiyeiw valu beti eno wongis ambei nyon. 
\s1 Xel Yuda zeim axound Setepan 
\p  
\v 8 Gweimbeeng Setepan on moux wei pup en Anutu xe lalei xeiles me nikanzek, me mi wong dee wei lulvako ngenong eno eivek xomaxoneing senghoing.  
\v 9 Ekom xomaxoneing valu qandi me wong veweeng is Setepan. Xel on anghei xomek qekueing ama wei xel taxe bei tul e la. Xel on nanghei Yuda eno lam anghei Sairini me Aleksandlia me lam anghei provins wei Silisia me Esia.  
\v 10 Ekom xel se teyeimbei bale zeyi e lupeyei me Laweeng Vambuing wei di luk angya yo. 
\p  
\v 11 Woyom xel xupek me zeim xel valu laleind lek me neil embei, “Xa ngo Setepan lukyak lek Mose me Anutu.” 
\p  
\v 12 Om xel zeim xomaxoneing laleind lek me teivateiv me putoung wei petieing o. Om xel zeimaxoun Setepan me qou e me la wou xel kanzol.  
\v 13 Xel beyal xel valu bei xel a byex qayeeng tyonyeing lek Setepan me neil ambei nye, “Taxombouk eno tambiy ne se mi tip lukeing nilul lek xomek vambuing tine me e xe qayeeng petieing.  
\v 14 En xa ngo e neil tiyon bei, ‘Yesu wei Nasaret o tyek lelolexe xomek vambuing tine me pelipek sakwaing wei Mose wong wou xey yo.’” 
\p  
\v 15 Xel dalus tiwei toundei eivek kanzol beeng eno domend wou Setepan, me xel yei e ma yon siing ambei angela ti manghalus. 
\c 7  
\s1 Setepan neil qayeeng wou xel kanzol 
\p  
\v 1 Woyom lumuki lukanzek teling wou e, “Qayeeng tiwei xel neil lek wang ne inye zonghek?” 
\p  
\v 2 Om moxo neil elox, “Xam lingyeiw me xam mangyeiw, xam ngo wou a le! Xeiyaing wei Anutu xe eno lam tyip wou xe mend Apraham gyeik nanghei toundei eivek Mesopotamia, myaxeeng atax en ingwei mindei eivek Haran o.  
\v 3 Anutu neil wou e, ‘Wang na veil bam me nimpapu, dom ghe na tembuing tiwei tyek a talex wou wang o.’ 
\p  
\v 4 “Om Apraham moxo ghanaw tembuing wei Kaldia me la dei eivek Haran. Ka bouk wei Apraham ma mey yo, Anutu wong e la tembuing tiwei xam ghe toundei lek gweimbeeng ne.  
\v 5 Anutu se wong tembuing ti wou Apraham nanghei inye, me se wong tembuing ti bombek wou e. Qe Anutu neil qayeeng atax wou moxo bei e me e neumambu wei loxyus en e yo tyek na qou nind tembuing kayon, gyeik Apraham neu nanghei ma yo.  
\v 6 Anutu luk wou Apraham eivek sakwaing tine: Wa neumambum tyek bong ambei xel ba eivek beyeeng wei se xel venaxow xe yo, me tyek xel bo pok ngandoung me xel on tyek bo nilul wou xel teyei lek vakovek qes 400.  
\v 7 Anutu neil, tyek a bong myaveweeng wou tembuing tiwei mi wo pok ngandoung wou xel o, dekalekom tyek xel nam myayaing veil beyeeng tiyon me bong lalo wou ay eivek beyeeng tine.  
\v 8 Woyom Anutu wong qokatu wei ghuweing ninavi yo. Me Apraham on Isaka ma gyeik xel ghuw e ninavi lek bouk lim yal o. Me Isaka yon Yakop ma, de Yakop on neuyeiw xoumeeng yuw mend wei xel wo lukanzek en velei xoumeeng yuw o. 
\p  
\v 9 “Yakop neuyeiw wei wo lukanzek en velei xoumeeng yuw on laleind wo vanei wou Yosep, om xel wo vateivek lek e wou xel amba, en xuk bandaing eivek Izip. Ekom Anutu vena mindei is e  
\v 10 me mi zeim e veil e xe nimaying dalus. De wong lupeyei nimza wou e om king Parao wei Izip o lalei vind Yosep. Om wong Yosep yeiteyei Izip me e xe lulul dalus wei e beeng o. 
\p  
\v 11 “Woyom maxep ngandoung ti yeip lek beyeeng Izip dalus me Kenan, om nimaying ngandoung lam wou xomaxoneing, me xe bundyeiw se teyeimbei gyeiwou yaeing ti.  
\v 12 Om gyeik Yakop ngo bei yaeing toundei eivek beyeeng Izip, moxo wong xe bundyeiw la Izip ti myaxeeng.  
\v 13 Xel lox me la luyuw, eno Yosep neil xow teyei wou liyeiw, me Parao woulek Yosep liyeiw is ambei nyon.  
\v 14 Om Yosep wong qayeeng la wou ma Yakop me e neumambu dalus bei xel nam wou e, xel xouing teyei lek 75.  
\v 15 Woyom Yakop la xo wei Izip nei, dekakom e me xe mend a bund eno xel xouing mey anghei nyon.  
\v 16 Xel qou neing wei xel xe meyeing me lox Sekem me toung xel eivek leiveeng meyeing wei Apraham xouv wou Hamor neuyeiw anghei Sekem en malew valu yo. 
\p  
\v 17 “Nambei bouk di lam paviy ingwei Anutu embei bong e xe qayeeng zonghek wei mi neil wou Apraham eno embo neing lek, de xel xomaxoneing Israel vamva wei mi dei eivek Izip eno di nyouk.  
\v 18 Woyom king nge, wei se woulek Yosep, eno yeiteyei Izip.  
\v 19 King tiyon mi yei xe xe xomaxoneing wo nilul me mi tyoxe xe bundyeiw me wong nilul wou xel, me mi tendu xel bei xel banex neuyeiw wei yakyeis eno na myayaing en kandek xel amey. 
\p  
\v 20 “Lek bouk kayon eno Mose umbek, me Mose yon yakyeis nimza ka wou Anutu manghalus. Moxo mindei eivek ma beeng teyei lek dentouk qes yal.  
\v 21 Om gyeik xel toung e la myayaing, Parao neu vex zeim e me qou me yeiteyei nambei emaxow neu moux.  
\v 22 Mose wevek xomek qapiya me qou kwa nimza dalus wei Izip o, me e tambiy wei mi luk nikanzek me mi wo xuk leimalei yon wo nikanzek. 
\p  
\v 23 “Gyeik Mose xe vakovek qes xoumeeng vey (40), moxo wou kwa bei embei na gyei liyeiw wei Israel o.  
\v 24 Moxo yei Izip ti di leis Israel ti, om Mose la vind li Israel on me qou e lu me leis Izip tiyon mey.  
\v 25 Mose wou kwa bei inyon emaxow xe xel Israel tyek boulek inyon bei Anutu wong e lam bei e devind xel, ekom xel se woulek.  
\v 26 De yanyeing eno Mose lam me yei Israel yayuw di leis ama. Moxo wong en embei bale zeyi luw me neil, ‘Inyon muw limim ama yo, nambei nya muw ghe leis ama?’ 
\p  
\v 27 “Ekom xomaxoneing nge wei wo vevek atax eno tendu Mose la nenya de neil, ‘Eti beyal wang me wong wang wo gyovaxa me tambiy wei ngoeing qayeeng wei xa yo.  
\v 28 Wa being nyeis a mey nambei ingwei wang leis Izip ti mey vezeiveeng o?’  
\v 29 Gyeik Mose ngo qayeeng tine, moxo pek me la Midian, me la dei inyon ambei tambiy ba me wo neu moux yuw. 
\p  
\v 30 “Ka vakovek qes xoumeeng vey (40) la veil, woyom angela ti tyip wou Mose eivek nenyex magyand wei tum lek xax mema eivek tembuing bandaing paviy lukendu Sinai yo.  
\v 31 Gyeik Mose yei tine, moxo etek me dula paviy en embei gyei embo nimza, moxo ngo Tambiy Ngandoung vya neil ambei nye,  
\v 32 ‘A Anutu wei wa bumyeiw o, Anutu wei Apraham, Isaka me Yakop o.’ Mose etek is yalenyeing me embei se gyei. 
\p  
\v 33 “Woyom Tambiy Ngandoung neil wo e, kwax wa xe vaxalambes on veil, en beyeeng kawei wang toungale lek on inye tembuing vambuing.  
\v 34 A xei kwa nilul wei xel wong wou a xe xel xomaxoneing eivek Izip o woy. A ngo xel xe engeing, om a lam bei na qou xel noum veil nimaying. Om lam kane, en tyek a bong wang nox me na Izip. 
\p  
\v 35 “Mose tine kawei xel pesek e me neil, eti beyal wang en gyovaxa me tambiy wei ngoeing qayeeng wei xa yo? Mose moxo Anutu wong ela bei e gyeiteyei xel me na qou xel angya angela mema wei tyip wou e lek xax nayak o.  
\v 36 Mose tine qou xel me lam veil Izip me wong dee me lulvako eivek Izip, me nanghei Mamileeng Gyand me ela eivek tembuing bandaing on teyei lek vakovek qes xoumeeng vey (40). 
\p  
\v 37 “Mose kayon tiwei neil wou Israelyeiw bei, ‘Anutu tyek bong poropet ti nambei ay eivek xam venaxow xe xomaxoneing.’  
\v 38 Mose tine dei eivek qekueing ama yon eivek tembuing bandaing is xe bundyeiw, me is angela tiwei luk is Mose lek lukendu Sinai yo is xe bundyeiw, me moxo qou qayeeng mapieing me lam bei e nam bong wou xey. 
\p  
\v 39 “Ekom xe bundyeiw pyalek en xel embei se betiwou e. Qe xel pesek e me eivek xel xe woueing nalei bei xel embei nox me na Izip.  
\v 40 Om xel neil wou Aron, ‘Wa menyex anutuyeiw en xel natax en xa. En nambei Mose tine eno la tax en xa me lam myayaing veil Izip eno xa loungen bei vati wong e!’  
\v 41 Bouk tiyon eno xel betiy manghaxo neu ti tenu. De xel qou lul leimalei me wong ela wou nambei xound me wong xeindlala ngandoung me sanghoxe lul wei xel wong angya memend o.  
\v 42 Ekom Anutu toung demi wou xel me pelipek xel laleind eivek bei xel bong lalo wou sayeiv, dentouk me betum teyei lek qayeeng wei poropet byex eivek qapiya yo: 
\q1 “Xam xomek wei Israel o, beip xam ghe toung xound me da wou ay teyei lek vakovek qes xoumeeng vey (40) wei xam ghe mindei eivek tembuing bandaing o, ei? 
\q1  
\v 43 Xam ghe qalei xomek wei Molek me betum wei xam xe anutu Lepan tenu bandaing wei xam ghe betiy bei na mi bo lalo wou yo. Nambei nyon tyek a bong xam ghe na eivek beyeeng tiwei yeip Babilon valu lox nei. \rq Amos 5:25-27\rq* 
\p  
\v 44 “Lek bouk wei xe bundyeiw dei eivek tembuing bandaing eno xel qalei xomek sel wei Anutu xe qoupek wei petieing mi yeip eivek eno is xel. Xomek tiwei xel lax ne eno Anutu neil wou Mose bei xel balax teyei lek tenu wei talex wou Mose yo.  
\v 45 Kalekom xe bundyeiw is Yosua qou xomek sel me qoupek wei petieing o me lam bei na qou tembuing wei xel amba xe yo. Anutu tiy xel la veil, dom lax xomek sel ne lek tembuing on me elam tyip wou bouk wei Dawit o.  
\v 46 Dawit tiwei Anutu lalei wo nimza wou e eno teling wou Anutu bei dev xomek nimza ti wou Anutu wei Yakop o.  
\v 47 Dekakom Salomo ev Anutu xe xomek tiyon. 
\p  
\v 48 “Ekom Anutu wei tyoung gheyapu nei se mindei eivek xomek wei xomaxoneing ev o. Nambei poropet neil, 
\q1  
\v 49 “‘Tambiy Ngandoung neil, “Tyoung gheyapu yon a xe siaking, 
\q2 me tembuing on a xe zek wei a mi lax vaxang lek o. 
\q1 Om tyek xam ghe dev xomek vati wou ay? 
\q2 O beyeeng wei ambei qou laweeng eno yeip inya? 
\q1  
\v 50 Beip a memang se toung lulul dalus ti beimambei ne?”’ \rq Yesaya 66:1-2\rq* 
\p  
\v 51 “Xam xomaxoneing on lumimpeyei nikanzek me xam laleimim on wo mapetok me xam nenyamim on wo qatu. Me xam ghe teyei lek bumyeiw, me ghe mi pyalek Laweeng Vambuing.  
\v 52 Poropet eti eno xam bumyeiw se mi wo nilul wou e? Xel leis xel xomaxoneing wei mi neil Tambiy Ti Bombek o teyei, wei e bei nam o. Me gweimbeeng xam ghe neil e teyei de ghe leis e mey.  
\v 53 Xam on ghe qou petieing wou angela, ekom xam seng betiwou.” 
\s1 Xel nex Setepan mey angya qakous 
\p  
\v 54 Gyeik xel ngo qayeeng tine, xel laleind wo vanei ngandoung wou e, me nga vind wou e.  
\v 55 Ekom Laweeng Vambuing pup Setepan, om yeila tyoung gheyapu nei me yei xeiyaing wei Anutu yo, me yei Yesu toungale wou Anutu mema payeiv.  
\v 56 De moxo neil, “Wei, a xei tyoung gheyapu tax me Xomaxoneing Neu Moux toungale wou Anutu mema payeiv.” 
\p  
\v 57 Ka xel ngo tine xel sevun nenyend de ghak niseikeing, en xel embei se ngo e vya, xel xouing qapyex me la wou e,  
\v 58 de tetei e la myayaing veil beyeeng ngandoung on dom nex e gya qakous. De xel wei wong qayeeng en Setepan eno kwax xel xe teimb me toung wou moux ghavis ti lei Sol eno vaxa. 
\p  
\v 59 Ka xel nex Setepan nangya qakous, Setepan zeimema bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu, wa zeim a nung laweeng veil.”  
\v 60 Woyom moxo ev vaxa qatu eivek de eng niseikeing bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wa seng bo myaveweeng wou xel en sewokeing wei xel o.” Ka neil tine woy, moxo yeip. 
\c 8  
\p  
\v 1 Sol toundei inyon me yei kwa wei xel wong wou Setepan me e mey yon, eno lalei wo nimza. 
\s1 Sol di wo nol wou xel wei wongeingis o 
\p Lek bouk kawei xel leis Setepan eno xel di wo nol wou xel wongeingis wei mindei eivek Yerusalem. Om xel dalus pek me vuwama lala eivek tembuing danghei wei Yudia me Samaria. Dom sinaleyeiw nanghei toundei eivek Yerusalem.  
\v 2 Anutu xe xel moux wei mi betiwou e xe qayeeng eno ev Setepan me mi wo talot en e xe meyeing.  
\v 3 Ekom Sol anghei di wo nol wou xel wongeingis. Me mi la eivek xomek tambak on titi me tetei moux alis vex, me toung xel eivek xeitueing. 
\s1 Pilip la toundei Samaria 
\p  
\v 4 Xel wei pek me vuwama lala, eno mi neil Xoulek Nimza la eivek beyeeng inyayeiw wei xel la dei yo.  
\v 5 Pilip la xo wei beyeeng ngandoung nei ti eivek Samaria me neil Kilisi teyei nanghei inyon.  
\v 6 Gyeik xel qendu ngandoung on ngo Pilip me yei dee leimalei wei e wong o, xel dalus liw nenyend me ngo vati wei e di neil o.  
\v 7 En xel laweeng nilaxes nyayek niseikeing de lam myayaing veil xel ngenong on, de xel ngenong wei bezomb o, me xel wei mema vaxa wo nilul eno wo nimzalek.  
\v 8 Om moux alis vex wo xeindlala ngandoung eivek beyeeng ngandoung tiyon. 
\s1 Simon on mi wo velaw 
\p  
\v 9 Xomaxoneing ti mindei eivek beyeeng ngandoung tiyon, e lei Simon eno mi wong palak eivek beyeeng ngandoung ond, om xomaxoneing dalus wei Samaria eno etek, moxo mi byexvaxa bei e tambiy teiv ngandoung ti,  
\v 10 de xomaxoneing dalus, me xel wei leind ngandoung me leind nayak toung nenyend wou e me neil, “Moux tine qou nikanzek ngandoung nambei Anutu xe Nikanzek.”  
\v 11 De xel liw nenyend wou Simon en nambei e wong etekeing wou xel lumama en e xe palak.  
\v 12 Ekom gyeik Pilip di neil Xoulek Nimza wei Anutu xe tete lalei yo eivek Yesu Kilisi lei, omek xel wongis de xel lipek moux alis vex.  
\v 13 Simon venaxow wongis me lipek. Me moxo mi betiwou Pilip me la danghei danghei nei, me yei dee leimalei me lulvako ngandoung wei Pilip wong, om mi wounalei ngenong. 
\p  
\v 14 De woyom sinaleyeiw wei mindei eivek Yerusalem eno ngo bei Samariayeiw lewexe lek Anutu xe xoulek, om xel wong Petele luw Yoan la wou xel.  
\v 15 Gyeik luw la tyip, luw zeimemend wou xel bei xel a qou Laweeng Vambuing,  
\v 16 en nambei Laweeng Vambuing seng ghei lam lek xel valu qe xel qou lipekeing eivek Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu lei venaxow.  
\v 17 Woyom Petele luw Yoan li memend lek xel, me xel qou Laweeng Vambuing. 
\p  
\v 18 Simon yei inyon bei Laweeng Vambuing lam lek xel gyeik sinale luw xouing li memend lek xel on, om qou malew me la wou luw,  
\v 19 me neil, “Muw wong nikanzek tiyon wou ay, en kandek a ni memang lek xelti ond e qou Laweeng Vambuing o.” 
\p  
\v 20 Ekom Petele neil wou e, “Wa xe malew embo nol is wang, en wang wou kwam being bou lul wei Anutu wong bandaing o en malew!  
\v 21 Wa seng teyeimbei bong Anutu xe xuk tiwei uw andi wong ne, en nambei wa laleim on se wo bombek wou Anutu manghalus.  
\v 22 Wa pekwi xow veil kwa nilul tiwei wang wong o. Dom na zeimemam wou Tambiy Ngandoung bei e teyeimbei semaleeng wa xe kwa nilul wei di yeip eivek wa laleim on.  
\v 23 En a xei bei wa laleim on pup en lul nilul, me lul nilul on tup wang axound.” 
\p  
\v 24 Woyom Simon lewexe, “Muw zeimemamim wou Tambiy Ngandoung en ay, en kandek lulul wei muw ghe neil on ti se balwou ay.”  
\v 25 Om luw neil Tambiy Ngandoung xe xoulek teyei, de neil wou xel en lulul wei Tambiy Ngandoung wong wou luw o. De Petele me Yoan lox me la Yerusalem, luw di lox eno luw neil Xoulek Nimza eivek beyeeng ngenong wei Samaria yo. 
\s1 Pilip neil Xoulek Nimza wou Itiopia ti 
\p  
\v 26 Dekalekom angela wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe eno ti neil wou Pilip, “La xonei wou sakwaing tembuing bandaing, wei la xo Yerusalem nei me la Gasa yo.”  
\v 27 Om moxo qandi lek me la, me la tyip wou xomaxoneing wei Itiopia eno ti wou sakwaing, tambiy yon xel veil e nikanzek veil, tambiy yon lei ngandoung wei mi yeiteyei malew wei kwin Kandesi wei Itiopia yo. Xomaxoneing tine la Yerusalem bei na dundek wou Anutu,  
\v 28 om loum me lox me la beeng, de deilek e xe karis dom di pyaw qapiya wei poropet Yesaya byex o.  
\v 29 Laweeng Vambuing neil wou Pilip, “La paviy karis tiyon me la vaxam is e.” 
\p  
\v 30 Woyom Pilip veimya me la wou karis tiyon me ngo ingwei tambiy moxon di pyaw qayeeng wei poropet Yesaya byex o. Om Pilip teling wou e, “Beip wang woulek qayeeng wei wang di pyaw on?” 
\p  
\v 31 Moxo neil embei, “Wangwei xel ti se neil wou a nei, on tyek a boulek ambei nya?” Om moxo neil wou Pilip bei, e zekna mendei is e. 
\p  
\v 32 Tambiy tiwei xel veil e nikanzek veil eno di pyaw xoulek wei yeip eivek qapiya eno nambei nye: 
\q1 “Xel dandiy e nambei sipsip ti me la bei na nyeis e mey, ekom se neil qayeeng ti, 
\q2 me nambei sipsip lingheing wei xel qou 
\q1 me la bei na qateiv e nivlus veil o. 
\q1  
\v 33 Xel wo niyalenyeing wou e 
\q2 om xel se zeim e xe qayeeng wo nimza. 
\q2 Om eti teyei bei tul pavulek en e neumambu? 
\q2 En xel zeim e xe mapieing veil anghei tembuing.” \rq Yesaya 53:7-8\rq* 
\p  
\v 34 Tambiy tiwei xel veil e nikanzek veil eno teling wou Pilip, “Wa neil neing wou ay, bei poropet di luk en eti, emaxow o xel nge?”  
\v 35 Woyom Pilip neil qayeeng wei di yeip eivek qapiya yo wou tambiy tiyon, me neil Xoulek Nimza wou e en Yesu. 
\p  
\v 36 Ka luw di la wou sakwaing me la tyip wou memiing valu om tambiy on neil, “Wei, memiing inye. Nambei nya ekom a se teyei bei zipek?”  
\v 37 [De Pilip neil, “Wangwei wang bongis laleim dalus nei, yond wang teyei being zipek.” De moxo lewexe me neil, “A wongis bei Yesu kilisi yon Anutu Neu Moux.”]  
\v 38 Om moxo neil me karis nale, de luw Pilip xouing teila eivek memiing me Pilip lipek e.  
\v 39 Ka luw lek loum veil memiing, Laweeng Vambuing wei Tambiy Ngandoung eno lam lutika me qou Pilip de malang, om tambiy on se lox yei e no, ekom moxo di la wou sakwaing is xeilala me la beeng.  
\v 40 De Pilip yei bei la toundei eivek beyeeng Asdot, om la beyeeng tiyon me neil Xoulek Nimza eivek beyeeng sapa yon dekalekom la tyip Sisalia. 
\c 9  
\s1 Sol pekwi xow 
\p  
\v 1 Kalekom Sol di luk niseikeing en embei bo nol wou Tambiy Ngandoung xe xel betiyeing me nyeis xel a mey, om la wou lumuki lukanzek,  
\v 2 me teling wou moxo bei e byex qapiya ti ena wou xomek qekueing ama eivek Damaskus, en kandek wangwei e gyei eti yeiw mendi betiwou wou Sakwaing Tiyon, moux o vex, ond e zeim axound xel ambei xel wei xeitueing o de na qou me noum Yerusalem.  
\v 3 Ka moxo la wou sakwaing me la paviy Damaskus, eno xeiyaing ti lam lutika nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei me tel evivekwou e.  
\v 4 Moxo oing me teila lek tembuing de ngo vya ti neil wou e, “Sol, Sol, nambei nya wang di wo nimaying wou ay?” 
\p  
\v 5 Sol teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung wang eti?” 
\p Moxo neil, “A Yesu, tiwei wang di wo nimaying wou yo.  
\v 6 Gweimbeeng qandi lek me la eivek beyeeng wei Damaskus nei, en tyek tambiy ti na neil wou wang en vati wei wang bong o.” 
\p  
\v 7 Xel xomaxoneing wei di la is Sol eno nale inyon de se wo lukluk, xel ngo vya ti ekom xel se yei xelti.  
\v 8 Sol qandi lek veil tembuing, ekom gyeik ingwei vindek manghalus lek eno moxo se yei lulti. Om xel zeim e mema me la eivek Damaskus.  
\v 9 Teyei lek bouk yal eno moxo manghalus nanghei toundei matekeing, om se ya lulti, o se num. 
\p  
\v 10 Betiyeing ti toundei eivek Damaskus e lei Ananias. Tambiy Ngandoung taxe la wou e eivek ingwei manghalus pekwi yo me neil, “Ananias!” 
\p Moxo neil elox, “Tambiy Ngandoung a toundei yo.” 
\p  
\v 11 Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou e, “Qandi lek me la xomek wei Yudas o, wou sakwaing mema wei xel mi taxe bei Sakwaing Bombek nei, me teling en xomaxoneing wei lam anghei Tarsus, e lei Sol, wei!, moxo di zeimema.  
\v 12 Eivek ingwei manghalus pekwi eno yei moux ti lei Ananias lam me liw mema lek e bei bong e manghalus gyeina no.” 
\p  
\v 13 Ananias neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, a ngo qayeeng ngenong en moux tine, me nimaying dalus wei mi wong wou wa xe xel wei mi wongis wang eivek Yerusalem o.  
\v 14 De e lam inye is nikanzek wei lumuki leitata wong wou bei e nam a zeimaxoun xel dalus wei mi taxe wa leim o.”  
\v 15 Ekom Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou Ananias, “La! tambiy tinei inye a xe xukxe wei a beyal bei e qalei a leing me na wou xel amba, me xel king me wou xomaxoneing wei Israel o.  
\v 16 Tyek a talex wou e en nimaying maying wei embei qalei en a leing o.” 
\p  
\v 17 Woyom Ananias la eivek xomek me la lalei. De li mema lek Sol, moxo neil, “Ling Sol, Ka wang di lam inye eno Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu tyip wou wang wou sakwaing, eno wong a lam bei wang gweina no me Laweeng Vambuing e pup wang lek.”  
\v 18 De lutika eno lulti nambei bis teila veil Sol manghalus, om moxo teyeimbei gyeina no. De moxo qandi lek dom lipek,  
\v 19 Ka e ya yaeing valu woy, eno moxo qou nikanzek no. 
\s1 Sol neil Xoulek Nimza nanghei Damaskus 
\p Sol dei inyon bouk valu is xel betiyeing eivek Damaskus.  
\v 20 Lutika eno moxo neil xoulek eivek xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw bei Yesu yon Anutu Neu Moux.  
\v 21 Xel dalus tiwei ngo e eno etek me teling, “Beip inyon tambiy tiwei mi leis xel eivek Yerusalem wei mi taxe lei tiyon o? Beip se lam inye bei na qou xel nambei xel xeitueing me na wou xel lumuki leitata?”  
\v 22 Ekom Sol wo nikanzek kamouyo, me neil xoulek yeip yanyateiv wou Yudayeiw wei mindei eivek Damaskus bei “Yesu yon Kilisi.” 
\p  
\v 23 Ka bouk ngenong la veil, om Yudayeiw qekuma me tup qayeeng lekti bei, xel embei na zeimaxoun Sol dom nyeis e mey,  
\v 24 ekom Sol qou kwa woy wou xel xe woueing nalei. Bendiyeing aluw boukeing eno xel mi toung mend wou tete mya wei Damaskus o, en xel embei nyeis e mey.  
\v 25 Ekom e xe xel betiyeing qou e eivek boukeing me lek tete ngandoung wei vivekwou beyeeng on me wong e lep me la eivek pasik ngandoung me e la tete demi veil beyeeng on. 
\p  
\v 26 Ka e la tyip Yerusalem, me moxo embei na is xel betiyeing, ekom xel dalus yaleeng en e de xel se wongis bei e wo betiyeing ti neing.  
\v 27 Ekom Banabas qou e me la wou xel wei sinale yo. Moxo neil wou xel bei Sol di lam wou sakwaing eno yei Tambiy Ngandoung me Tambiy Ngandoung luk wou e, me eivek Damaskus e luk nikanzek wou xel on eivek Yesu lei.  
\v 28 Om Sol toundei is xel me ghavineeng eivek Yerusalem, moxo se yaleeng qe di luk nikanzek en Tambiy Ngandoung lei.  
\v 29 E luk me nganeng is Yudayeiw wei mi luk Grik o en Yesu, ekom xel di wong en embei nyeis e mey.  
\v 30 Gyeik liyeiw ngo qayeeng tine, xel qou e me la Sisalia me wong e la Tarsus. 
\p  
\v 31 Woyom xel wongeingis eivek Yudia, Galili me Samaria eno dei wo nimza is ama. Xel valu se wo nol wou xel, om Laweeng Vambuing byexaxoun xel, de xel dei xeinghembi eivek Tambiy Ngandoung. De xel wongeingis nyouk me wo ngenong. 
\s1 Ainias me Dokas 
\p  
\v 32 Ka Petele ghavineeng me la eivek beyeeng valuvalu nei, moxo la en embei na gyei xel wongeingis wei toundei eivek beyeeng Lida nei.  
\v 33 Nanghei inyon eno moxo yei xomaxoneing ti lei Ainias, tambiy on bezomb, om moxo mi yeip lek zek teyei lek vakovek qes lim yal.  
\v 34 Petele neil wou e, “Ainias, Yesu Kilisi wong wang wo nimzalek. Qandi me vevilexe wa xe ghus.” Lutika eno Ainias qandi.  
\v 35 Xel dalus tiwei mindei eivek Lida me Saron eno yei moxo wo nimzalek, om xel pekwi me loum wou Tambiy Ngandoung. 
\p  
\v 36 Eivek Jopa inyon betiyeing ti lei Tabita (xel pekwi bei Dokas), taxombouk eno vexo mi wo nimza me vind xel wei kanyo yo.  
\v 37 Lek bouk kayon vexo qou myavanei ti me mey, om xel lipek vexo dom liw e la eivek xomek lalei wei yeip ghey yo.  
\v 38 Lida yon di yeip paviy Jopa, de xel betiyeing ngo bei Petele la toundei Lida, om xel wong tambiy yuw la wou e me neil wou e, “Wang nam daing wou xa!” 
\p  
\v 39 Petele la is luw, me gyeik e la tyip eno xel qou e me la xomek gheyapu wei Dokas di yeip eivek on, vexeiv dalus on toungale vivekwou e, xel di eng me talex teimb wei Dokas mi duw o gyeik e ghei toundei mapieing is xel o. 
\p  
\v 40 Petele wong xel dalus la myayaing veil xomek lalei, woyom moxo ev vaxakatu eivek dom zeim. De pekwi ma lox wou meyeing me neil, “Tabita, qandi.” Vexo vindek malek me yei Petele dom qandi me dei ghey.  
\v 41 Moxo zeim e lek me vind e nale lek vaxa, woyom taxe xel Wongeingis me xel vexeiv lam, dom talex Tabita wou xel bei toundei mapieing.  
\v 42 Xuk ti Petele wong ne eno qayeeng la teyei lek beyeeng sapa wei Jopa nei, me xomaxoneing ngenong wongis Tambiy Ngandoung.  
\v 43 Petele dei eivek Jopa teyei lek bouk valu is tambiy ti lei Simon, tambiy on mi wo xuk lek manghaxo ninavi. 
\c 10  
\s1 Konilias taxe Petele 
\p  
\v 1 Nanghei Sisalia eno tambiy ti mi dei inyon eno lei Konilias, inyon beyeiv wei xel 100 vevekyeiw o wei xel mi taxe bei vevekyeiw qendu ti wei beyeeng Itali yo.  
\v 2 Moxo lis nipapu mi yaleeng me betiwou Anutu teyei lek bouk tambak, me mi vind xel wei kanyo yo. De taxombouk eno mi zeimema wou Anutu.  
\v 3 Bouk ti lek seivma yal wei soukeing eno Konilias mapekwi me yei bei Anutu xe angela ti lam di neil qayeeng wou e me neil embei, “Konilias!” 
\p  
\v 4 Konilias yaleeng me doma wou e, Moxo teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung, inye va?” 
\p Angela lewexe, “Wa xe zeimeing me vineing wei wang mi wong wou xel kanyo eno la gheyapu wou Anutu manghalus nambei da wei woueing nalei en o.  
\v 5 Om wong moux valu la Jopa me qou tambiy tiwei lei Simon o me loum. Wei xel mi taxe e lei nge eno Petele.  
\v 6 Moxo mindei is Simon tambiy wei mi wo xuk lek manghaxo ninavi yo, wei e beeng di yeip wou mamileeng nenyawes o.” 
\p  
\v 7 Ka angela luk is e woy dom la, woyom Konilias taxe e xe xukxe yuw me xel vevekyeiw eno ti wei mi betiwou Anutu me mi yeiwou xow woy en xuk wei Konilias o.  
\v 8 Moxo neil wou lal en lulul sapa wei tyip on dom wong lal la Jopa. 
\s1 Petele manghalus pekwi me yei 
\p  
\v 9 Lek bouk nge yanyeing wei seivma evlek eno tambiy yal on la tyip paviy beyeeng ngandoung Jopa, de Petele lek la xomek demi qetyei bei na zeim mema.  
\v 10 Moxo maxepya om embei gya lul yaeing valu, ka xel di yeiwou lul yaeing, eno moxo manghalus pekwi me yei.  
\v 11 Moxo yei tyoung gheyapu tax me lulti nambei qaeing ngandoung ti, wei xel byex yis eivek nenyawes vey de wong e tei lam lek tembuing.  
\v 12 Eivek qaeing on eno pup en leliy leliy wei vaxa vey eno lam eivek tiyon me ingwei mi yelek tembuing me menek menek o.  
\v 13 Woyom vya ti neil wou e, “Petele, qandi, de leis me wa.” 
\p  
\v 14 Petele neil elox bei, “Se teyei, Tambiy Ngandoung! A se mi xa lul wei nilul o nilaxes o ti.” 
\p  
\v 15 Woyom vya tine neil wou e luyuw, “Wa se taxe lulti nilaxes wei Anutu wong e wo vako yo.” 
\p  
\v 16 Tine wo luyal, de lutika eno qaeing ngandoung tiyon leklox me la tyoung gheyapu. 
\p  
\v 17 Kalekom Petele di wounalei ngenong en ingwei manghalus pekwi me yei eno qes, de moux yal wei Konilias wong lal la eno la yeiwou Simon beeng om lal nale wou tete mya.  
\v 18 Xel taxe la me teling bei, “Simon tiwei lei nge bei Petele eno toundei inye?” 
\p  
\v 19 Ka Petele nanghei di wounalei en ingwei manghalus pekwi me yei vati yo, eno Laweeng Vambuing neil wou e bei, “Simon, moux yayal di yimexe wang o.  
\v 20 Om qandi me lep me la xonei, wa seng bounaleim ngenong en laeing is lal, en a wong lal lak.” 
\p  
\v 21 Petele la xonei me neil wou lal, “A tiwei mal ghe di wimexe eno inye. Mal ghe lam en va?” 
\p  
\v 22 Moux yal on neil elox, “Konilias beyeiv wei xel vevek o wong ghal a lam. E yon bombek me tambiy wei mi yaleeng en Anutu yo, e tiwei xel Yudayeiw dalus mi wevek e xeinghembi yo. Angela vambuing neil wou bei wang na e xe xomek en kandek e ngo vati wei wambei neil o.”  
\v 23 Woyom Petele neil wou moux yal on me qou lal me la eivek beeng me yeiteyei lal boukeing tiyon. 
\s1 Petele la Konilias beeng 
\p Nge yanyeing eno Petele la is lal me xel wongeingis valu nanghei Jopa eno la is.  
\v 24 Yanyeing eno xel la tyip Sisalia. Konilias di wou kwa en xel, me taxe nipapu dalus me gweleeng yeiw wei mindei paviy e yo me xel qeku la toundei.  
\v 25 Ka Petele la eivek xomek, Konilias la pelong e me ev vaxa qatu eivek de wo lalo wou e.  
\v 26 Ekom Petele wong e nale ghey. De neil wou e, “Nale, a maxow ne moux bandaing.” 
\p  
\v 27 De Petele la lalei me luk is e, me yei xomaxoneing qendu ngandoung ti di qekuma.  
\v 28 Moxo neil wou xel, “Xam venaxow ghe woulek e wo nimza bei, Inyei se la teyei lek xa xe petieing bei Yudayeiw ti na mendei is xel amba o na paviy xel. Ekom Anutu talex wou ay bei a se taxe xelti bei e nilul o e nilaxes.  
\v 29 Om a se pyalek wa vyam wei wang taxe ay yo. Qe a lam teyei lek wa vyam, om ambei teling xam bei xam ghe taxe ay en va?” 
\p  
\v 30 Konilias lewexe, “Bouk vey lak veil eno a toundei eivek bang me na zeimemang lek seivma tine, lek seivma yal wei soukeing o. Lutika eno tambiy ti byex teimb wei teltyip eno nale wou a manghalus  
\v 31 me neil, ‘Konilias, Anutu ngo wa xe zeimeing mema me wounalei en wa xe wongeing wei wang mi wong wou xel kanyo yo.  
\v 32 Om wong xelti la Jopa en Simon wei xel mi taxe lei nge bei Petele yo. Moxo la toundei eivek xomek wei Simon wei mi wo xuk lek manghaxo ninavi yo, wei e xe xomek toundei wou mamileeng nenyawes o.’  
\v 33 Om a wong tambiy yal lak lutika, dom inye nimza bei wang lam. Gweimbeeng wei xe xouing dalus a toundei inye wou Anutu manghalus bei na ngo wou lul sapa wei Tambiy Ngandoung peti wou wang bei wa neil wou xa yo.” 
\s1 Petele neil xoulek eivek Konilias beeng 
\p  
\v 34 Woyom Petele embei baluk: “Gweimbeeng a woulek zonghek bei inyon Anutu se mi talex lalei vineing wou xelti venaxow  
\v 35 qe mi lewexe lek xomaxoneing wei lam anghei tembuing tambak nei me mi yaleeng en e me mi wong vati wei bombek o.  
\v 36 Xam ghe woulek qayeeng wei Anutu wong ela wou xomaxoneing wei Israel o, me neil Xoulek Nimza wei lalei vevopeing wei lam eivek Yesu Kilisi yo, e tiwei wo Tambiy Ngandoung en lul dalusateiv o.  
\v 37 Xam ghe woulek lul tambak woy wei belup ela teyei lek tembuing sapa wei Yudia nei. Dekakom Yoan neil qayeeng wei lipekeing o. Lul ne qandi tax eivek Galili.  
\v 38 Xam ghe woulek bei Anutu beyal Yesu wei Nasaret o me wong Laweeng Vambuing me nikanzek wou e, me xam ghe woulek ingwei e la ghavinenyeing me vind xel me wong xel dalus wei mindei xeinghembi eivek nikanzek wei tambiy mapetok o wo nimzalek, en nambei Anutu toundei is e. 
\p  
\v 39 “Xa xei lek mami en lul dalus wei Yesu wong eivek tembuing tambak wei Yudayeiw me eivek Yerusalem o. Xel leis e mey nangya ingwei xel teyu e lek xax o,  
\v 40 ekom Anutu piyexe e veil meyeing lek bouk yal, de lenghek lek bei xomaxoneing gyei e.  
\v 41 Xomaxoneing dalus on se yei e, qe xel wei yei eno inyon Anutu beyal xel wongeingis wei xa mi xa me na num is e gyeik ingwei qandi lek veil meyeing o.  
\v 42 E wong qayeeng nikanzek wou xa bei xa neil qayeeng wou xomaxoneing me na neil teyeimbei, e tambiy tiwei Anutu beyal bei e zeim qayeeng wei mapieing me meyeing o.  
\v 43 Poropet dalus neil e teyei bei xel dalus wei wongis e eno mi semaleeng xel xe sewokeing veil eivek Yesu lei.” 
\p  
\v 44 Ka Petele nanghei di neil qayeeng tine, Laweeng Vambuing lam axone lek xomaxoneing dalus wei ngo qayeeng ne yo.  
\v 45 Xel wongeingis wei ghuw nindnavi me lam is Petele eno etek en vineing wei Laweeng Vambuing qapyex elam lek xel wei bamba yo is.  
\v 46 En xel ngo ingwei xel on di luk eivek vya vya me sanghoxe Anutu yo. 
\p Woyom Petele neil,  
\v 47 “Eti teyeimbei bale zeyi xomaxoneing ne en ingwei xel embei zipek eivek memiing o? En xel qou Laweeng Vambuing nambei ingwei xey a qou ne.”  
\v 48 Om moxo wong qayeeng nikanzek wou xel bei, “Xel a qou lipekeing eivek Yesu Kilisi lei.” Woyom xel teling wou Petele bei e toumendei is xel bouk valu. 
\c 11  
\s1 Petele neil xuk nimza wei wong o teyei 
\p  
\v 1 Xel sinale me liyeiw wei mindei lala eivek distrik Yudia eno ngo qayeeng tiyon bei, xel amba eno qou xoulek wei Anutu yo is ambei nyon.  
\v 2 De gyeik Petele la pu wei Yerusalem nei, xel betiyeing wo ninkanzek en kwa wei ghuweing ninavi veil o, om xel neil qayeeng lox me loum lek e,  
\v 3 de xel neil, “Wang la eivek xel moux wei se ghuw ninavi yo bend me ghe wa is xel.” 
\p  
\v 4 Woyom Petele neilteyei wou xel bombek en lul sapa wei belup o:  
\v 5 Moxo neil, “A mindei eivek beyeeng ngandoung wei Jopa nei me na mi zeimemang eno a manghalus pekwi me na xei. A xei lulti nambei qaeing ngandoung wei xel byex yis lek nenyawes vey eno tei lam anghei tyoung gheyapu, me lam wou ingwei a toundei ghei yo.  
\v 6 A xei la eivek lalei me na xei leliy wei vaxa vey wei tembuing o, a xei leliy leliy bemeeng, me leliy leliy wei mi yelek bambound o, me menek menek wei gheyapu yo.  
\v 7 Woyom a ngo vya ti neil wou ay, ‘Petele, qandi lek, leis leliy on me wa.’ 
\p  
\v 8 “A neil bei, ‘Ma, se teyei ti, Tambiy Ngandoung! Lul wei nilul o, me ingwei nilaxes o ti se mi lam eivek a myang ne.’ 
\p  
\v 9 “Ekom vya tine luk e loum anghei tyoung gheyapu nei luyuw no, ‘Wa se taxe lul wei Anutu wong e wo vako yon nilaxes.’  
\v 10 Tine belup luyal, de woyom lul dalus tiyon leklox me la tyoung gheyapu no. 
\p  
\v 11 “Lek bouk kayon bombek, eno moux yal wei lam anghei Sisalia eno lam nale ghei ingwei a toundei ghei yo.  
\v 12 Laweeng Vambuing neil wou ay bei, ‘Wa seng bounaleim ngenong en ingwei wa being na is xel o.’ Moux limti beimambei ne lindama eno lam is ay, me xa la eivek moux moxon beeng.  
\v 13 Moxo neil wou xa en ingwei yei angela ti eno lam tyip wou e eivek e beeng on me neil, ‘Wong xel la Jopa wou Simon tiwei xel mi taxe e bei Petele yo.  
\v 14 Moxo tyek na qou qayeeng me nak wou wang, de eivek qayeeng on eno wang me wa xe xel dalus wei xomek on eno tyek Anutu devind xam veil meyeing.’ 
\p  
\v 15 “Ka a di luk wou xel eno Laweeng Vambuing lam lek xel nambei ingwei lam lek xey myaxeeng o.  
\v 16 Woyom a wou naleind en vati wei Tambiy Ngandoung neil o: ‘Yoan lipek xomaxoneing en memiing, ekom tyek xam ghe zipek en Laweeng Vambuing.’  
\v 17 Om wangwei Anutu bong lul nimza ti wei teyeima nambei ingwei wong wou xe wei wongis Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu Kilisi, yond ay eti, a teyei bei paseisexe Anutu!” 
\p  
\v 18 Ka xel ngo qayeeng tine woy eno xel tip xel xe qayeeng lukeing lox me loum wouma dom sanghoxe Anutu me neil, “Woyom Anutu e zenghek lek xel amba bei xel pekwi xow me na qou mapieing.” 
\s1 Xel wongeingis wei Antiok o 
\p  
\v 19 Gweimbeeng xel wongeingis ngenong pek me vuwama lala en ingwei xel leis Setepan mey o, eno valu pek me la Ponisia, Saiprus me Antiok, eno xel di neil qayeeng wou Yudayeiw venaxow.  
\v 20 Ekom moux valu nanghei Saiprus me Sairini eno la Antiok me luk wou xel Grik is ambei nyon, me neil wou xel en Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu xe Xoulek Nimza.  
\v 21 Tambiy Ngandoung nikanzek toundei is xel, om xomaxoneing ngenong wongis me pekwi xow me loum wou Tambiy Ngandoung. 
\p  
\v 22 Qayeeng tine eno la eivek xel wongeingis anghei Yerusalem o nenyend, om xel wong Banabas la Antiok.  
\v 23 Ka moxo la tyip me yei Anutu xe lalei xeiles wei wo neing lek eno toundei is xel, om moxo wo xeilala me byexaxoun xel dalus bei xel a mi mendei is laleind tixemou wou Tambiy Ngandoung is laleind dalus.  
\v 24 Moxo yon moux nimza, wei pup en Laweeng Vambuing me e xe wongeingis eno wo nikanzek. Me xomaxoneing ngenong eno xel lam is xel wei Tambiy Ngandoung o.  
\v 25 Woyom Banabas la Tarsus me la yimexe Sol,  
\v 26 ka moxo yeiwou e, qou e me la Antiok. Lek vakovek qes tiyon dalus, Banabas aluw Sol dei is xel wongeingis me mi teyoxe xomaxoneing ngenongakes. Nanghei Antiok eno xel betiyeing qou leind Klisten ti myaxeeng o. 
\p  
\v 27 Eivek bouk tine eno xel poropet valu lam anghei Yerusalem me lam axo wei Antiok ne.  
\v 28 Xel poropet on ti, lei Agabus, nale ghey me eivek Laweeng Vambuing eno moxo neilteyei bei tyek maxep ngandoung nam wou xel me na teyei lek tembuing sapa wei Rom o. (Tine lam eivek bouk wei Klodias toundei king o.)  
\v 29 Xel betiyeing titi wong malew e teyei lek xel xe nikanzek, xel embei devind liyeiw wei toundei eivek Yudia nei.  
\v 30 Xel wong tine, me wong xel xe vineing me Banabas aluw Sol qou me la wou teivateiv wei Yerusalem o. 
\c 12  
\s1 Petele lam myayaing veil xomek xeitueing 
\p  
\v 1 Lek bouk ambei nye, king Herot zeimaxoun xel valu wei xel wongeingis o, en embei bo nol wou xel.  
\v 2 Moxo neil me xel wo nol wou Jems, inyon Yoan li moux, me leis e mey angya ngeyeing vevek.  
\v 3 Herot yei bei lul tiwei e wong ne wo nimza wou xel Yudayeiw mendghalus, om moxo di wong en embei zeimaxoun Petele is ambei nyon. Herot wong tine lek Bouk Wei Yaeing Belet Wei Yis Ma Veil o.  
\v 4 Ka xel zeimaxoun e, Herot toung moxo eivek xomek xeitueing, me wong e la eivek xel belimbo yon memend, xel belimbo yon qendu vey om xel embei qou e me na myayaing me bong qayeeng en e yanyateiv eivek xomaxoneing on mendghalus, loxyus en bouk wei Pasova yo. 
\p  
\v 5 Om xel di yei Petele teyei eivek xomek xeitueing, ekom xel wongeingis di zeimemend bei Anutu e devind Petele. 
\p  
\v 6 Boukeing nge wei la tax en ingwei Herot embei qou e me na eivek xomek wei zeimeing qayeeng o, eno Petele di yeip eivek xel vevek on yuw senghoing, xel tup en sen yuw, de vevekyeiw valu toungale zeyi xomek xeitueing on mya.  
\v 7 Se wo lululek en angela wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe eno lam tyip me xeiyaing tel la eivek xomek xeitueing on lalei. Angela byex mema lek e byek de piyexe e. Moxo neil, “Qandi lek Daing!” Dom sen kwax veil e mema. 
\p  
\v 8 Woyom angela neil wou e, “vex wa xe let vivekwou xow me byex vaxalambes lek.” Om Petele wong ambei e neil o. Angela neil wou e no, “Byex wa xe teimb ding de betiy ay.”  
\v 9 Petele betiwou e me la myayaing veil xeitueing, ekom moxo se woulek bei angela di wong tiyon neing ayang wou e, qe moxo embeik nge manghalus pekwi me yei.  
\v 10 Luw la ghanaw xomek mya tiwei tax o me la nge wei yuw o is xel belimbo yon dom lam wou tiwei mya aen wei la wou beyeeng ngandoung o. Xomek mya aen on venaxow tax en luw, dom luw la lox me la myayaing. Gyeik luw di tupwou sakwaing mema nayak on ti me la, se wou lululek en angela malang. 
\p  
\v 11 Woyom Petele mavindek lek de yeila me neil, “A se bou naleind ngenong en a woulek gweimbeeng bei Tambiy Ngandoung wong e xe angela lam zeim a veil Herot xe lalei vanei me veil lul dalus wei xomaxoneing wei Yudayeiw embei bong o.” 
\p  
\v 12 Ka e lu yeip yaing en tine, moxo la Maria beeng. Maria neu yon Yoan de e lei nge eno Malaka, nanghei inyon eno xomaxoneing ngenong qekuma me di zeimemend.  
\v 13 Petele leis mema lek qapomb tiwei myayaing o, me xukxe vex ti lei Roda lam en embei tax qapomb.  
\v 14 Ekom vexo woulek Petele vya, vexo wo xeilala mouyo, om veimya me lox dom se tax xomek mya qe lox me neil embei, “Petele toungale wou qapomb.”  
\v 15 Xel neil wou e, “Wang loung o.” Ekom vexo di wo lukendu lek me neil embei inye e yo, xel neil no, “Beind inyon e xe angela yo.”  
\v 16 Ekom Petele nanghei di leis mema lek qapomb, om xel tax qapomb me yei e, xel etek en e.  
\v 17 Om Petele pepeeng xel angya mema bei xel se baluk, qe e neilteyei wou xel en ingwei Tambiy Ngandoung qou e me lam myayaing veil xeitueing o woy, De moxo neil embei, “Xam aneil wou Jems me liyeiw en tine.” Woyom moxo la veil xel me la beyeeng nge. 
\p  
\v 18 De satiboukeing, eno xel vevekyeiw loung en Petele en mama, om xel etek me neil embei, “Petele la nya?”  
\v 19 Herot wo xuk lek Petele yimexeing ekom se yeiwou e, moxo lox me la wo telinyeing wou xel vevek me luk nikanzek bei xel a mey. 
\s1 Herot mey 
\p Woyom Herot la nanghei Yudia me la Sisalia me la dei inyon nayaka.  
\v 20 Herot wo veweeng ngandoung is xomaxoneing wei Taia me Saidon o. Om xel xouing toung lekti me lam yei e bei embo lalei vevopeing is xel, en nambei xel xe beyeeng ngandoung on mi qou vineing en yaeing lam eivek king Herot xe tembuing. Om xel luk is Blastus wei king xe xukxe me e lalei la is xel.  
\v 21 Lek bouk wei Herot beyal, eno moxo vunek en e xe teimb ding wei king o, me dei lek e xe siaking de wong qayeeng wou xomaxoneing sapa yon.  
\v 22 De woyom xel wei ngo qayeeng on taxe bei, “Vya tine inye anutu ti vya, se xomaxoneing ti vya.”  
\v 23 Om lutika eno angela wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe eno ti leis e, me meii ya e lalei lalei ma de mey en Herot se sanghoxe Anutu.  
\v 24 Ekom xoulek wei Anutu yon la wo ngandoung me la beyeeng tambak.  
\v 25 De Banabas aluw Sol wong luw xe xuk sinale ma, om luw loum veil Yerusalem me lox me la Antiok, de luw qou Yoan wei lei nge Malaka eno is xow. 
\c 13  
\s1 Xel wong Banabas aluw Sol la xuk sinale 
\p  
\v 1 Eivek kongrikesin wei Antiok eno inye xel poropet me xel putoung mi dei inyon eno xel leind ambei nye: Banabas, me Simion wei xel mi taxe e lei nge bei Ningak me Lusias wei Sairini, me Manain (e nipapu wei Herot seyap ngandoung o) me Sol.  
\v 2 Ka xel di wo lalo wou Tambiy Ngandoung me di vambu yaeing, Laweeng Vambuing neil wou xel bei, “Xam beyal Banabas aluw Sol wou ay en xuk tiwei a taxe luw en o.”  
\v 3 Om ka xel vambu yaeing me zeimemend, xel liw memend lek luw dom wong luw la. 
\s1 Sol aluw Banabas la neil xoulek eivek Saiprus 
\p  
\v 4 Laweeng Vambuing wong luw la xo wei beyeeng Selusia nei me qou sip nanghei inyon me la Saiprus, tembuing danghei tiwei di yeip eivek mamileeng o.  
\v 5 Luw la tyip Salamis, luw neil Anutu xe xoulek eivek xel Yudayeiw xe xomek qekueing ama. De Yoan mindei is luw nambei luw xe vineing. 
\p  
\v 6 Luw la tup eivek Saiprus tembuing nayak wei mi yeip eivek mamileeng on dalus dekakom luw la tyip beyeeng Papos. Nanghei inyon eno luw yei Yuda ti wei mi wo palak me e poropet wei tyonyeing o lei Ba-Yesu,  
\v 7 tambiy on mindei is lei ngandoung wei seyap o lei Segius Paulus, lei ngandoung wei seyap on lupeyei nimza om wong qayeeng la wou Banabas aluw Sol bei luw na neil Anutu xe xoulek en embei ngo.  
\v 8 Ekom Elimas on Ba-Yesu (en inye qes wei e lei eno nambei inye) tambiy wei wevek o eno mi pesek xuk wei luw o. En mi wong en embei pelipek seyap lei ngandoung lalei bei e se bongis Yesu.  
\v 9 Woyom Sol, e lei nge wei xel taxe eno Paulus, eno pup en Laweeng Vambuing, moxo yei Elimas kanzek dom neil,  
\v 10 “Wang on tambiy mapetok neu me wang mi wo vevek is lul dalus wei bombek o! Wang pup en lul nilul leimalei wei tyonyeing o. Gyeik inya ekom wa tip kwa wei wang mi pakei qayeeng neing wei Tambiy Ngandoung eno la wo qayeeng tyonyeing.  
\v 11 Ekom Tambiy Ngandoung mema wo vevek is wang. Wa mam on tyek na tuzeyi, me tyek wa seng gwei xeiyaing wei sayeiv o, qe tyek wa mendei nambei nyon enden ka.” 
\p Lutika eno laxap me mapetok lam beliv e manghalus, moxo la bandabanda, me di yimexe xel valu bei xel a zeim e mema me na.  
\v 12 Lei ngandoung wei seyap eno yei vati wei belup on, de moxo wongis, en nambei moxo etek en teyoxeing wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe yo. 
\s1 Paulus aluw Banabas la neil xoulek anghei Antiok wei toundei eivek tembuing danghei wei Pisidia nei 
\p  
\v 13 Nanghei Papos, Paulus me e xe xel nipapu la lek sip me la beyeeng Pelga eivek tembuing danghei wei Pampilia yo, dekakom Yoan lox veil xel me la Yerusalem.  
\v 14 Nanghei Pelga eno xel la beyeeng nayak Antiok wei tembuing danghei wei Pisidia nei. Lek bouk Sabat eno xel la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o me la dei.  
\v 15 Ka gyovaxa wei xomek qekueing ama eno pyaw qayeeng Petieing, me qayeeng Poropet ma woy, tambiy wei mi yeiteyei xomek qekueing ama eno wong qayeeng la wou xel, me neil, “Xam lingyeiw, wangwei xam mendi qou qayeeng wei embei ghandu xound xel xomaxoneing nei, on xam a neil.” 
\p  
\v 16 Paulus nale ghey de pepeeng xel angya mema, dom neil: “Xam moux wei Israel me xam ba wei ghe mi waleeng en Anutu yo, xam ngo wou a le!  
\v 17 Anutu tiwei Israel xe eno beyal xa bumiyeiw. Moxo wong Israelyeiw wo ngenong gyeik xel mindei eivek Izip o, moxo qou xel lam myayaing veil beyeeng tiyon nangya nikanzek ngandoung wei e yo.  
\v 18 Moxo mi qalei nimaying wei xel xe deing o teyei lek vakovek qes xoumeeng vey (40) eivek beyeeng bandaing on.  
\v 19 Ka Anutu semaleeng xomaxoneing velei lim yuw eivek Kenan, wong xel xe tembuing wou e xe xomaxoneing nambei xel xe lulul nimza.  
\v 20 Lul tine dalus eno qandi teyei lek vakovek qes 450. 
\p “Ka tine la veil eno Anutu beyal xel gyovaxa wei xel gyeiteyei xel Israel me ena tyip wou bouk wei poropet Samuel o.  
\v 21 Woyom xel moux alis vex teling en king ti, om Anutu wong Sol wei Kis neu moux eno wou xel, inyon velei wei Benyamin o, wei yeiteyei xel teyei lek vakovek qes xoumeeng vey (40).  
\v 22 Ka Anutu laluwexe Sol, moxo beyal Dawit wo xel xe king. Moxo neil e teyei wou xel: ‘A xeiwou Dawit wei Jesi neu moux wei a maxow laleing vind o. Moxo tyek bong lul tambak wei ambei e bong o.’ 
\p  
\v 23 “Om Anutu wong Yesu lam, inyon Dawit buyeiw ti, Tambiy wei vind xey veil nimaying eno wou xel Israel, nambei ingwei e neil zonghek o.  
\v 24 De gyeik Yesu se ghei lam, Yoan teyoxe xel en qayeeng wei pekwieing xow o me lipekeing eno wou xel Israel dalus.  
\v 25 Deka lam paviy ingwei Yoan wong e xe xuk ma, moxo neil, ‘Xam ghe wou naleimim bei ay eti? A se tambiy tiyon. Ma, ekom tyek moxo mendi nam yus en ay, e tiwei a se teyei bei tul yis veil e xe vaxalambes o.’ 
\p  
\v 26 “Xam lingyeiw wei Apraham neuyeiw, me xam ba wei ghe mi waleeng en Anutu yo, eno xam ngo. Qayeeng tiwei Yesu embei devind e xe moux alis vex veil meyeing eno Anutu wong e lam wou xey.  
\v 27 Xel xomaxoneing wei mindei eivek Yerusalem me xel xe gyovaxa eno se yeimend wou qayeeng wei xel poropet o, wei xel mi pyaw eivek Sabat titi yo. Qe, xel byex qayeeng lek Yesu me qayeeng wei poropet neil eno wo neing lek.  
\v 28 De xel se yeiwou sewokeing ti eivek e bei bo qayeeng en e me nyeis e mey, om xel teling Pailat bei e nyeis e mey.  
\v 29 Xel wong lul dalus wei xel poropet byex eivek qapiya en e yo woy, eno xel zewax e tei lam veil xax me liw e eivek eeng ti.  
\v 30 Ekom Anutu piyexe e qandi lek veil meyeing,  
\v 31 de bouk ngenong eno Yesu talex xow wou xel wei mi la is e eno la veil Galili me la Yerusalem. Gweimbeeng xel wei yeimawou eno neil Yesu teyei wou xa xe xomaxoneing. 
\p  
\v 32 “Xa neil Xoulek Nimza wou xam: En vati wei Anutu neil zonghek is xe bundyeiw o  
\v 33 moxo wong qayeeng wo neing lek en xey wei xel neundyeiw o, en piyexe Yesu qandi lek veil meyeing. Nambei ingwei xel byex eivek qapiya lalo tiwei yuw o bei: 
\q1 “‘Wang on a neung, 
\q2 gweimbeeng a wong ambei wa mam.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 2:7\rq* 
\m  
\v 34 Om Anutu piyexe e veil meyeing, de se teyei bei patal, om neil eivek qayeeng ti beimambei ne: 
\q1 “‘Tyek am bong mata wei vambuing me zonghek wei a neil wou Dawit eno wou xam.’ \rq Yesaya 55:3\rq* 
\m  
\v 35 Om moxo neil no eivek qapiya lalo nge nambei nye: 
\q1 “‘Tyek wa seng teyei bei bong wa xe tiwei vambuing eno daxe pataleing.’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 16:10\rq* 
\p  
\v 36 “Eivek bouk wei Dawit mi dei eno mi betiwou Anutu lalei. Deka moxo mey, xel ev is mayeiw me e neing patal.  
\v 37 Ekom e tiwei Anutu piyexe e veil meyeing eno se axe pataleing. 
\p  
\v 38 “Nambei nyon, xam lingyeiw, xa neil wou xam bei. Xam ghe boulek bei Yesu wei xa neil wou xam eno teyeimbei semaleeng sewokeing wei xam o.  
\v 39 Petieing wei Mose yo se teyei bei semaleeng xam xe sewokeing veil. Ekom wangwei xelti bongis Yesu yond Anutu semaleeng e xe sewokeing dalus de wong e wo bombek.  
\v 40 Om xam ghe gweiteyei xow en kandek lul wei poropet neil ne eno se nam atyip wou xam: 
\q1  
\v 41 “‘Wei, xam wei ghe mi wo vyamim wou Anutu xe qayeeng ne, 
\q2 eno tyek xam ghe detek me ghe bo nol, 
\q1 en tyek am bong lul tiwei tyek xam seng teyei bei bongis eno eivek xam senghoing 
\q2 de woyom wangwei xelti neil wou xam atax en inye nei, 
\q3 ond tyek xam seng bongis.’” \rq Habakuk 1:5\rq* 
\p  
\v 42 Ka Paulus aluw Banabas la veil xomek qekueing ama, xel xomaxoneing neil wou luw bei luw noum a neil qayeeng valu wou xel lek Sabat nge yus no.  
\v 43 Moux alis vex la myayaing veil xomek qekueing ama, eno xel Yudayeiw ngenong me xel amba wei mi betiwou kwa wei xel Yuda yo eno xel betiy Paulus aluw Banabas, de luw wo qayeeng wei e beil xel lundlek en xel ami mendei nikanzek eivek Anutu xe lalei xeiles. 
\p  
\v 44 Lek bouk Sabat nge yus eno xomaxoneing wei beyeeng ngandoung on valu beti qekuma me la ngo Tambiy Ngandoung xe qayeeng.  
\v 45 Gyeik xel Yudayeiw yei Xomaxoneing qendu ngandoung on, xel laleind wo nilul me lukyak lek Paulus en vati wei di neil o. 
\p  
\v 46 Woyom Paulus aluw Banabas luk nikanzek wou xel bei: “Xa bei neil Anutu xe qayeeng wou xam atax. Ekom xam ghe pesek me ghe toung demimim wou en xam ambei se qou mapieing luta luta, om xa pekwi me na la wou xel amba.  
\v 47 Inye vati wei Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou xa yo: 
\q1 “‘A wo wang wong ambei xeiyaing wei xel amba yo, 
\q2 en kandek wa devind xomaxoneing wei tembuing tambak veil meyeing.’” \rq Yesaya 49:6\rq* 
\p  
\v 48 Xel amba ngo tine, xel wo xeindlala me pamilexe Tambiy Ngandoung xe qayeeng. Me xel dalus wei Anutu beyal en mapieing luta luta eno wongis. 
\p  
\v 49 De Tambiy Ngandoung xe qayeeng on la wo tambak eivek tembuing danghei tiyon dalus.  
\v 50 Ekom Yudayeiw zeim xel vex wei leind tata wei mindei xeinghembi eivek Anutu me zeim xel gyovaxa wei beyeeng ngandoung on laleind lek. Om xel zeimaxoun Paulus aluw Banabas, me tiy luw la veil beyeeng ngandoung on.  
\v 51 Om luw pepa vegyuveeng veil vaxend bei xel on boulek bei xel wo sewokeing en kwa wei xel wong on, dom luw la veil Antiok me la beyeeng nayak Aikoniam.  
\v 52 De xel betiyeing eno pup en xeindlala me Laweeng Vambuing. 
\c 14  
\s1 Paulus aluw Banabas la neil xoulek eivek Aikoniam 
\p  
\v 1 Eivek beyeeng nayak Aikoniam, Paulus me Banabas wong ambei ingwei luw mi wong o, me la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei xel Yudayeiw o. Nanghei inyon eno luw neil xoulek wo nimza om xel ngenong wei Yudayeiw me xel amba eno wongis.  
\v 2 Ekom xel Yudayeiw wei mi pesek en embei se bongis eno zeim xel amba laleind lek me xel laleind wo nilul wou xel wei wongis o.  
\v 3 Om Paulus aluw Banabas dei enden ka eivek inyon, de luw se yaleeng en neileing qayeeng wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe lalei xeiles o, om Anutu wong ninkanzek wou luw me luw wong dee wei lulvako leimalei yo.  
\v 4 Xel xomaxoneing wei beyeeng ngandoung on dembuma la yuw, om xel valu la is Yudayeiw, de valu la is sinaleyeiw.  
\v 5 Woyom xel amba me Yudayeiw is xel xe gyovaxa tup qayeeng wouma bei bo nol wou Paulus aluw Banabas me banex luw a mey angya qakous.  
\v 6 Ekom luw woulek inyon, om luw pek me la eivek tembuing danghei wei Likonia eivek beyeeng nayak yuw wei Listra me Debi, me beyeeng beyeeng wei toundei paviy yo,  
\v 7 nanghei inyon eno luw lox me la neil Xoulek Nimza no. 
\s1 Paulus aluw Banabas la neil xoulek eivek Listra me Debi 
\p  
\v 8 Eivek Listra inyon tambiy ti mindei, eno vaxa bezomb gyeik ingwei umbek o, om moxo se mi ghavineeng.  
\v 9 Moxo mi ngo ingwei Paulus mi luk on, Paulus doma wou e, me yeimbei moxo wongis me e teyeimbei bo nimza lek.  
\v 10 Om Paulus taxe la bei, “Nale lek vaxam!” Woyom moux moxo nale ghey de tetyeik me la. 
\p  
\v 11 Xomaxoneing qendu ngandoung on yei vati wei Paulus wong on, om xel taxe la eivek Likonia vyend bei, “Anutu lam axone wou xey nambei xomaxoneing!”  
\v 12 Banabas, xel taxe e lei bei anutu Sus, me Paulus xel taxe bei anutu Helmes, en nambei e mi la tax en lukeing.  
\v 13 Xomek lalo wei anutu Sus eno toundei paviy tete mya wei beyeeng ngandoung on, om lumuki wei xomek lalo yon me xel xomaxoneing on qou manghaxo moux me palawa me la tete mya wei beyeeng ngandoung on en xel embei besei xound wou luw. 
\p  
\v 14 Ekom sinale Banabas aluw Paulus ngo tine, luw lex luw xe teimb dom veimyend me la senghoing eivek xel qendu yon me taxe bei:  
\v 15 “Xam moux, xam ghe di wong tine en va? Uw ne xomaxoneing is me xomaxoneing nambei xam. Uw a di qou Xoulek Nimza me na lam wou xam, om uw a neil wou xam bei xam pekwi xow veil lul nilul tine de ghe na wou Anutu mapieing, e tiwei toung tyoung aluw tembuing me mamileeng me lulul sapa wei toundei eivek o.  
\v 16 Eivek bouk wei takwei yo eno moxo wong xel tembuing dalus on betiwou xel venaxow xe sakwaing.  
\v 17 Ekom e venaxow se xupek en xomaxoneing bei xel se boulek e. Ma. Taxombouk eno moxo mi talex e xe kwa nimza wou xam. Moxo mi wong luing lam anghei tyoung eivek xam xe lulul wei xam ghe ev eivek xuk o, me moxo wong yaeing ngenong wou xam is me wong xam laleimim wo xeilala.”  
\v 18 Luw neil qayeeng tine wou xel, ekom xel wo nikanzek bei besei xound wou luw. Om luw neil nikanzek bei xel se besei xound wou luw. 
\p  
\v 19 Woyom Yudayeiw valu lam anghei Antiok me Aikoniam me zeim xel qendu yon laleind lek. Om xel nex Paulus angya qakous me tetei ela myayaing veil beyeeng ngandoung on, de xel embeik nge moxo mey.  
\v 20 Ekom ka xel betiyeing qekuma vivekwou e, de moxo qandi lek me lox me la eivek beyeeng ngandoung on. De yanyeing eno Paulus aluw Banabas la Debi. 
\s1 Luw loum Antiok eivek Siria 
\p  
\v 21 Luw neil Xoulek Nimza eivek beyeeng ngandoung tiyon me qou xel ngenong wo betiyeing. Woyom luw lox me la Listra, Aikoniam me Antiok,  
\v 22 me luw byexaxoun xel betiyeing laleind me neil qayeeng nikanzek wou xel bei, “Xam a mi mendei embo nikanzek eivek wongeingis me zonghek. Tyek xey a na eivek nimaying ngenong atax en kandek nana eivek tete lalei wei Anutu yo”.  
\v 23 Paulus aluw Banabas beyal xel gyovaxa eivek kongrikesin titi. De luw vambu yaeing me zeimemend, me toung xel la wou Tambiy Ngandoung, inyon eti yeiw wei wongis Tambiy Ngandoung o.  
\v 24 Ka luw la senghoing eivek tembuing danghei wei Pisidia, me la tyip eivek tembuing danghei wei Pampilia,  
\v 25 me luw la neil xoulek eivek beyeeng nayak Pelga, dekakom luw la xo wei beyeeng Atalia nei. 
\p  
\v 26 Nanghei Atalia luw la eivek sip me lox me la Antiok, inyon beyeeng wei xel wong luw la eivek lalei xeiles wei Anutu yo en xuk wei luw wong ema gweimbeeng ne yo.  
\v 27 Luw lam tyip inyon eno luw qeku xel kongrikesin lekti me wo qayeeng dalus wei Anutu wong wou luw me e tax xomek mya wei wongeingis eno wou xel amba yo.  
\v 28 De luw dei inyon enden ka is xel betiyeing. 
\c 15  
\s1 Xel kanzol qekuma nanghei Yerusalem 
\p  
\v 1 Xel moux valu lam axone veil Yudia me la Antiok me di teyoxe xel amba wei wongis o bei: “Wangwei xam se ghuw nimim navi nambei Mose xe kwa nei, on tyek Anutu se devind xam veil meyeing.”  
\v 2 Paulus me Banabas ngo qayeeng wei xel moux on neil o om luw wo vevek wou qayeeng is xel me vuk lek qayeeng is xel lox me loum. Om xel beyal Paulus me Banabas bei luw na is xel wongeingis valu, bei xel na pu Yerusalem nei me na gyei xel sinale me teivateiv en telinyeing tine.  
\v 3 De kongrikesin wong xel la, om xel la lox Ponisia me Samaria senghoing, me di neil wou xel en ingwei xel amba pekwi xow o. Qayeeng nimza tine wong xel wongeingis wo xeindlala.  
\v 4 Ka xel la tyip Yerusalem eno xel wongeingis me xel sinale me gyovaxa qou xel. De Paulus aluw Banabas neil wou xel en lul dalus wei Anutu wong wou xel nangya luw memend o. 
\p  
\v 5 Woyom xel Parisi valu wei wongis eno nale me neil, “Xel amba na mi ghuw ninavi me betiwou petieing wei Mose yo.” 
\p  
\v 6 De xel sinale me teivateiv qekuma bei menyex wou telinyeing tine.  
\v 7 Ka xel neil qayeeng ngenong woy, Petele nale ghey me neil wou xel: “Xam lingyeiw, xam ghe woulek bei takwei eno Anutu beyal ay eivek xam senghoing bei a neil Xoulek Nimza wou xel amba en xel a ngo dom bongis.  
\v 8 Anutu, tiwei woulek xomaxoneing dalus laleind eno talex wou xey bei lewexe lek xel me wong Laweeng Vambuing wou xel, nambei ingwei wong wou xey o.  
\v 9 Moxo se wong kwa nge wou xel de nge wou xey, qe wong xel laleind wo vako en ingwei xel wongis o.  
\v 10 Woyom nambei nya xam ambeing bo axeing wou Anutu gweimbeeng? Xam se toung pelang nimaying lek xel betiyeing kwend, beip inyon xey o xe bundyeiw se teyei bei qalei?  
\v 11 Ma! Xey a wongis bei, eivek lalei xeiles wei xe xe Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu eno Anutu vind xey a lam veil meyeing nambei ingwei vind xel on.” 
\p  
\v 12 Xel dalus wei qekuma eno deduingma, en nambei xel di ngo Banabas me Paulus di neil qayeeng wei Anutu wong dee me lulvako eivek xel amba senghoing nangya luw memend o.  
\v 13 Luw tip qayeeng eno Jems luk elekla bei: “Xam lingyeiw, xam ngo a xe qayeeng.  
\v 14 Simon neil wou xam en vati wei Anutu talex myaxeeng en ingwei mi wou naleind en xel amba yo, bei na qou xel xomaxoneing me xel bong ambei emaxow xe.  
\v 15 Me qayeeng wei xel poropet eno la teyei lek is ambei nyon, xel byex eyeip eivek xoulek bei, 
\q1  
\v 16 “ ‘Ka tine na veil eno tyek a noum me nam 
\q2 me na dev Dawit xe xomek sel no wei pek me teila veil o. 
\q1 Lulul wei xomek lelolexe eno tyek a menyex wou 
\q2 de na dev vako no, 
\q1  
\v 17 en kandek moux alis vex wei xel amba wei se Yuda eno gyimexe Tambiy Ngandoung, 
\q2 me xel amba dalus wei mi wongis a leing o, 
\q1 Tambiy Ngandoung neil embei. E venaxow wong lul tine qandi.’ 
\q2  
\v 18 Xel woulek inyon takwei qenang nei. \rq Amos 9:11-12\rq* 
\p  
\v 19 “Nambei nyon a xe woueing nalei bei, xe se teyei bei bong lulti bo pok en xel amba wei pekwi xow me loum wou Anutu yo.  
\v 20 Embong ondek xey a byex qapiya wou xel, me na neil wou xel bei xel se qou yaeing wei xel toung ambei da wou tenu bandaing o, me kwa nilul wei kwapesiv o, me leliy leyeis wei xel bembinexe e kwa yo de xel se gya leliy wei gyand o.  
\v 21 En eivek beyeeng ngandoung titi eivek bouk wei myaxeeng o xomaxoneing valu mi neil petieing wei Mose yo teyei de xel mi pyaw eivek xomek qekueing ama lek bouk wei Sabat o.” 
\s1 Xel wong qapiya la wou xel wongeingis wei xel amba yo 
\p  
\v 22 Woyom sinaleyeiw me teivateiv, is kongrikesin, xel embei beyal xel venaxow xe moux valu me bong xel na Antiok is Paulus me Banabas. Xel beyal Yudas (xel mi taxe lei nge bei Balsabas) me Silas, moux yuw on teiv eivek liyeiw senghoing.  
\v 23 Xel wong qapiya tine la is xel: 
\pmo Xa sinaleyeiw me teivateiv ne xam limimyeiw, 
\pmo xa byex qapiya ne lak wou xam wongeingis wei xel amba yo eivek Antiok, Siria me Silisia: 
\pmo Bendiyeing xam. 
\b  
\pm  
\v 24 Xa ngo bei xomaxoneing valu qandi eivek xa senghoing me lak wo nol wou xam laleimim is xel xe qayeeng me wong nimaying wou xam. Ekom xa se lenghek lek xel me wong xel lak wou xam.  
\v 25 Om xa dalus a toung laleimi lekti me na beyal xel valu me na wong xel lak wou xam is xa xe gweleeng Banabas me Paulus wei xa laleimi vind o,  
\v 26 moux yuw on teyeimbei saing luw xe mapieing en xe xe Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu Kilisi lei.  
\v 27 Nambei nyon xa wong Yudas aluw Silas lak wou xam, bei luw nak a neil qayeeng wei xa byex eno wou xam eivek luw venaxow myend.  
\v 28 Inye wo nimza wou Laweeng Vambuing me xa bei xa se toung nimaying lek xam. Qe xa neimbei xam a mi betiwou kwa valu nambei nye.  
\v 29 Xam mendei dingta veil yaeing wei xel toung ambei da wou tenu bandaing o. Xam seng gwa leliy is gyand, me xam se gwa leliy leyeis wei xel qo e kwa yo me xam pesek kwa nilul wei kwapesiv o. Tyek xam ghe bo nimza wangwei xam pesek lulti beimambei ne. Xam a mi mendei embo nimza. 
\p  
\v 30 Woyom xel wong moux ti beimambei yon la xo wei Antiok nei, de xel qeku moux alis vex wei xel wongeingis eno lekti me wong qapiya wei xel byex o wou xel.  
\v 31 Xomaxoneing pyaw qayeeng tiyon me xel wo xeindlala en ingwei xel qou qayeeng nimza wei embei devind me bong nikanzek wou xel o.  
\v 32 Yudas me Silas, luw venaxow on poropet. Om luw neil qayeeng ngenong bei devind me bong nikanzek wou liyeiw.  
\v 33-34 Ka luw la dei inyon bouk valu is xel woy, woyom liyeiw wong luw lox is mata wei lalei vevopeing bei luw nox wou xel wei wong luw lam o.  
\v 35 Ekom Paulus aluw Banabas nanghei toundei eivek Antiok, nanghei inyon eno luw me xel ngenong di teyoxe me neil qayeeng wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe yo. 
\s1 Paulus aluw Banabas dembuma 
\p  
\v 36 Bouk valu la veil woyom Paulus neil wou Banabas, “Uw ambei nox mena me na ghei lindyeiw eivek beyeeng on dalus wei xey a neil Tambiy Ngandoung xe qayeeng eivek o me nanghei bei xel toundei woy.”  
\v 37 Banabas embei Yoan wei xel mi taxe e lei nge bei Malaka, eno na is luw,  
\v 38 ekom Paulus wou kwa bei inye se nimza bei e qou Malaka, en nambei la veil luw anghei Pampilia me se lox me la wo xuk is luw no.  
\v 39 Luw pyalek ama niseikeing me dembuma om luw se wo xuk is ama no. Banabas qou Malaka de luw qou sip me la tembuing nayak Saiprus eivek mamileeng,  
\v 40 ekom Paulus beyal Silas me luw la, de liyeiw toung luw eivek lalei xeiles wei Tambiy Ngandoung o.  
\v 41 Moxo la eivek provins wei Siria me provins wei Silisia yo, me byexaxoun xel kongrikesin wei toundei inyon o. 
\c 16  
\s1 Timote la is Paulus aluw Silas 
\p  
\v 1 Paulus la beyeeng nayak Debi me la beyeeng nayak Listra is ambei nyon, nanghei inyon eno betiyeing ti lei Timote mindei inyon. Moxo ta yon Yuda vexo wei mi wongis o eno ti, de ma yon nanghei Grik.  
\v 2 Xel wongeingis wei Listra me Aikoniam eno mi luk en Timote bei, e tambiy nimza.  
\v 3 Paulus embei qou Timote me na dingta ti is e, om moxo ghuw e ninavi nambei kwa wei Yudayeiw o. En wounalei en Yudayeiw wei mindei eivek beyeeng beimambei yon o, en xel dalus woulek bei e ma yon Grik.  
\v 4 Ka xel la eivek beyeeng nge me la nge, eno xel wong qayeeng wei sinaleyeiw me teivateiv luklek me tup woy eivek Yerusalem eno wou xel, bei xomaxoneing dalus betiwou.  
\v 5 Om xel kongrikesin on xe wongeingis wo nikanzek me xel di nyouk taxombouk. 
\s1 Paulus mapekwi me yei Masedonia ti 
\p  
\v 6 Paulus me e xe xel wei mi wo xuk lekti eno la eivek tembuing danghei wei provins Esia nei, en nambei Laweeng Vambuing neil axound bei luw se neil qayeeng ti eivek Prigia me Galesia.  
\v 7 Ka xel la tyip wou tembuing danghei wei Misia, xel wong me yei en xel embei na eivek provins Bitinia, ekom Yesu xe Laweeng Vambuing peti xel bei xel se na inyon.  
\v 8 Om xel la senghoing eivek Misia de la xo beyeeng nayak Troas nei.  
\v 9 Eivek boukeing tiyon eno Paulus mapekwi me yei moux wei tembuing danghei wei Masedonia yo ti eno toukale me tay wou e, “Wang nam ingwei Masedonia ne me devind xa.”  
\v 10 Ka Paulus mapekwi me yei tine, xa xeiwou xow daing bei na Masedonia, xa woulek bei, Anutu taxe bei xa na neil e xe Xoulek Nimza wou xel nei. 
\s1 Lidia pekwi xow nanghei Pilipai 
\p  
\v 11 Nambei nyon, xa qou sip nanghei beyeeng nayak Troas me na la bombek wou Samotres eivek mamileeng, de yanyeing eno xa la Neapolis.  
\v 12 Nanghei inyon eno xa la Pilipai, wei xel Rom yeiteyei me dei lek takwei yo. Inyon beyeeng ngandoung wei tembuing danghei tiwei myaxeeng wei provins Masedonia yo. Om xa dei inyon bouk valu. 
\p  
\v 13 Lek bouk Sabat eno xa la myayaing veil tete mya wei beyeeng ngandoung on me na la ingwei memiing vi nei, wei xa woulek bei inye beyeeng wei xomaxoneing mi zeim memend anghei yo. Woyom xa dei tembuing me na luk wou xel vex wei qekuma nanghei inyon o.  
\v 14 Vex wei mindei inyon eno ti lei Lidia, ngo qayeeng tine me mi wo lalo wou Anutu. Vex on beeng qes Taiataira, me vexo mi wo xuk malew en qaeing wei mateyek o. Tambiy Ngandoung pekwi vex on lalei, om li nenya wou qayeeng wei Paulus di neil on.  
\v 15 Ka vex on me e xe xel wei xel xouing mindei eivek xomek on lipek, vexo neil embei, “wangwei xam ghe gwei bei a wongis Tambiy Ngandoung nei, ond xam ghe nam mendei eivek a bang.” Om vexo wo nikanzek en xa, me xa betiwou e xe qayeeng. 
\s1 Paulus aluw Silas la xeitueing 
\p  
\v 16 Bouk ti xa la beyeeng wei zeimeing mema yo, de vexawo xukxe bandaing ti lam pelong xa, laweeng ti mindei eivek e me mi yei me neil vati wei tyek nam loxyus o teyei. Vex on mi qou malew ngenong wou mayeiw en xuk wei mi wong on.  
\v 17 Vexawo tine eno mi betiwou Paulus me xa dalus, me mi taxe bei, “Xel moux dalus tine inye xukxe wei Anutu Nikanzekta wei Gheyapu nei. Xel mi neil wou xam en sakwaing wei embei devind xam veil meyeing o.”  
\v 18 Vex tine mi wong ambei nye teyei lek bouk tambak. Dekakom Paulus lalei wo myavanei om pekwi ma wou me neil niseikeing wou laweeng on, “A neil wou wang eivek Yesu Kilisi lei bei, lam myayaing veil vex on!” De lutika eno laweeng la veil vexo. 
\p  
\v 19 Ekom vexawo yon mayeiw yei bei sakwaing wei qoueing malew eno lati, om xel zeimaxoun Paulus aluw Silas me tetei luw me qou luw me la nale wou xel gyovaxa mend eivek beyeeng wei xel mi wo vateivek o.  
\v 20 Xel qou luw me la wou xel wei mi ngo qayeeng o me neil, “Moux yuw ne inye Yuda, luw di wo nol wou xe laleind eivek xe bend ne.  
\v 21 Me luw embei puw xey a na betiwou kwa valu wei xey a lax petieing zeyi bei xey wei Rom eno se bong o.” 
\p  
\v 22 Xel moux alis vex tendulekti, me byex qayeeng lek Paulus aluw Silas. Me xel wei mi ngo qayeeng eno luk nikanzek wou luw de kwax luw xe teimb veil dom sesa luw en beyei.  
\v 23 Ka xel wo nol wou luw woy, woyom xel toung luw la eivek xomek xeitueing, de wong qayeeng nikanzek wou tambiy wei mi yei xomek xeitueing teyei yo bei, emdi gyeiteyei luw bo nimza.  
\v 24 Tambiy on ngo petieing wei nge wei mi ngo qayeeng o, om toung luw eivek xeitueing tiwei laleiyang me tup luw vaxend eivek pelang. 
\p  
\v 25 Lek boukeing masenghoing eno Paulus me Silas di zeimemend me wong lalo wou Anutu, me xel valu wei xeitueing eno di ngo luw.  
\v 26 De lutika eno tembuing pi me xomek xeitueing on wo pimapi me mundeeng wei xomek xeitueing eno pi. Lutika eno qapomb wei xomek xeitueing on tax, me xel dalus xe sen tax.  
\v 27 Tambiy wei mi yei xomek xeitueing teyei eno qandi, me yei bei xomek xeitueing xe qapomb tax, om moxo puw e xe ngeyeing vevek dom embei nyeis venaxow en embeik nge xel wei la xeitueing eno pek me la.  
\v 28 Ekom Paulus taxe la wou moxo bei, “Wa seng bo nol wou xow! En xa dalus a toundei inye.” 
\p  
\v 29 Tambiy wei mi yei xomek xeitueing teyei eno taxe bei xel a qou nenyex tumeing me nam, moxo veimya me la lalei is etekeing me yaleeng de teila paviy Paulus me Silas vaxend.  
\v 30 Woyom moxo qou luw me la myayaing me teling, “Teiv amuw, tyek am bong ambei nya en kandek Anutu e qou a noum?” 
\p  
\v 31 Luw neil elox bei, “Wang bongis Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu, on tyek Anutu devind wang nam veil meyeing me wa xe xel wei xomek o is.”  
\v 32 Woyom luw neil qayeeng wei Tambiy Ngandoung o wou e me xel dalus wei e beeng o is.  
\v 33 Eivek boukeing masenghoing eno tambiy wei xomek xeitueing on qou luw me sekweyexe luw xe qatyex, woyom lutika eno moxo lis nipapu dalus qou lipekeing.  
\v 34 Tambiy wei xomek xeitueing eno qou luw me la eivek beeng me toung lul yaeing eno lam wou luw en moxo pup en xeilala en nambei xel wongis Anutu, e me nipapu dalus. 
\p  
\v 35 Satiboukeing eno tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng eno wong e xe xel belimbo la wou tambiy wei xomek xeitueing is qayeeng tine bei: “Wong tambiy yuw on la.”  
\v 36 Tambiy wei mi yei xomek xeitueing teyei eno neil wou Paulus bei, “Tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng eno neil embei wang me Silas ghe na. Muw ghe na is laleim vevopeing.” 
\p  
\v 37 Ekom Paulus neil wou lei ngandoung wei xosepu yon: “Uw ne moux wei Rom o. Nambei nya xel wei mi ngo qayeeng eno se ngo qayeeng wei uw eno wo nimza, me yei bei uw a wong sewokeing ti o ma? Ekom xel leis uw bandaing me toung uw eivek xomek xeitueing. Om gweimbeeng xel embei qou uw xupekeing? Ma! Wong xel venaxow lam qou uw me la myayaing.” 
\p  
\v 38 Lei ngandoung wei xosepu eno wong qayeeng tine wou tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng o, me xel ngo bei Paulus me Silas on Rom yuw, om xel yaleeng.  
\v 39 Woyom xel wei mi ngo qayeeng eno lam me beoux xow wou luw dom qou luw me la veil xomek xeitueing, de teling wou luw bei luw na veil beyeeng ngandoung on.  
\v 40 Ka Paulus aluw Silas lam myayaing veil xeitueing, luw la Lidia beeng, me la tyip wou liyeiw me byexaxoun xel en qayeeng valu, de woyom luw la. 
\c 17  
\s1 Paulus aluw Silas la neil xoulek eivek Tesalonika 
\p  
\v 1 Ka luw la eivek beeng nayak Ampipolis me beeng nayak Apolonia, luw la tyip beeng nayak Tesalonika, nanghei inyon eno xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o ti toukale.  
\v 2 Paulus la eivek xomek qekueing ama nambei e xe kwa wei mi wong o, me eivek Sabat yal eno mi luk is xel en qayeeng wei di yeip eivek Anutu xe qapiya yo.  
\v 3 Moxo mi neil Anutu xe qayeeng qes teyei me neil ambei nye, Kilisi tyek na qou myavanei ngandoung me na mey, dekakom tyek qandi lek veil meyeing. Moxo neil, “Yesu tiwei andi neilteyei wou xam ne, inye Kilisi.”  
\v 4 Xel valu wei Yuda eno wongis me betiwou Paulus aluw Silas, me Grik valu ngandoung wei mi wo lalo wou Anutu eno betiwou luw. Me vex ngenong wei leind tata eno betiwou luw is ambei nyon. 
\p  
\v 5 Ekom Yudayeiw qouwou luw, om xel qou xel wei nilul o valu nanghei ingwei beyeeng vateivek nei, me qeku xel ngenong is me xel wo nol wou beyeeng ngandoung tiyon. Xel veimyend me la wou Jeson xe xomek me la yimexe Paulus aluw Silas bei na qou luw me na myayaing wou xel qendu ngandoung on.  
\v 6 Ekom xel se yeiwou luw, om xel tetei Jeson is liyeiw valu me qou xel me la wou xel gyovaxa wei beyeeng on, dom taxe bei, “Moux tine mi wo kwa nol me ghavineeng e lala eivek tembuing sapa nei, om gweimbeeng ne xel lam inye,  
\v 7 me Jeson qou xel me la eivek beeng. Xel moux dalus tine mi pyalek Sisa xe qayeeng, me xel mi neil embei, king nge toundei, e lei Yesu”  
\v 8 Xel xomaxoneing is gyovaxa wei beyeeng nayak on ngo tine, eno xel tambak on etek ngandoung me di wo vyend lala.  
\v 9 Woyom xel wong Jeson me lei yeiw ba yon xouv xomek wei ngoeing qayeeng o dom wong xel la. 
\s1 Paulus aluw Silas la neil xoulek eivek Belia 
\p  
\v 10 Ka di wo mangamong en embei bouk, Paulus aluw Silas lindyeiw wong luw la beyeeng nayak Belia. Luw la tyip inyon, me xel la eivek Yudayeiw xe xomek qekueing ama.  
\v 11 Xel Yuda wei mindei Belia eno xel xe kwa yon nimza ghanaw Yudayeiw wei Tesalonika yo, en xel ngo qayeeng wei Paulus neil on me xel laleind vind, teyei lek bouk eno xel mi pyaw qayeeng wei yeip eivek qapiya vambuing o me yeimbei xoulek wei Paulus neil on zonghek, o ma.  
\v 12 Xel wei Yuda yon eno ngenong wongis, me Grik vex ngenong wei leitata yo, me moux wei Grik eno xouing wongis ambei nyon. 
\p  
\v 13 Ekom xel Yudayeiw wei mindei eivek Tesalonika woulek bei Paulus di neil qayeeng wei Anutu xe yo eivek Belia, om xel la inyon is, me zeim moux alis vex on laleind lek me wong xel dalus etek mouyo.  
\v 14 Woyom xel lindyeiw wo daing me wong Paulus la xo mamileeng vi nei, ekom Silas aluw Timote nanghei toundei Belia.  
\v 15 Xel moux wei la is Paulus eno qou e me la beyeeng nayak Atens, de woyom Paulus wong qayeeng wou xel bei xel a neil wou Silas aluw Timote bei luw na wou e daing. 
\s1 Paulus neil xoulek eivek Atens 
\p  
\v 16 Ka Paulus di axe luw anghei Atens, moxo yei beyeeng ngandoung on pup en anutu tyonyeing ngenong. Om wong e lalei wo maying.  
\v 17 Om moxo la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei xel Yudayeiw o me luk is Yudayeiw me xel amba wei mi wo lalo wou Anutu yo. De lek bouk titi moxo mi la beyeeng vateivek me luk is moux alis vex wei lam mindei inyon o.  
\v 18 Xel moux wei lundpeyei nimza wei Epikurian me xel wei Stoik, eno wo veweeng is e en qayeeng. Xel valu teling, “Tambiy tiwei mi luk bandabanda nei embei neil va?” Om xel valu neil, “Beind moxo di neil qayeeng en anutuyeiw wei beyeeng bamba yo.” Xel neil tine en nambei Paulus di neil Xoulek Nimza en Yesu wei qandi lek veil meyeing o.  
\v 19 Woyom xel qou Paulus me la qekueing ama wei xel kanzol lek lukendu Areopagus, nanghei inyon eno xel neil wou e, “Teyei bei xa ngo qayeeng vako tiwei wang di teyoxe me ghe wong elam ne?  
\v 20 Wang wong qayeeng bange valu lam eivek xa nenyami, om xa bei ngo bei qayeeng tine qes ambei nya.”  
\v 21 (De xel Atensyeiw dalus me xel amba wei mindei inyon eno se mi wo lulti qe xel mindei bandaing me mi luk en lulvako wei xel ngo yo.) 
\p  
\v 22 Woyom Paulus nale ghey eivek qekueing ama wei xel kanzol lek lukendu Areopagus me neil: “Xam moux wei Atens! A xei xam ghe wo nimkanzek en wongeingis kwa leimalei wei lalo yo.  
\v 23 En nambei a la ghavinenyeing me na xei e wo nimza me na xei lul wei xam ghe mi wong lalo wou yo. Me a xei qeind ti xel byex qayeeng lek ambei nye: E NA WOU ANUTU TI WEI XA SE WOULEK O. Om Anutu tiwei xam seng woulek on xam ghe mi wo lalo bandaing wou e, om gweimbeeng ambei neil e xe qayeeng wou xam. 
\p  
\v 24 “Anutu tiwei toung tembuing me lulul dalus eivek o, inyon Tambiy Ngandoung wei tyoung aluw tembuing, me se mindei eivek xomek vambuing wei xel ev angya memend o.  
\v 25 Me se mi qou vineing en lul wei xomaxoneing wong angya memend o, me se teyei bei qou lulti, en nambei e maxow wong mapieing me laweeng wou xomaxoneing me lulul dalusateiv.  
\v 26 Eivek bu tixemou ne eno e toung xomaxoneing lam dei lek tembuing sapa, en kandek xel a mi gyeiteyei tembuing tambak, e maxow beyal bouk wei xel a mi mendei yo, me e maxow lax enghek wei xel xe tembuing o.  
\v 27 Anutu wong ambei nye en kandek xomaxoneing gyimexe e me nam wou me boulek e zonghek en nambei se dei dingta veil xey.  
\v 28 ‘En eivek Anutu eno xey a wo xomaxoneing me na toundei mapieing me na mi la me na loum me na dei lek tembuing.’ Nambei xam venaxow xe xel valu wei lupeyei eno neil embei, ‘Xe ne Anutu neuyeiw.’ 
\p  
\v 29 “Nambei nyon xey a toundei nambei Anutu neuyeiw, om xey se bou naleind bei Anutu yon nambei ghol me silva me qakous, me xe se bou naleind bei e yon tenu bandaing wei xomaxoneing wong angya venaxow memend me lundpeyei wei xe venaxow o.  
\v 30 Takwei eno xomaxoneing lundpeyei ma, om Anutu se neil qayeeng ti en vati wei xel mi wong o. Ekom gweimbeeng ne neil qayeeng nikanzek wou xomaxoneing dalus lek tembuing sapa bei xel pekwi xow.  
\v 31 En e maxow lax bouk wei embei tyek bong qayeeng en xomaxoneing dalus wei tembuing o, om beyal tambiy ti woy. Tambiy tine eno mey ekom Anutu piyexe e qandi lek veil meyeing.” 
\p  
\v 32 Xel ngo Paulus neil qayeeng en xomaxoneing qandi lek veil meyeing, xel valu luk seloukeing lek e, ekom xel valu neil embei, “Xa bei ngo qayeeng valu en lul tine no.”  
\v 33 Dekalekom, Paulus la veil xel kanzol.  
\v 34 Xel moux valu betiwou Paulus me wongis. Ti lei Dionisius, e kanzol wei xel mi qekuma lek lukendu Areopagus, me vex nge is ambei nyon e lei Damaris, me xomaxoneing valu beti wongis. 
\c 18  
\s1 Paulus neil xoulek eivek Korin 
\p  
\v 1 Kalekom, Paulus la veil Atens me la beyeeng nayak Korin.  
\v 2 Nanghei inyon eno moxo la tyip wou Yuda ti, e lei Akwila. Tambiy on beeng qes anghei Pontus, e tiwei lam anghei Itali is venei Prisila yo, en nambei Klodias wo qayeeng wou Yudayeiw dalus bei xel na veil Rom. Om Paulus la en embei gyei xel,  
\v 3 Paulus mi dei me wo xuk is xel, en nambei Paulus, Akwila, Prisila, lal xouing mi wo xuk wei duweing sel o.  
\v 4 Lek bouk tambak wei Sabat eno Paulus mi la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o, me neil qayeeng lumama wou Yudayeiw me xel Grik bei em beil xel lundlek. 
\p  
\v 5 Woyom Silas aluw Timote lam anghei Masedonia, Paulus neil Anutu xe xoulek wou xel Yudayeiw teyei lek bouk tambak me neil wou xel bei Yesu yon Kilisi.  
\v 6 Ekom Yudayeiw se ngo e qe xel pesek e me lukyak lek moxo. Om Paulus pepa vegyuveeng veil e xe teimb me neil wou xel, “Wangwei xam a qou nilul, ond inyon di yeip wou xam venaxow, nimaying on se wou ay. Gweimbeeng ne tyek a na neil xoulek wou xel amba.” 
\p  
\v 7 Woyom Paulus la veil xomek qekueing ama me la eivek xomek wei Titius Jastus wei xel amba yo eno nale paviy xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o, tambiy yon mi wong lalo wou Anutu.  
\v 8 Klispas on gyovaxa wei xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o. E is venei neu dalus mi wongis Tambiy Ngandoung, me xel ngenong wei Korin eno ngo Paulus xe qayeeng me wongis de lipek. 
\p  
\v 9 Boukeing ti eno Tambiy Ngandoung luk wou Paulus eivek ingwei mapekwi yo me neil: “Wa seng gwaleeng qe wa toumbale ding lek lukeing, de wa se mendei kanzek.  
\v 10 En a toundei is wang, om xelti se teyei bei zeim wang me bo nol wou wang, en nambei a xe xel ngenong toundei eivek beyeeng ngandoung tine.”  
\v 11 Om Paulus toundei eivek Korin teyei lek vakovek qes ti me ela dentouk limti, me teyoxe Anutu xe xoulek wou xel. 
\p  
\v 12 Ka Galio wo lei ngandoung wei seyap en provins Akaya, xel Yudayeiw qeku lekti me wo vevek is Paulus me qou e me la wong qayeeng en e.  
\v 13 Xel wong qayeeng en e me neil, “Tambiy tine, mi teyoxe wou xomaxoneing bei xel se bongis petieing qe xel bong lalo wou Anutu en sakwaing ba.” 
\p  
\v 14 Ka Paulus embim a neil qayeeng nox wou xel, ekom Galio pekwi me neil wou xel Yudayeiw bei, “Wangwei tambiy tine qayil petieing o bo sewokeing ti wou xam, ond a teyeimbei ngo qayeeng wei xam o.  
\v 15 Ekom xam ghe di pyanaleimim en qayeeng me leimim me xam venaxow xe petieing, om xam ghe lam wou ay. A se teyei bei ngo qayeeng en lulul ambei nyon, om xam venaxow menyex wou qayeeng ne.”  
\v 16 Om moxo wong xel loum myayaing veil wongeing qayeeng.  
\v 17 De xel zeimaxoun Sostenes inyon gyovaxa wei xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o, me xel leis e paviy xomek wei ngoeing qayeeng o. Ekom Galio mou se di wounalei en lul ambei nyon. 
\s1 Paulus lox me la Antiok wei distrik Siria 
\p  
\v 18 Paulus toundei eivek Korin teyei lek bouk matika. Dekalekom moxo ghanaw liyeiw dom qou sip me la provins Siria, Akwila luw venei Prisila la is e. Ka xel embei na, moxo qateiv luvelus veil nanghei beyeeng nayak Senklia en nambei tup qayeeng ti is Anutu.  
\v 19 Xel la tyip beyeeng nayak Epeses, nanghei inyon eno Paulus ghanaw Prisila luw Akwila. De e maxow la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o me neil qayeeng wou xel.  
\v 20 Xel teling wou bei e toumendei bouk valu is xel, ekom moxo pesek.  
\v 21 Ekom ka e la, moxo neil wou xel, “Wangwei Anutu lalei devind nei ond tyek a noum wou xam.” Woyom moxo qou sip me la veil Epeses.  
\v 22 Moxo la tyip Sisalia, dekakom moxo la pu wei Yerusalem nei me la neil bendiyeing wou xel kongrikesin on woy om la xo wei Antiok nei. 
\p  
\v 23 Paulus la dei Antiok bouk valu, dekalekom qandi nanghei inyon me la beyeeng nge me la nge teyei lek tembuing danghei wei Galesia yon me Prigia, me byexaxoun xel betiyeing en qayeeng. 
\p  
\v 24 Dekakom Yuda ti lei Apolos, tambiy wei beeng Aleksandlia, eno lam dei Epeses. Tambiy on mi luk qayeeng nimza, me moxo mi woulek e wo nimza en Anutu xe qayeeng wei di yeip eivek qapiya yo.  
\v 25 Xel teyoxe e woy en sakwaing wei Tambiy Ngandoung o, me e luk is nikanzek me mi neil wou moux alis vex en Yesu bombek, ekom moxo woulek lipekeing wei Yoan o.  
\v 26 Moxo neil qayeeng nikanzek eivek xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o. De Prisila me Akwila ngo e, luw qou e me la xomek wei luw o me neil sakwaing wei Anutu yo en Yesu wou e en kandek moxo boulek embo nimza. 
\p  
\v 27 Ka Apolos embei na Akaya, liyeiw wei mi dei Epeses eno byexaxoun e en qayeeng. Me byex qapiya wou xel betiyeing wei Akaya bei xel a qou e. Gyeik e la tyip inyon eno moxo wong vineing ngandoung wou eti yeiw wei Anutu wong lalei xeiles wou xel me xel wongis o.  
\v 28 Moxo wo nikanzek lek qayeeng neileing bei pelipek Yudayeiw nind qayeeng wou xomaxoneing mendghalus. Moxo neil xoulek eivek Anutu xe qapiya me talex e yeip yaing bei Yesu yon Kilisi. 
\c 19  
\s1 Paulus neil xoulek eivek Epeses 
\p  
\v 1 Ka Apolos toundei eivek Korin, Paulus la ghavineng eivek beyeeng wei toundei lek lukendu nei dekakom la tyip Epeses. Nanghei inyon eno moxo la tyip wou xel betiyeing valu  
\v 2 me teling wou xel, “Beip xam ghe qou Laweeng Vambuing gyeik xam ghe wongis o?” Xel lenghek bei, “Ma yo, xa se ngo bei inyon Laweeng Vambuing ti toundei.” 
\p  
\v 3 Om Paulus teling, “Woyom xam ghe qou lipekeing vati?” 
\p Xel neil, “Yoan xe lipekeing.” 
\p  
\v 4 De Paulus neil embei, “Yoan xe lipekeing on lipekeing wei pekwieing xow o. Moxo neil wou xel xomaxoneing on bei xel bongis tambiy tiwei di lam yus en e yo, inyon Yesu.”  
\v 5 Ka xel ngo qayeeng tine, xel qou lipekeing eivek Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu lei.  
\v 6 Woyom Paulus li mema lek xel, me Laweeng Vambuing lam lek xel, de xel neil qayeeng eivek vya leimalei me neil qayeeng poropet.  
\v 7 Xel moux dalus tiyon teyei lek xoumeeng yuw. 
\p  
\v 8 Om Paulus la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o me neil qayeeng nikanzek nanghei inyon teyei lek dentouk qes yal, moxo luk is nikanzek wou xel me veil xel lundlek en lul dalus wei Anutu xe tete lalei yo.  
\v 9 Ekom xel valu laleind wo nikanzek, om xel se wongis, me eivek xomexomek mendghalus eno xel neil qayeeng nol lek Sakwaing Tiyon. Om Paulus qou xel betiyeing me la veil xomek qekueing ama, de taxombouk eno moxo mi luk wou xel eivek Tiranus xe xomek wei teyoxeing o.  
\v 10 Moxo mi wong ambei nye teyei lek vakovek qes yuw, en kandek Yudayeiw dalus me xel Grik dalus wei mindei eivek provins Esia eno na ngo Tambiy Ngandoung xe qayeeng. 
\p  
\v 11 Anutu wong lulvako leimalei wei nikanzek eno nangya Paulus mema,  
\v 12 om xel moux alis vex mi qou angesip me qaeing myasepu wei Paulus axlek o, dekakom xel mi qou me la toung lek xel wei vanei wong xel o, dom vanei wei xel eno ma, me laweeng nol eno la veil xel is ambei nyon. 
\p  
\v 13 Xel Yuda valu wei mi la ghavinenyeing me tiy laweeng nol. Xel valu wong en embei neil Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu lei, me na tiy laweeng nol veil xel moux alis vex. Xel mi neil ambei nye, “Eivek Yesu lei, e tiwei Paulus mi neil e xe qayeeng o, a neil nikanzek wou wang bei lam myayaing.”  
\v 14 Lumuki leitata wei Yudayeiw o ti lei Skeva eno neu moux lim yuw, eno xel mi wo kwa tine wou laweeng nilul.  
\v 15 Bouk ti, eno laweeng nol neil elox wou xel, “A woulek Yesu, me a woulek Paulus, ekom xam on eti yeiw?”  
\v 16 Woyom tambiy tiwei laweeng nol mindei eivek eno vyeip lek xel me leis xel dalus. Moxo leis xel on wo nol ayang, omva xel pek veil xomek on me la xeind touk is gyand. 
\p  
\v 17 Yudayeiw dalus me xel Grik wei mindei eivek Epeses eno ngo tine, om xel yaleeng ngandoung mouyo, om xel sanghoxe Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu lei.  
\v 18 Xel ngenongakes wei wongis woy, eno lam wou xel moux alis vex ba yon mendghalus, me neil xel xe sewokeing wei xel mi wong takwei eno teyei.  
\v 19 Moux alis vex ngenong wei mi wo wevek me palak, eno qekuwou qapiya yon me lam sei lek nenyex eivek xel moux alis vex on mendghalus. Xel pyaw memend wou qapiya wei xel xouv eno teyei lek 50,000 malew selewa.  
\v 20 Eivek sakwaing ambei nye eno Tambiy Ngandoung xe qayeeng wo ngandoung me vula wo tambak is nikanzek. 
\p  
\v 21 Ka lul dalus tine tyip woy, Laweeng Vambuing wo kwa wou Paulus bei e na Masedonia me Akaya dekakom na Yerusalem. Om moxo neil, “Kalekom a na Rom is ambei nyon.”  
\v 22 Woyom ka moxo wong e xe vineing aluw, Timote me Elastus la Masedonia, dom e maxow toundei eivek provins wei Esia nei me e den nayaka. 
\s1 Nanghei Epeses eno xel luk nol lek Paulus 
\p  
\v 23 Lek bouk kayon eno xel valu wong vevek en qayeeng zeyi Sakwaing Tiyon.  
\v 24 Moux ti mindei, e lei Demitrius, tambiy on mi yeiwou lulul angya silva me yeiwou tenu nayak nayak teyei lek ambei xomek lalo wei anutu vex Atemis nangya silva, moxo se mi qou malew nayaka lek xuk wei mi wong on.  
\v 25 Moxo qeku xel xouing lekti, is xel wei mi wong xuk bange yo, me neil: “Xam moux, xam ghe boulek bei xey a mi qou malew wo nimza en xuk tiwei xey a di wong ne.  
\v 26 Me xam ghe wei me ghe ngo Paulus tiwei di wong me puw xomaxoneing ngenong eivek Epeses nei me pelipek xel laleind, de se eivek Epeses venaxow, qe paviy embim na eivek tembuing dalus wei provins Esia yo is. Me neil embei, ‘Anutu wei xey a wong angya memend ne se anutu zonghek.’  
\v 27 Qayeeng tiwei Paulus di neil ne teyei bei bo xe xe xuk vateivek ne lei bo nol. Me lul nge is ambei nyon, qayeeng wei e ne tyek teyeimbei bong xomek qekueing ama wei anutu vex Atemis o bong ambei lul bandaing eivek woueing nalei wei xomaxoneing o, me takwei eno xomaxoneing wei provins Esia me tembuing sapa wei xel mi wo lalo wou anutu vex tine yo. Ekom qayeeng wei Paulus eno embei semaleeng lei laeing wei e yo.” 
\p  
\v 28 Xel ngo qayeeng tine, eno xel laleind wo myavanei me taxe bei, “Atemis anutu wei Epeses, vex on lei laeing!”  
\v 29 Beyeeng ngandoung on dalus wo nindenduing ngenong, me xomaxoneing dalus on zeimaxoun Gaius me Alistakas me veimyend me la beyeeng wei qekueing ama yo. Tambiy yuw on nanghei Masedonia eno luw mi ghavineng is Paulus.  
\v 30 Paulus venaxow embei na senghoing is moux alis vex on, ekom xel betiyeing neil axound bei e se na.  
\v 31 Xel seyap valu nanghei Esia yon Paulus xe gweleeng, om xel wong qayeeng la wou Paulus bei, e se na eivek beyeeng wei qekueing ama yon. 
\p  
\v 32 Xel xomaxoneing dalus on lundpeyei yon la bandabanda. Xel valu di taxe lul nge de valu di taxe lul bange. Xel ngenong on se woulek bei xel di qekuma en vati.  
\v 33 Xel Yudayeiw tendu Aleksanda la mya nei wou xomaxoneing on mendghalus, xel valu wei toungale yon yei me neil embei, tambiy kawei sewokeing qes o inyon. Om Aleksanda embei neil qayeeng nox wou xel om pepeeng xel angya mema bei xel se baluk.  
\v 34 Ekom xel yei bei e yon tambiy wei Yuda yo ti, om moux alis vex on dalus ghak niseikeing teyei lek seivma yuw me neil embei, “Atemis wei Epeses ne lei yon ngandoung!” 
\p  
\v 35 Kuskus wei beyeeng ngandoung Epeses on pepeeng moux alis vex on bei xel denduing ama de neil: “Xam moux wei Epeses on ngo, xomaxoneing eti se woulek bei Epeses ne beyeeng wei yeingteyei xomek wei anutu vex Atemis o, me yeiteyei qakous vambueing tiwei tei lam anghei tyoung o?  
\v 36 Xomaxoneing ti se teyei bei pyalek qayeeng tine, nambei nyon xam deduingma, xam seng bo daing me ghe bong lulti.  
\v 37 Xam ghe qou tambiy yuw ne me ghe lam inye, ekom luw se panax lulti eivek xomek lalo, o lukyak lek xe xe anutu vex.  
\v 38 Woyom wangwei Demitrius me e xe xel xukxe eno xe qayeeng ti wou tambiy ti, ond bouk wei ngoeing qayeeng o di yeip. Me xel seyap toundei, bei xel menyex wou xel xe qayeeng.  
\v 39 Ek wangwei xam xe qayeeng valu nanghei, ond xam ghe nyeis inyon a mey eivek xel wei qekuma yon.  
\v 40 A neil ambei nyon en xey a toundei eivek nimaying ngandoung om seyap wei Rom eno teyei bei bo qayeeng en xey, en kwa wei xey a wong gweimbeeng ne eno qes ma. De wangwei xel teling xey bei xey a lam qekuma me na ghak enva, on tyek xey se teyei bei neil qayeeng ti nox.”  
\v 41 Ka kuskus neil qayeeng tine woy, moxo wong xel xomaxoneing on la. 
\c 20  
\s1 Paulus la Masedonia me Grik 
\p  
\v 1 Ka lukeing ngenong wei xomaxoneing on ma, Paulus taxe xel betiyeing qeku lam wou e me luk is xel. Woyom moxo neil qayeeng xeilala wou xel woy, me puw xel memend dom la Masedonia.  
\v 2 Moxo la ghavineeng eivek danghei tiyon, me wo qayeeng ngenong wou xomaxoneing bei na byexaxoun xel, de woyom la Grik wei xel mi taxe bei provins Akaya is ambei nyon,  
\v 3 moxo dei nanghei inyon teyei lek dentouk qes yal. Dekakom Yudayeiw tup qayeeng lekti, bei nyeis e gyeik ingwei embei na Siria yo, om moxo embei nox me na Masedonia.  
\v 4 Tambiy wei beyeeng Belia, inyon Sopata, Pilas neu moux, Alistakas me Sekandas on lam anghei Tesalonika, Gaius nanghei Debi, Timote is ambei nyon, me Tikikas me Tlopimas nanghei provins Esia nei.  
\v 5 Xel moux ti beimambei yon la tax en xa me di axe xa nanghei Troas.  
\v 6 Ka bouk wei Yaeing Belet Wei Yis Ma Veil o, eno xa qou sip me na la veil Pilipai, deka bouk lim la veil eno xa la wou xel wei la Troas atax o, me nanghei inyon eno xa dei teyei lek bouk lim yuw. 
\s1 Paulus piyexe Yutikus veil meyeing nanghei Troas 
\p  
\v 7 Lek bouk ti tax wei Sounda yo xa xouing a lam qekuma lekti bei dembu belet me na gha pasa. Paulus luk wou xel xomaxoneing on en nambei moxo tyek na veil xel lek bouk yanyeing, om moxo di puw qayeeng me ela boukeing masenghoing.  
\v 8 Inyon lam ngenong di tum eivek xomek lalei tiwei gheyapu yo, nanghei ingwei xa di qekuma yo.  
\v 9 De yak ghavis ti toundei paviy xomek mya nayak wei qoueing laweeng o e lei Yutikus, Paulus di puw qayeeng ngenong om moxo ma yeip me nalei maxow. Dekakom moxo oing me teila tembuing nanghei xomek lalei tiwei yal o, om xel la zeim e lek ekom moxo mey.  
\v 10 Paulus la xonei, me yeip lek ghavis on neing, de zeim e mema me neil, “Xam seng detek ti, moxo nanghei di pi yo!”  
\v 11 Woyom moxo lox me la gheyapu nei de dembu belet me ya is moux alis vex. Dekakom moxo mi luk me ela woyaing, om moxo la.  
\v 12 Yak ghavis on toundei mapieing, me xomaxoneing on qou me la beyeeng de xel laleind wo nimza. 
\s1 Paulus la veil Troas me la Miletus 
\p  
\v 13 Xa la eivek sip me na la beyeeng nayak Asos, me na di axe Paulus anghei Asos, e maxow neimbei xa na tax, en embei na vaxa.  
\v 14 De moxo la tyip wou xa ghei Asos, om xa qou e lam lek sip me xa xouing a la beyeeng Mitilini.  
\v 15 Yanyeing eno xa la eivek sip anghei inyon me na la tyip tembuing nayak Kios eivek mamileeng. De yanyeing nge eno xa la liveil me na teila tembuing nayak Samos eivek mamileeng, de yanyeing nge eno xa la tyip beyeeng nayak Miletus.  
\v 16 Paulus wou eivek nalei woy me qou sip me ghanaw Epeses en embei se mendei enden eivek provins Esia, qe embei na daing me na Yerusalem, wangwei e teyei nei, ond embei gyei bouk wei Pentikos o nanghei Yerusalem. 
\p  
\v 17 Nanghei Miletus, Paulus wong qayeeng la wou teivateiv wei kongrikesin wei Epeses bei xel nam wou e.  
\v 18 Xel la tyip woy, woyom moxo neil wou xel, “Xam ghe woulek kwa wei a mi wong gyeik a mindei is xam taxombouk o, myaxeeng wei a lam wou xam eivek provins Esia yo.  
\v 19 A mi wong Tambiy Ngandoung xe xuk me na mi beoux xow is mang louk, de na mi qalei nimaying wei Yudayeiw mi wong wou ay yo.  
\v 20 Xam ghe woulek bei a se xaleeng qe a mi neil qayeeng nimza wei embei devind xam o, me na mi teyoxe xam eivek beyeeng senghoing me na la xomek titi is me na teyoxe xam.  
\v 21 A mi neil e yeip yaing wou Yudayeiw me Grikyeiw bei xel pekwi xow me noum wou Anutu me bongis xe xe Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu. 
\p  
\v 22 “Me gweimbeeng, Laweeng Vambuing neil wou ay bei a na Yerusalem, de a se woulek vati wei embei balwou ay anghei inyei yo.  
\v 23 Ekom a woulek bei eivek beyeeng ngandoung sapa yon eno Laweeng Vambuing peti ay, bei tyek a balwou nimaying ngenong de xel a toung a na eivek xeitueing.  
\v 24 Ekom a se axe bei mapieing wei ay eno inyei lul nimza ti qe inye bandaing, en kandek a bong xuk pok me xuk wei Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu wong wou ay eno ema bole. Me na bong xuk tiwei neileing Anutu xe Xoulek Nimza wei lalei xeiles o. 
\p  
\v 25 “De gweimbeeng a woulek bei xam wei a neil qayeeng qes wei tete lalei wou xam o eno tyek xam seng nox me na gwei a manghalus no.  
\v 26 Nambei nyon, a neil e gyeip yaing wou xam gweimbeeng ne bei wangwei xel ti qou myaveweeng wei meyeing luta yo, on inye a se wong esewok.  
\v 27 En nambei Anutu xe qayeeng qes wei xam a being boulek, eno a se axvun.  
\v 28 Xam ghe gwei xow teyei, me moux alis vex dalus wei Laweeng Vambuing wong wou xam bei xam ghe gweiteyei yo, xam on Anutu xe gyovaxa wei kongrikesin o. Wei e xouv xam angya emaxow gyand o.  
\v 29 Ka a bei na ekom a woulek bei, naw bemeeng tyek nam eivek xam senghoing me bo nol wou sipsip yeiw ne.  
\v 30 De xam venaxow xe xel valu tyek qandi me bong qayeeng tyonyeing me na puw xel betiyeing valu betiwou xel.  
\v 31 Om xam ghe gweiteyei xow, xam ghe bounaleim bei teyei lek vakovek qes yal eno a se mi tip neileing wou xam titi boukeing aluw bendiyeing is mang louk. 
\p  
\v 32 “Gweimbeeng a toung xam eivek Anutu mema, en ambei xam ghe bou naleimim en e xe qayeeng wei lalei xeiles o. Lalei xeiles tine eno teyeimbei bo nikanzek wou xam, me tyek teyeimbei bong lulul nimza dalus wei Anutu mi wong wou xomaxoneing wei e wong xel wo vambuing o.  
\v 33 A se mi xei manglek silva me ghol me qaeing wei xelti xe yo.  
\v 34 Xam venaxow ghe woulek woy bei a maxow memang ne mi wong vineing wou xow me na mi vind xel wei mindei is ay yo.  
\v 35 Eivek lul tambak wei a mi wong o, a talex wou xam bei xey a betiwou kwa wei xey a bo xuk nikanzek. En kandek xey a devind xel wei nikanzek maeing o, xey a bou naleind en qayeeng wei Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu venaxow neil o: ‘Inye mata nimza ena wou xel wei mi tatei memend o ghanaw xel wei mi qou e lam wou xow o.’” 
\p  
\v 36 Paulus neil qayeeng tine woy, woyom moxo ev vaxa qatu eivek dom zeimema is xel gyovaxa yon dalus.  
\v 37 Moxoyeiw dalus eng me zeimaxoun Paulus dom ya e ling.  
\v 38 Xel xouing laleind pyaxow en qayeeng wei e neil o, en tyek xel se nox gyei e ma no. De woyom xel qou e me la eivek sip. 
\c 21  
\s1 Paulus la Yerusalem 
\p  
\v 1 Ka xa la veil xel teivateiv on, xa la ingwei mamileeng nei me na qou sip de sepa me na la bombek wou ailan Kos. Deka woyaing xa la veil ailan Rodes me na la tyip beyeeng nayak Patara.  
\v 2 Nanghei inyon eno xa xei sip ti embei na distrik Ponisia, om xa la eivek sip tiyon me sepa me na la.  
\v 3 Ka xa ghei di xeip lek mamileeng eno xa xei la ailan Saiprus nanghei mema qeinz, ekom xa ghanaw tembuing nayak eivek mamileeng on me na la tyip Siria. Xa la liveil anghei beyeeng nayak Taia, nanghei inyon eno sip la toung qoupek teila.  
\v 4 Xa xei xel betiyeing nanghei inyon, om xa dei is xel teyei lek bouk lim yuw. Eivek Laweeng Vambuing eno xel neil wou Paulus bei e se na pu Yerusalem nei.  
\v 5 Ekom xa xe seivma la wou eivek, om xa ghanaw beyeeng on me na la. Xel betiyeing dalus lis venei neu xel xouing qou xa me la myayaing veil beyeeng on, de xa ev vaxami qatu eivek lek luzeeng wei mamileeng vi yon de na zeimemami.  
\v 6 Ka xa puw ama memami woy, woyom xa lek la sip, de moxoyeiw lox bend. 
\p  
\v 7 Xa la veil Taia, dom na la tei beyeeng Tolemes. Xa neil bendiyeing wou xel lingyeiw dom na toundei is xel bouk ti.  
\v 8 Lek bouk nge xa la tyip Sisalia me na toundei eivek Pilip xe xomek inyon sinale ti, e eivek xel lim yuw on eno ti wei mi vind xel sinaleyeiw o.  
\v 9 Moxo neuyeiw vexawo vey wei mi dei paleveeng, eno xel mi neil xoulek ambei poropet. 
\p  
\v 10 Ka xa dei teyei lek bouk valu eivek Sisalia, poropet ti lei Agabus eno lam veil Yudia me lam axo wei Sisalia ne.  
\v 11 Moxo lam wou xa, me qou Paulus xe let, de tup emaxow mema luw vaxa de neil, “Laweeng Vambuing neil ambei nye, ‘Eivek sakwaing tine Yudayeiw wei mindei eivek Yerusalem eno tyek bako tambiy tiwei e xe let ne yo me na toung e na eivek xel amba memend.’” 
\p  
\v 12 Xa ngo tine, eno xa me xel xomaxoneing on eno xa tay wou Paulus bei e se na pu wei Yerusalem nei.  
\v 13 Woyom Paulus neil embei, “Xam ghe di eng me ghe wong a laleing pyaw xow en va? A xeiwou xow woy bei xel a toung ay eivek xeitueing, me xel nyeis a mey nanghei Yerusalem en Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu lei.”  
\v 14 Paulus wo nikanzek bei embei na, om xa tip lukeing me na neil, “Lul wei Tambiy Ngandoung wounalei bei etyip, ond inyon etyip.” 
\p  
\v 15 Ka bouk valu la veil, xa xeiwou xow me na la pu wei Yerusalem nei.  
\v 16 Xel betiyeing valu wei mindei Sisalia eno lam is xa me qou xa me la Nason wei Saiprus eno beeng. Inyon betiyeing wei takwei yo ti wei tyek xa toumendei is e yo. 
\s1 Paulus la tyip Yerusalem 
\p  
\v 17 Ka xa la tyip Yerusalem, eno xel lingyeiw qou xa is xeilala.  
\v 18 Yanyeing eno Paulus me xa dalus a la xei Jems, me teivateiv dalus eno lam toundei inyon.  
\v 19 Paulus neil bendiyeing wou xel, de neil wou xel en vati wei Anutu wong eivek xel amba senghoing en e xe xuk wei wong o. 
\p  
\v 20 Ka xel teivateiv ngo Paulus xe qayeeng woy, xel sanghoxe Anutu. De xel neil wou Paulus: “Ling, wang wei, xel ngenongakes wei Yuda eno wongis, om xel dalus on di luk ngenong en qayeeng petieing wei Mose yo.  
\v 21 Ekom xel on valu neil wou xel en wang bei, wang di teyoxe Yudayeiw dalus wei mindei eivek xel amba senghoing bei xel a saing Mose xe petieing, de neil wou xel bei xel se ghuw neundyeiw ninavi, o xam se betiwou kwa wei takwei yo.  
\v 22 Tyek xey a bong vati? Gyeik xel a ngo inye neing bei wang lam,  
\v 23 om wong vati wei xa bei neil wou wang ne. Inyon moux vey toundei is xey, xel eti yeiw wei neil qayeeng zonghek ti is Anutu yo.  
\v 24 Qou xel moux beimambei ne, me xam xouing betiwou kwa wei deing vako yo me wa dexouv xel xe da en kandek xel a puw lund velus veil. Woyom tyek xel dalus boulek zonghek bei neing ma veil qayeeng tiwei xel byex lek wang ne, ekom wamaxow mendi betiwou petieing.  
\v 25 De xel amba wei wongeingis, eno xey a byex qapiya wou xel bei xel gyeiteyei xow en yaeing leliy wei xel sei da wou anutu tyonyeing o, me xel se gya leliy wei gyand toundei eivek o, me leliy leyeis wei xel tup xel kwend me xel se bong kwa nilul wei kwapesiv o.”  
\v 26 Paulus qou xel moux wei xel neil qayeeng zonghek is Anutu woy yo, de yanyeing eno emaxow betiwou kwa dalus wei e bei bo vako yo is xel. Woyom moxo la ingwei xomek vambuing nei me neil wou lumukiyeiw en bouk nge wei tyek xel bo vako yo de tyek xel titi nam a toung xel xe da. 
\s1 Xel zeimaxoun Paulus 
\p  
\v 27 Gyeik bouk lim yuw embim nama, xel Yudayeiw valu nanghei provins wei Esia eno yei Paulus eivek xomek vambuing. Om xel zeim moux dalus on laleind lek me zeimaxoun e,  
\v 28 de xel taxe niseikeing bei, “xam moux wei Israel o, vind xa! Moux tine inye tambiy wei mi teyoxe xomaxoneing dalus la danghei danghei nei me neil nilul lek xe xe xel xomaxoneing me Mose xe petieing me beyeeng tine. Me se tine venaxow, qe qou Grikyeiw me la eivek xomek vambuing lalei me wo nol wou xomek vambuing ne wo nilaxes.”  
\v 29 (En nambei takwei eno xel yei Tlopimas wei Epeses o toundei eivek Yerusalem is Paulus, me xel embeik nge Paulus qou tambiy on me la eivek xomek vambuing on lalei.) 
\p  
\v 30 Xel xomaxoneing dalus wei beyeeng ngandoung on etek mouyo, me xomaxoneing dalus veimyend me lam anghei danghei danghei nei. Me zeimaxoun Paulus, xel tetei e veil tete lalei wei xomek vambuing on, dom xel wo daing me toung tete mya dalus zeyi.  
\v 31 Kalekom xel di wong en embei nyeis e, om xel wong qayeeng la wou vevekyeiw xe lei ngandoung wei Rom o bei beyeeng ngandoung wei Yerusalem eno neilama me di leis ama bandabanda.  
\v 32 Moxo wo daing me qou beyeiv xel lei ngandoung me xel vevek valu dom xel veimyend me la wou xel qendu ngandoung on. Gyeik xel on yei lei ngandoung is e xe xel vevekyeiw, xel tip de se leis Paulus no. 
\p  
\v 33 Lei ngandoung on lam paviy me zeimaxoun Paulus me luk nikanzek wou xel vevek on bei xel atup e nangya sen yayuw. Woyom moxo teling Yudayeiw bei, tambiy yon eti me vati ingwei e di wong on.  
\v 34 Xel qendu ngandoung on valu taxe lul nge de xel valu taxe lul bange me neil qayeeng la bandabanda, om lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o se teyei bei ngo wou qayeeng qes, om luk nikanzek wou xel vevek bei xel a qou Paulus me na eivek bend.  
\v 35 Ekom gyeik Paulus la tyip wou lewing, xel vevekyeiw yei moux alis vex on ngenong embei nyeis e, om xel qalei moxo me la.  
\v 36 Xel moux alis vex wei di betiy xel on taxe niseikeing bei, “Leis e mey!” 
\s1 Paulus luk is xel qendu ngandoung on 
\p  
\v 37 Ka vevekyeiw qou Paulus me embei na eivek bend, moxo teling wou lei ngandoung bei, “Teyei bei a neil qayeeng ti wou wang?” Lei ngandoung neil embei, “Wang woulek Grik vyend?  
\v 38 Beip wang on Izip, tiwei wo vevek wou seyap de qou 4,000 moux wei mi wong vevek en ngeyeing me la eivek tembuing bandaing wei bouk valu la veil o?” 
\p  
\v 39 Paulus neimbei, “A ne Yuda ti, nanghei Tarsus eivek Silisia, a bang nei lei laeing. Teyeimbei a baluk wou xel xomaxoneing ne.” 
\p  
\v 40 Tambiy wei Lei ngandoung on lewexe lek telinyeing tiyon, Paulus nale lek lewing dom pepeeng xel qendu ngandoung on. Ka xel denduing ma, moxo luk wou xel eivek Yuda vyend. 
\c 22  
\p  
\v 1 “Xam lingyeiw me xam mangyeiw, xam ngo a xe qayeeng wei ambei neil gweimbeeng ne eno qes teyei.”  
\v 2 Xel ngo moxo di luk wou xel eivek xel venaxow vyend Hibru, om moxoyeiw denduing ma. 
\p De Paulus neil embei:  
\v 3 A ne Yuda ti, a umbek eivek Tarsus wei Silisia nei, ekom a ling eivek Yerusalem de Gameliel mi teyoxe ay en petieing wei Mose xe yo, me a mi byexaxoun Anutu xe kwa wei lalei vind xey nambei xam valu ghe di wong gweimbeeng ne.  
\v 4 An di wo nol wou xel wei wongis bei na nyeis xel amey, xel wei mi betiwou sakwaing tine, a zeimaxoun xel moux alis vex me na toung xel la eivek xomek xeitueing.  
\v 5 Lumuki lukanzek me xel kanzol dalus tyek na neil a teyei. A qou qapiya wou xel me na la wou lingyeiw eivek Damaskus, me na la inyei bei na bako xel xomaxoneing nanghei inyon me na qou xel me na nam Yerusalem en xel teivateiv bo myaveweeng wou xel. 
\p  
\v 6 “Bendiyeing wei seivma evlek a lam paviy Damaskus, de lutika eno xeiyaing teleing ti lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei me tel evivekwou ay.  
\v 7 A teila lek tembuing me na ngo vya ti neil wou ay, ‘Sol! Sol! Nambei nya wang di wo nol wou ay?’ 
\p  
\v 8 “A teling bei, Tambiy Ngandoung, ‘Wang eti?’ 
\p “Moxo neil eloum bei, ‘A Yesu wei Nasaret, tiwei wang di wo nimaying wou yo.’  
\v 9 A xe xel wei mi la is ay yo eno yei xeiyaing, ekom xel se woulek tambiy tiwei di luk is ay eno vya. 
\p  
\v 10 “De a teling, Tambiy Ngandoung, ‘Tyek a bong vati?’ Tambiy Ngandoung neil, ‘Qandi lek me la eivek Damaskus. Nanghei inyon tyek xel a neil wou wang en vati wei wambei bong o.’  
\v 11 A xe xel wei la is ay eno zeim a memang me xa la eivek Damaskus, en nambei xeiyaing on byex a mang tekzeyi. 
\p  
\v 12 “Tambiy ti lei Ananias lam me yei ay. Moxo mi wevek Anutu xeinghembi me mi betiwou qayeeng petieing wo nimza. Me Yudayeiw wei mindei inyon eno mi neil embei e moux nimza.  
\v 13 Moxo nale paviy ay me neil, ‘Ling Sol, wa mamghalus e gyeina!’ De lutika eno a manghalus yeila me a xei e. 
\p  
\v 14 “Woyom moxo neil: ‘Anutu wei xe mendyeiw eno beyal wang bei wang boulek e xe lalei vineing me ghe gwei Tambiy Tiwei Bombek ayang o me na ngo e xe qayeeng eivek e mya.  
\v 15 Wang teyei lek e xe tambiy wei yeimawou woy o, om tyek wa qou vati wei wang wei lek mamghalus me ghe ngo yo me na neil teyei ena wou xomaxoneing sapa.  
\v 16 Om gweimbeeng ne wang di axe vati? Qandi lek me qou lipekeing. De taxe e lei en e sekweyexe wa xe sewokeing veil o.’ 
\p  
\v 17 “Ka a loum Yerusalem me na di zeimemang eivek xomek vambuing, a xeip naleing ma,  
\v 18 me na xei Tambiy Ngandoung luk wou ay nambei inye. ‘La daing, me la veil Yerusalem lutika, en tyek xel se ngo wa xe qayeeng wei wambei neil a teyei yo.’ 
\p  
\v 19 “A lewexe bei, ‘Tambiy Ngandoung, xel moux tine woulek bei a la Yudayeiw xe xomek qekueing ama, me na la nge me na toung moux alis vex wei wongis wang eno eivek xeitueing de na leis xel.  
\v 20 De gyeik xel leis Setepan mey, wa xe tambiy wei mi neil wa xe xoulek eno a toukale paviy me na xei e gyand qapyex o, me na xeiteyei eti yeiw wei leis e yo xe teimb.’ 
\p  
\v 21 “Woyom Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou ay, ‘La. Tyek a bong wang na dingta lul nei wou xel amba.’ ” 
\s1 Paulus on nanghei Rom 
\p  
\v 22 Xel qendu tiyon ngo Paulus deka moxo neil tine. Woyom xel taxe niseikeing bei, “Leis e mey! Tambiy ambei nyon se toumendei mapieing lek tembuing!” 
\p  
\v 23 Ka xel wo vyend me kwax xel xe teimb ding me nex ela me nex vegyuveeng la gheyapu,  
\v 24 om lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o wo qayeeng nikanzek bei xel a qou Paulus me na bend. Moxo neil wou xel bei xel sesa e me bo telinyeing me gyimexe nimaying tiyon qes, embei boulek bei xel xomaxoneing on di wo vyendlek e en va.  
\v 25 Ka xel tup Paulus mema vaxa bei na sesa e, Paulus neil wou beyeiv wei xel xe yo, wei toukale paviy on me neimbei, “Inye se la teyei lek petieing bei wa sesa tambiy wei Rom wei xam seng ghei wo qayeeng en e yo?” 
\p  
\v 26 Beyeiv ngo qayeeng tine, om moxo la neil wou lei ngandoung wei vevekyeiw o. Moxo teling, “Tyek wang bong ambei nya? Moux tine inye tambiy wei Rom o.” 
\p  
\v 27 Lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o la wou Paulus me teling, “Neil wou ay, inyon wa Rom ti ei?” Moxo lewexe, “Ee inye ay yo.”  
\v 28 Woyom lei ngandoung neil wou e, “A wong malew ngandoung bei na bong ambei tambiy wei Rom o.” 
\p Paulus neil elox bei, “Ekom a umbek eivek beyeeng ne nambei tambiy wei Rom o ti.” 
\p  
\v 29 Eti yeiw wei di wong en embei sesa e eno duxeind lutika. Deka lei ngandoung woulek bei Paulus on tambiy wei Rom, om moxo yaleeng en venaxow neil wou xel vevek bei xel a tup Paulus en sen. 
\s1 Paulus nale wou xel kanzol mendghalus 
\p  
\v 30 Yanyeing eno lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o embei boulek qes bei nambei nya ekom Yudayeiw byex qayeeng lek Paulus, om moxo kwax sen veil Paulus. De wong qayeeng la wou xel kanzol me lumuki leitata bei xel nam qekuma. De qou Paulus me lam wong e nale wou xel mendghalus. 
\c 23  
\p  
\v 1 Paulus doma wou xel kanzol me neil, “Xam lingyeiw eivek a laleing, a mi la bombek me sewokeing ma veil ay wou Anutu manghalus me e lam tyip gweimbeeng.”  
\v 2 Moxo neil ambei nyon, eno lumuki lukanzek Ananias neil nikanzek wou xel moux wei toukale paviy Paulus on bei xel petapexe e mya.  
\v 3 Woyom Paulus neil wou e, “Anutu tyek sesa wang, wang on nambei tete nol wei xel pelei teleing lek o! Wang wou kwam en wa bei betiwou petieing me ghe bo qayeeng en ay, om wang lam toundei inyon, ekom wamaxow ghe pyalek petieing me ghe neil nikanzek bei xel sesa ay.” 
\p  
\v 4 Xel wei toukale paviy Paulus eno neil, “Nambei nya wambei neil qayeeng nol lek Anutu xe lumuki lukanzek on?” 
\p  
\v 5 Paulus neil elox bei, “Xam lingyeiw, a se woulek bei inyon moxo lumuki lukanzek. En nambei xel byex eivek xoulek bei: ‘Xam se baluk nilul lek tambiy wei mi yeiteyei wa xe xel xomaxoneing o.’ ” 
\p  
\v 6 Woyom Paulus woulek woy bei, xel on valu yon Sadyusi me xel valu yon Parisi, om taxe la wou xel kanzol, “Xam lingyeiw, a ne Parisi, me Parisi neu moux ay. A nale lek qayeeng wongeing en nambei a mi toung manghalus bei xel meyeing tyek qandi lek.”  
\v 7 Paulus neil qayeeng tine, eno qayeeng vevek qandi eivek xel Sadyusi me xel Parisi, me xel wei di qekuma eno dembuma is ambei nyon.  
\v 8 (Xel Sadyusi neil embei xel meyeing tyek se qandi lek, me inyon angela ma me laweeng ma, ekom xel Parisi wongis lul tine dalus.) 
\p  
\v 9 Om bembeeng on wong nindenduing ngandoung kamouyo, me xel putoung wei petieing o valu eno Parisi wei toungale inyon eno luk nikanzek bei, “Xa se xei lulti sewok eivek tambiy ne. Beind laweeng o angela luk wou e.”  
\v 10 Qayeeng vevek wo ngandoung om lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o yaleeng enok moux alis vex tetei Paulus me e neing a tip. Om moxo wo qayeeng nikanzek wou xel vevekyeiw bei xel na tetei e veil xel me na qou e me na eivek bend. 
\p  
\v 11 Yanyeing boukeing eno Tambiy Ngandoung toungale paviy Paulus me neil, “Wa bale bo nikanzek! Nambei ingwei wang mi neil a xe xoulek eivek Yerusalem o, om wa mi neil a xe qayeeng ambei nyon eivek Rom is.” 
\s1 Xel Yuda neil embei nyeis Paulus amey 
\p  
\v 12 Yanyeing satiboukeing eno Yudayeiw qekuma me tup qayeeng lekti, me xel neil neing is inya punei bei, tyek xel se gya o na num, qe ka xel nyeis Paulus amey bole.  
\v 13 Xel moux wei neil qayeeng tine eno teyei lek xoumeeng vey (40).  
\v 14 Xel la wou xel lumuki leitata yo me teivateiv me neil, “Xa neil neing is inya punei bei, xa se teyei bei gha lulti qe ka xa nyeis Paulus amey le.  
\v 15 Woyom gweimbeeng, xam me xel kanzol ghe bong qayeeng na wou lei ngandoung, en e qou Paulus me nam axone wou xam. Me na tyoxe e bei xam ambei ngo qayeeng neing valu en tine. Dom xa menyex wou xow en kandek na nyeis e gyeik moxo nam a tyip inye yo.” 
\p  
\v 16 Ekom Paulus li vex neu moux ngo qayeeng tine, om moxo la eivek xel vevekyeiw bend me neil wou Paulus. 
\p  
\v 17 Woyom Paulus taxe beyeiv ti me neil wou e, “Qou moux ghavis tine me la wou lei ngandoung wei vevek o. Moxo embei neil qayeeng ngandoung ti wou e.”  
\v 18 Om moxo qou e me la wou lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o. Beyeiv neil, “Paulus, tambiy wei la xeitueing, taxe a la me teling wou ay bei a qou moux ghavis tine me na nam wou wang en e bei neil lul valu wou wang.” 
\p  
\v 19 Lei ngandoung wei vevek o zeim moux ghavis on mema, de qou e me la nenyawes me teling e, “Inye wambei neil vati wou ay?” 
\p  
\v 20 Moxo neil, “Xel Yuda toung qayeeng lekti bei tyek teling wou wang bei wa qou Paulus me ghe na wou xel kanzol yanyeing. Xel embei tyoxe wang bei na ngo wou qayeeng on qes bo nimza en tambiy yon.  
\v 21 Wang seng bong e wou xel, en xel on teyei lek xoumeeng vey (40) eno di xupek me axe me neil neing is inya punei bei tyek xel se gya lulti o na num qe ka xel nyeis Paulus amey bole. Xel yeiwou xow gweimbeeng, xel di axe wang bei wang zenghek lek xel xe qayeeng.” 
\p  
\v 22 Lei ngandoung wei xel vevekyeiw o wong ghavis on la de luk nikanzek wou e, “Wa se neil wou xelti bei wang neil qayeeng tine wou ay.” 
\s1 Xel wong Paulus la Sisalia 
\p  
\v 23 Woyom moxo taxe e xe beyeiv yuw me wo qayeeng nikanzek wou luw bei, “Muw ghe gweiwou me na qou 200 vevekyeiw is 70 vevekyeiw wei mi dei lek vuteiv o me na qou 200 moux wei mi wo vevek angya yiy o is. Me xam ghe na Sisalia boukeing lek seivma limvey.  
\v 24 Xam ghe gweiwou vuteiv wou Paulus is ambei nyon me na qou e me ghe na nimza wou Peliks lei ngandoung wei seyap o.” 
\p  
\v 25 Moxo byex qapiya nambei nye: 
\b  
\mi  
\v 26 A Klodias Lisias, a byex qapiya ne lak wou wa Peliks lei ngandoung wei seyap o. Bendiyeing wang. 
\b  
\pi1  
\v 27 Tambiy tine eno Yudayeiw zeimaxoun me xel embim nyeis e, ekom a la is a xe xel vevekyeiw me na la qou e veil xel memend, en a woulek bei inyon e wei nanghei Rom o.  
\v 28 Ambei ngo wou bei nambei nya ekom xel byex qayeeng lek e, om a qou e me na la wou xel xe kanzol.  
\v 29 A xei bei xel byex qayeeng lek e me teling wou e en xel venaxow xe petieing, ekom xel se wong qayeeng ti teyei bei e mey o e na xeitueing.  
\v 30 De a ngo bei xel tup qayeeng lekti xupekeing en xel embei nyeis tambiy tine na mey, om a wong e lak wou wang lutika. Me a wong qayeeng nikanzek wou xel wei byex qayeeng lek e yo bei xel nak a neil qes tiwei xel zeim e eno wou wang teyei. 
\b  
\p  
\v 31 Om xel vevekyeiw, eno betiwou qayeeng nikanzek wei xel e lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o me qou Paulus me lak eivek boukeing me la beyeeng Antipatris.  
\v 32 Yanyeing eno xel wei mindei lek vuteiv eno la is e, de xel vevekyeiw valu loum bend nanghei Yerusalem.  
\v 33 Xel vevekyeiw wei mindei lek vuteiv o la tyip Sisalia, xel qou qapiya me la wong wou lei ngandoung wei seyap o de wong Paulus la wou e.  
\v 34 Lei ngandoung wei seyap o pyaw qapiya, woyom teling Paulus bei, “wang lam anghei provins tina.” Moxo woulek bei Paulus lam anghei Silisia,  
\v 35 Lei ngandoung wei seyap o neil, “Tyek a ngo wa xe qayeeng gyeik xel wei wong qayeeng en wang o nam a tyip inye.” Woyom e wo qayeeng nikanzek wou belimbo yeiw bei xel gyei Paulus teyei eivek Herot beeng. 
\c 24  
\s1 Xel gyovaxa wei Yuda yo wo qayeeng en Paulus 
\p  
\v 1 Ka bouk lim la veil, woyom Ananias lumuki lukanzek la xo wei Sisalia nei is xel teivateiv valu me tambiy wei lupeyei yeip yaing en petieing wei xel Rom o lei Tetalas, me qou xel xe qayeeng wei xel embei bo qayeeng en Paulus eno wou lei ngandoung wei seyap o manghalus.  
\v 2 Woyom lei ngandoung Peliks taxe Paulus la lalei, de Tetalas wong qayeeng en e me neil ambei nye: “Lei ngandoung Peliks, xa dei ewo nimza eivek wa xe lalei vevopeing me wang vind xa xe xel me ghe menyex wou lulul ngenong wei takwei wei xel se dei ewo nimza yo.  
\v 3 Xa xei lulti beimambei ne, om xa laleimi wo nimza mouyo, me na neil dange ngandoung wou wang.  
\v 4 Ekom xa se teyei bei zeimaxoun wang enden. Ambei tay wou wang en wa laleim vevop wou xa me na ngo xa xe qayeeng sepi kane. 
\p  
\v 5 “Xa xei tambiy tine eno mi wo nilul ngenong, moxo mi zeim xel laleind lek en vevek eivek Yudayeiw senghoing me la teyei lek tembuing sapa. Tambiy on gyovaxa wei xel qendu tiwei la veil xa dom xel mi taxe bei Nasaret o.  
\v 6 Me moxo wong me yei en embei bong xomek vambuing on bo nilaxes wou Anutu manghalus, ekom xa zeimaxoun e, me xa bei bo qayeeng en e nangya xa maxow xe petieing.  
\v 7 Ekom Lisias lei ngandoung lam is e xe vevekyeiw me wo vevek is xa me tetei Paulus veil xa memami.  
\v 8 Dekalekom neil qayeeng nikanzek wou eti yeiw wei embei zeim qayeeng en e eno e nam wou wang. Om wa venaxow ghe gwei embo nimza. Me teling e en tine, me na qou kwa wou emaxow vya en lul beimambei ne bei xa wo qayeeng en e.” 
\p  
\v 9 Xel Yuda vind Tetalas is ambei nyon, me byex qayeeng lek Paulus bei inye zonghek. 
\p  
\v 10 Woyom lei ngandoung wei seyap o tetax kwa bei e baluk om Paulus neil elox: “A woulek bei lek vakovek qes valu eno wang mi zeim qayeeng wei xa xomaxoneing dalus ne. Om a laleind wo nimza me na lewexe lek wa xe qayeeng.  
\v 11 Wangwei wa teling enana nei, yon wang boulek bei bouk xoumeeng yuw la veil eno a la pu Yerusalem bei na bong lalo.  
\v 12 A xei bei xel wei Yuda eno se yei bei a wo veweeng is xelti eivek xomek vambuing, o xel se yei bei a zeim xel qekueing ama yon laleind lek eivek Yudayeiw xe xomek qekueing ama me eivek beyeeng ngandoung on ti. Ma.  
\v 13 Me xel se teyei bei talex bei qayeeng wei xel byex lek a ne eno inye zonghek.  
\v 14 Ekom ambei neilteyei bei, a mi wong lalo wou Anutu wei xa bumiyeiw o me na mi betiwou Sakwaing Tiyon, wei xel mi taxe bei bange. A wongis lul dalus wei Mose byex eivek petieing o me xel poropet byex eyeip eivek qapiya yo,  
\v 15 me a wongis me na di toung mang en Anutu nambei xel moux beimambei ne bei tyek na piyexe xel wei bombek o me xel wei nilul o eno xel xouing qandi lek veil meyeing.  
\v 16 Om nambei nyon a mi wo nikanzek me na mi xeiteyei laleing wo nimza bei emi mendei embo bombek wou Anutu manghalus me xel xomaxoneing mendghalus is ambei nyon. 
\p  
\v 17 “Ka a la dei vakovek qes valu eivek beyeeng ba, a loum Yerusalem me na qou lul wei xeilala yo valu wou a xe xel xomaxoneing bei na bong wou xel wei kanyo yo de na toung da.  
\v 18 De gyeik xel yei ay eivek xomek vambuing eno a wo vako woy wou Anutu manghalus. Me xel ngenong ti se toundei is ay, me wo nindenduing bandabanda.  
\v 19 Ekom Yudayeiw valu lam anghei provins wei Esia nei me zeimaxoun ay. Wangwei xel xe qayeeng ti mendei gyeip wou ay ond inye nimza bei xel venaxow nam inye wou wa manghalus me bong qayeeng en ay.  
\v 20 O xel beimambei wei toundei inye eno teyeimbei neil sewokeing vati wei xel yei eivek ay eno teyei gyeik ingwei a nale wou xel kanzol mendghalus o.  
\v 21 Om qayeeng tixemou wei a taxe eno nambei nye: ‘Qayeeng wei xel meyeing tyek qandi lek veil meyeing, om qes tine gweimbeeng xel wong qayeeng en ay.’ ” 
\p  
\v 22 Woyom Peliks woulek kwa wei xel xomaxoneing ne mi betiwou Sakwaing Tiyon wo nimza yo, om tetulexe bouk dom wong xel lox de neil, “Gyeik Lisias lei ngandoung wei xel vevek o nam, tyek a menyex wou wa xe qayeeng.”  
\v 23 Moxo wo qayeeng nikanzek wou beyeiv bei e toung Paulus eivek xel belimbo memend, me neil wou xel bei xel se bale zeyi e qe e mi ghavineeng me nox me num eivek xomek lalei me xel se bale zeyi e xe gweleeng qe xel a mi gyei e teyei en lulul vatiyeiw. 
\p  
\v 24 Bouk valu la veil, Peliks lam is venei Drusila, inye Yuda vex ti. Moxo wong qayeeng la wou Paulus me e lam de li nenya wou qayeeng wei e di neil o, Paulus neil wou e en kwa wei wongeingis Yesu Kilisi yo.  
\v 25 Ka Paulus luk is xel en sakwaing bombek, me ingwei xomaxoneing na mi gyeiteyei xow me ingwei Anutu tyek na zeim qayeeng en xey loxyus o. Omva Peliks moxo yaleeng me neil, “Gweimbeeng inye woy! Wang na. Deka anghei sakwaing ti gyeip yaing, on tyek a bong qayeeng nak wou wang.”  
\v 26 Lek bouk kayon bombek eno moxo embeik nge tyek Paulus bong malew valu wou e, en na zeimaxoun Peliks lalei de na tul e na nivax. Om lumama eno moxo mi wong qayeeng la wou e bei baluk is e. 
\p  
\v 27 Ka vakovek qes yuw la veil, Posias Festus qou Peliks nimbeeng. De Peliks embei bong Yudayeiw bo xeindlala en e, om wong Paulus toundei eivek xeitueing. 
\c 25  
\s1 Festus embei ngo Paulus xe qayeeng 
\p  
\v 1 Festus wo seyap wei provins Yudia yo. Ka bouk yal la veil eno Festus la veil Sisalia me la tyip Yerusalem nei.  
\v 2 Om xel lumuki leitata me Yuda xe gyovaxa lam wou e me byex qayeeng lek Paulus. Xel luk nikanzek wou Festus bei,  
\v 3 e devind xel me bong Paulus na Yerusalem, en nambei xel di yeiwou xow bei nyeis Paulus amey wou sakwaing.  
\v 4 Festus lewexe bei, “Paulus toundei eivek xeitueing anghei Sisalia, me a maxow a bim ana inyei paviyeing ka.”  
\v 5 Om moxo neil, “Xam xe gyovaxa valu nam is ay me bong qayeeng en tambiy yon, wangwei moxo bong sewokeing ti nei.” 
\p  
\v 6 Ka Festus dei bouk lim yal o xoumeeng is xel, de moxo la xo wei Sisalia nei, de yanyeing eno moxo la dei eivek xomek wei ngoeing qayeeng me wong qayeeng nikanzek bei xel a qou Paulus me nam wou e.  
\v 7 Ka Paulus lam woy, xel Yudayeiw wei lam axone nanghei Yerusalem eno nale vivekwou e, xel byex qayeeng nilul leimalei lek e bei bong qayeeng en e, ekom xel se teyei bei talex wou Festus bei qayeeng ne neing. 
\p  
\v 8 Woyom Paulus neil e xe qayeeng lox wou xel: “A se wong sewokeing ti lek petieing wei xel Yudayeiw, o lek xomek vambuing, o wou Sisa, king wei Rom o.” 
\p  
\v 9 Ekom Festus e bei bong xel Yudayeiw laleind bo nimza wou e, om teling wou Paulus, “Beip wa being na pu wei Yerusalem nei me bale lek qayeeng wou ay anghei inyei en qayeeng ti beimambei ne?” 
\p  
\v 10 Paulus lewexe, “Gweimbeeng a nale lek Sisa xe xomek wei ngoeing qayeeng eivek o. Wei tyek a bo qayeeng o. En a se wo sewokeing ti wou xel Yudayeiw, nambei ingwei wamaxow ghe woulek e wo nimza yo.  
\v 11 Nambei nyon wangwei a bong sewokeing ti teyei bei a mey lek nei, Ond tyek a se pesek en meyeing. Ekom wangwei qayeeng wei xel byex lek a ne se neing, ond xel ti se teyei bei toung ay eivek xel on memend. Tyek a maxow a bong qayeeng wou Sisa me e ngo!” 
\p  
\v 12 Ka Festus luk is e xe xel kanzol, moxo neil: “Wang neimbei Sisa e ngo wa xe qayeeng. Om tyek wang na wou Sisa!” 
\s1 Festus teling king Agripa 
\p  
\v 13 Bouk valu lak veil, King Agripa me Benaisi la tei Sisalia bei na bong luw xe qayeeng nimza wou Festus.  
\v 14 Ka xel dei luk ngenong nanghei inyon, Festus neilteyei wou king en Paulus xe qayeeng. Moxo neil: “Inyon tambiy ti toundei inye eno Peliks wong e ghei toundei eivek xomek xeitueing.  
\v 15 Gyeik a la Yerusalem, xel lumuki leitata me teivateiv wei Yudayeiw eno byex qayeeng lek e me teling bei xel bo myaveweeng wou moxo. 
\p  
\v 16 “A neil wou xel bei inye se kwa wei xa wei Rom o bei xa toung nimaying lek tambiy ti bandaing, qe ka e bale wou xel wei wo qayeeng en e yo mendghalus bole me na neil qayeeng valu me bale zeyi xow en xel xe qayeeng.  
\v 17 Om ka xel lam inye is ay, a se wong xel mi axe ay. Qe a dei eivek xomek wei ngoeing qayeeng eno lek nge yanyeing me na wong qayeeng la bei xel a qou tambiy on me nam.  
\v 18 Gyeik xel wei wo qayeeng en e yo nale me luk, ekom xel se neil qayeeng nilul ti lek e nambei a wou eivek naleing o.  
\v 19 Qe xel wei pyalek ama is e en xel xe lalo me tambiy wei mey eno lei Yesu, ekom Paulus neil embei moxo toundei mapieing.  
\v 20 A se teyei bei gheiwou qayeeng tine qes, om a teling moxo bei e teyei bei na Yerusalem me na bale lek wongeing qayeeng tine.  
\v 21 Ekom Paulus neil, embei toumendei eivek xeitueing teyei lek ingwei king Sisa wei Rom eno na ngo qayeeng wei e yo. Om a wong qayeeng nikanzek la bei xel gyei e teyei eivek xeitueing dekakom am bong e na wou Sisa.” 
\p  
\v 22 Woyom Agripa neil wou Festus, “A venaxow ambei ngo tambiy tine xe qayeeng.” Festus neil elox bei, “Yanyeing tyek wa ngo e xe qayeeng.” 
\s1 Paulus nale wou Agripa manghalus 
\p  
\v 23 Om yanyeing eno Agripa me Benaisi lam is vunekeing nimza me la eivek xomek lalei wei qekueing ama yo is xel wei wo lukanzek en vevekyeiw o me tambiy wei mi la tax en xel moux wei beyeeng ngandoung on o. De Festus neil om xel qou Paulus me lam.  
\v 24 Woyom Festus neil, “King Agripa, me eti yeiw dalus wei toundei is xey ne, xam ghe wei tambiy tine! Xel xomaxoneing sapa wei Yuda eno xel taxe la nikanzek wou ay eivek Yerusalem me eivek Sisalia, xel taxe bei a nyeis e mey enok moxo mendei mapieing enden.  
\v 25 Ekom a xei bei moxo se wo sewokeing ti teyei bei e mey, om e maxow wong e xe qayeeng bei king Sisa e ngo e xe qayeeng, Om a wou naleing bei a bong e na Rom.  
\v 26 Ekom a se woulek e xe sewokeing ti bei a byex qayeeng vati na wou e xe teiv. Nambei nyon a qou e me na lam wou xam dalus, me na lam wou wang, king Agripa, en kandek xey a ngo e xe qayeeng me a byex lul valu eivek qapiya.  
\v 27 En a wou naleind bei inye se nimza bei a bong xel xeitueing ti na Rom wangwei a se byex sewokeing wei e wong eno eivek qapiya enak is.” 
\c 26  
\p  
\v 1 Woyom Agripa neil wou Paulus, “a lenghek lek wang bei wa baluk me na neil wamaxow xe qayeeng.” 
\p Om Paulus pepeeng angya mema de neil e xe qayeeng:  
\v 2 “King Agripa, a wou naleing ambei nye, inye nimza bei a bale wou wa mamghalus gweimbeeng me baluk dom wa ni nenyam wou qayeeng beimambei wei xel Yudayeiw byex lek a ne.”  
\v 3 Wang woulek kwa dalus wei Yudayeiw eno woy me vati wei xel mi vuklek ama yo. Nambei nyon ambei wa mendei kanzek dom na ni nenyam wou a xe qayeeng dalus. 
\p  
\v 4 “Xel Yudayeiw dalus on woulek a woy gyeik a yakayang, nanghei myaxeeng wei a mindei eivek a maxow xe tembuing ne, me na mindei eivek Yerusalem is.  
\v 5 Xel woulek a woy en xel yeimend wou ay takwei qenang nei, om wangwei xel laleind devind nei, ond xel venaxow teyei bei neil a xe kwa wou wang. Inyon betiwou petieing nikanzek wei xa xe lalo yo, a mindei nambei xel Parisi.  
\v 6 En nambei a mi axe me na toung mang wou vati wei Anutu neil qayeeng zonghek is xa mamiyeiw om a nale lek qayeeng gweimbeeng ne.  
\v 7 Tine inye qayeeng zonghek wei xa xe xel veleivlei xoumeeng yuw wei mi toung mend wou bei gyei neing en vati wei xel mi wong lalo wou Anutu bendiyeing aluw boukeing o. Woyom King, en qes tine Yudayeiw byex qayeeng lek ay.  
\v 8 Nambei nya xam valu ghe wou kwamim bei Anutu tyek se piyexe xel meyeing qandi lek? 
\p  
\v 9 “Ay is ambei nyon a wou naleing bei bong lul ngenong en na bo nol wou Yesu wei Nasaret o lei.  
\v 10 De inyon vati wei a mi wong anghei Yerusalem o. A qou leing ngandoung wou xel lumuki leitata bei na toung xel vambuing ngenong eivek xeitueing, ay is ambei nyon a neimbei xel amey.  
\v 11 Teyei lek bouk ngenong a mi la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei xel Yudayeiw o me na la nge bei bo myaveweeng wou xel me na tendu xel bei xel baluk yak lek Yesu. A mi wong me na xei en ambei xel a neil qayeeng nilul lek Tambiy Ngandoung. A laleing mi wo myavanei wou xel, om a mi la dingta me na ximexe xel bei bo myaveweeng wou xel. 
\p  
\v 12 “Bouk ti a qou qayeeng me lei wei ngandoung o wou xel lumuki leitata bei nana Damaskus om xel wong a la.  
\v 13 Woyom king, lek ambei bendiyeing wei seivma evlek eno a di tupwou sakwaing, a xei xeiyaing ti lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei, xeiyaing ngandoung ghanaw sayeiv, eno siing vivekwou ay me a xe xel wei lam is ay yo.  
\v 14 Xa dalus a teila lek tembuing, de a ngo vya ti neil wou ay eivek Yuda vyend, ‘Sol, Sol, wang di wo nimaying wou ay en va? Wang byex vaxam lek lul wei manewou yo, me ghe wong vanei wou xow.’ 
\p  
\v 15 “Woyom a teling, ‘Wang eti, Tambiy Ngandoung?’ 
\p “Tambiy Ngandoung neil eloum bei, ‘A Yesu, wei wang di wo nimaying wou yo.  
\v 16 Gweimbeeng qandi lek me nale ghey. A talex xow wou wang me na beyal wang ambei a xe xukxe me tyek wa neil lulul vati wei wang wei woy en ay yo teyei, me vati wei tyek a talex wou wang yus o.  
\v 17 Tyek a zeim wang veil wamaxow xe xomaxoneing me xel amba memend en xel se bo nol wou wang. Dom na bong wang na wou xel  
\v 18 en wa tax xel mend gyeina me pekwi xel veil mapetok de noum wou xeiyaing, me xel noum veil Sandang nikanzek de noum wou Anutu, om Anutu teyeimbei semaleeng xel xe sewokeing veil de xel teyeimbei mendei is xel wei wo vambuing nangya xel xe wongeingis o.’ 
\p  
\v 19 “Woyom, king Agripa, a se pyalek lul tiwei a mang pekwi me na xei nanghei tyoung gheyapu yo.  
\v 20 Ti myaxeeng eno a neil xoulek wou xel wei toundei eivek Damaskus o, woyom a la wou xel wei Yerusalem me eivek Yuda dalus, me na la wou xel amba is, a neil qayeeng wei xel pekwi me noum wou Anutu me xam xe kwa yon e talex bei xam ghe pekwi xow woy.  
\v 21 Qes tiyon om Yudayeiw zeimaxoun ay eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing me xel embei nyeis a mey.  
\v 22 Ekom Anutu mi vind ay taxombouk me elam tyip gweimbeeng ne, om a nale inye wou wa mamghalus de na neil qayeeng wou xel wei leind maeing me xel wei leind tata yo is. A se neil qayeeng nge qe vati wei poropetyeiw me Mose neil eno tyek na tyip.  
\v 23 Inyon Kilisi tyek na qou myavanei me tyek qandi natax veil meyeing, de tyek na neil qayeeng wei xeiyaing eno teyei wou e maxow xe xomaxoneing me na neil wou xel amba is.” 
\p  
\v 24 Lek qes tine Festus taxe niseikeing me wo nol wou Paulus xe qayeeng. Moxo taxe bei, “Paulus wa lum on wo bandol o. Wang qou lupeyei ngenong me wa lumpeyei yon wong wang wo bandol.” 
\p  
\v 25 Ekom Paulus neil elox, “Lei ngandoung Festus, a se wo bandol. Vati wei a neil on zonghek me qes nimza.  
\v 26 King woulek lul dalus tine, om a teyei bei baluk wou e de a se xaleeng en e. En a woulek bombek bei lulul beimambei ne lam yeip yaingateiv.  
\v 27 King Agripa, wang wongis qayeeng wei xel poropetyeiw o? A woulek woy, bei wang wongis.” 
\p  
\v 28 Woyom Agripa neil wou Paulus, “Wang wou naleim bei inyon eivek seivma sepi kane eno tyek wang bong a bo tambiy wei na mi betiwou Kilisi yo?” 
\p  
\v 29 Paulus neil elox bei, “Seivma sepika o dingta, a mi zeimemang wou Anutu bei se wamaxow qe eti yeiw dalus wei di ngo ay gweimbeeng ne tyek xam xouing ghe ghok ay. Ekom ambei xel se tup xam angya sen me xam a toumendei eivek xeitueing.” 
\p  
\v 30 Woyom king qandi lek, is e xe lei ngandoung wei seyap o me Benaisi me eti yeiw wei toundei is xel o.  
\v 31 Xel la veil xomek lalei tiyon, me luk wouma, xel neil, “Tambiy tine se wong lulti wo nilul bei e mey o mendei eivek xeitueing.” 
\p  
\v 32 Agripa neil wou Festus, “Moux tine teyei bei na nivax, wangwei e maxow se neil wou Sisa bei e ngo e xe qayeeng nei.” 
\c 27  
\s1 Paulus la lek sip me la Rom 
\p  
\v 1 Nambei nyon xel tup qayeeng lekti bei xa na eivek sip me nana Itali. De xel toung Paulus me xel wei xeitueing eno valu eivek tambiy ti e lei Julias eno mema wei toundei nambei beyeiv eivek vevekyeiw qendu ti wei king lei ngandoung wei Rom o.  
\v 2 Xa la eivek sip wei beyeeng nayak Adlamitium. Sip tine tyek na tupwou mamileeng wei beyeeng nayak nayak wei provins Esia yo, om xa la eivek mamileeng me na la. Alistakas wei beyeeng Tesalonika nanghei tembuing danghei wei Masedonia eno la is xa. 
\p  
\v 3 De yanyeing eno xa la tei Saidon, me Julias lalei wo nimza wou Paulus, om wong Paulus la wou e xe xel gweleeng yeiw bei kandek xel bo vineing valu wou e.  
\v 4 Nanghei inyon eno xa la eivek sip no me na ghanaw tembuing nayak Saiprus eivek mamileeng, en laweeng ngandoung vei sip is xa.  
\v 5 Ka xa la eivek sip me na sek mamileeng me na la paviy Silisia me Pampilia eno xa teila nanghei beyeeng Maila eivek Lisia.  
\v 6 Nanghei inyon eno beyeiv wei xel vevek eno yei sip ti lam anghei Aleksandlia en embei na Itali om toung xa lek sip tiyon.  
\v 7 Xa mi la kaka teyei lek bouk valu en laweeng nikanzek vei sip is xa om wong pok wou xa en ingwei xa bei na Nidus o. Laweeng se wong xa la lox xa xe sakwaing, om xa se teyei bei na no, qe xa pekwi me na la tembuing nayak Krit eivek mamileeng paviy Salmone.  
\v 8 Xa wo pok me betiwou mamileeng vi me na la tyip wou beyeeng ti lei Beyeeng Nenyawes Nimza wei toundei paviy beyeeng nayak Lasea. 
\p  
\v 9 Xa la lek mamileeng bouk valu betiy lak veil, me gweimbeeng eno se bouk nimza wei laeing o, en bouk ngandoung wei Yudayeiw o, bouk wei xel mi vambu xow en yaing o, bouk tine la veil. Om Paulus peti xel bei,  
\v 10 “Xa me, a xei bei xe xe laeing eno tyek xey a qou nilul ayang eivek sip me xe xe qoupek valu tyek nati, me xemaxow is ambei nyon.”  
\v 11 Ekom beyeiv wei xel vevek o se ngo vati wei Paulus neil o, qe betiwou tambiy wei mi qou sip o me tambiy wei e xe sip on vyend.  
\v 12 Beyeeng tine se nimza bei sip na bale me ghupek eivek en laweeng ngandoung on, om xel moux ngenong on neil embei xel me di na eivek sip me na, xel embei betiwou mamileeng vi wei tembuing nayak Krit eivek mamileeng me na beyeeng nayak Piniks. Myakenu wei toundei nanghei nyon eno wo mya tambak la veweeng axo, me veweeng aning is. Xel embei mendei nanghei nyon en laweeng ngandoung tine tyip. 
\s1 Laweeng valeivek 
\p  
\v 13 Gyeik laweeng axonei tyip kaka, xel wou kwend en vati wei xel laleind vind o. Om xel puw anka dom xel la paviy mamileeng vi wei Krit o.  
\v 14 Ekom se wo lululek en laweeng ti xel mi taxe bei valeivek eno lam anghei tembuing nayak Krit.  
\v 15 Laweeng ngandoung on vei sip nikanzek om sip se teyei bei na, om xel wong laweeng valeivek on vei sip di la.  
\v 16 Ka xa la daing me na la tembuing nayak on valu pu wei paseisexe laweeng, wei xel taxe bei Kauda. Xa wo pok ngandoung lek puweing bot nayak lam paviy sip.  
\v 17 Woyom xel moux on puw bot leklam lek sip. Dekakom xel tup sel angya yis eivek xeinghembi bei e zeimaxoun e bo nikanzek. Xel yaleeng bei tyek xel na bale lek qakous wei mamileeng masenghoing o paviy Afrika, om xel tup sel angya yis dom wong e teila lek mamileeng dom laweeng di vei sip di la kaka.  
\v 18 Valeivek tyip me mamileeng di nex xa lox me loum, omva yanyeing eno xel wei mi wo xuk eivek sip on qou qoupek on me nex ela eivek mamileeng.  
\v 19 Lek bouk yal, eno xel nex sel me yis me qasok la veil sip angya memend.  
\v 20 Bouk ngenong la veil eno xa se xei seiv o betum ti lam nale en valeivek tine di wo nol wo xa, om xa wou kwami bei tyek xa dalus amey. 
\p  
\v 21 Bouk tambak eno moux beimambei ne se ya bambound ti, om Paulus nale wou xel mend me neil: “Xam moux, wangwei xam a ngo a xe qayeeng ne me xe se na veil Krit, yon tyek xey se teyei bei balwou nimaying tine me lul sapa ne tyek se nati.  
\v 22 Ekom gweimbeeng ne a neil wou xam bei, xam laleimim se bo nimaying en tyek xam ti seng teyei bei mey, qe sip venaxow tyek lelolexe.  
\v 23 En vezeiveeng boukeing eno a tiwei Anutu xe, me a mi wong lalo wou eno wong e xe angela ti lam nale paviy a byek  
\v 24 de neil, ‘Paulus, wa seng gwaleeng. Tyek wang mi bale zam wou Sisa manghalus. En, Anutu ngo wa xe zeimeing mema is me wong mapieing wou xel wei la is wang lek sip o.’  
\v 25 Angela neil wou ay, om xam moux on xam seng gwaleeng qe xam bale nikanzek, en a wongis Anutu bei tyek bong neing a tyip nambei kawei neil wou ay yo.  
\v 26 Nambei nyon mamileeng emdi qalei sip me na deka xey a na pop lek tembuing nayak on ti eivek mamileeng.” 
\s1 Sip wo nilul 
\p  
\v 27 Lek boukeing xoumeeng vey eno laweeng vei xa la lek mamileeng ngandoung wei Mediterenian on me na dula mamileeng wei Adriatik o, de boukeing masenghoing eno xel wei mi yeiteyei sip on axe bei sip embim na paviy mamileeng vi ti.  
\v 28 Xel qou mita me yei mamileeng on teyei lek 120 manghembi. Se denlek en xel lox me la qou mita no me yei bei inyon 90 manghembi.  
\v 29 Xa xaleeng bei tyek sip na tu xow lek qakous, om xel qou anka vey nanghei ingwei sip nelu nei me wong e lepla dom mi zeimemend bei e boyaing daing.  
\v 30 Xel wei mi yeiteyei sip on yimexe sakwaing wei xel embei na veil sip o, om xel tul yis veil bot on teila dom tyoing lek bei xel embei toung anka valu lek sip nelu.  
\v 31 Woyom Paulus neil wou beyeiv me xel vevekyeiw on, “Wangwei xel moux tine se toumendei lek sip, on tyek xam xouing a mey ama.”  
\v 32 Om xel vevekyeiw on qateiv yis wei mi zeimaxoun bot on veil dom e teila me mamileeng qalei me la. 
\p  
\v 33 Paviy e bim boyaing om Paulus wong qayeeng wou xel dalus bei xel gya yaeing. Paulus neil, “Xam laleimim on se dei wo nimza, me xam seng wa lulti wou baboumim. En xam ghe mindei bandaing teyei lek bouk xoumeeng vey ne, dom xam seng wa lulti.  
\v 34 Gweimbeeng a luk nikanzek wou xam bei xam a qou yaeing valu me ghe gwa. En e devind xam ghe bo nimkanzek. Xam lumim velus ti lek xam ti lumim eno se teyei bei puw me nati veil.”  
\v 35 Ka moxo neil tine, moxo qou belet valu me wong dange la wou Anutu eivek xel dalus mendghalus. Woyom moxo dembu dom ya.  
\v 36 Xel dalus on laleind wo nimza no me xel venaxow ya xend yaeing valu.  
\v 37 Xa dalus tiwei xa toundei lek sip ne eno teyei lek 276.  
\v 38 Ka xel ya enden xel, woyom xel nex qoupek wit on la eivek mamileeng bei sip se bo nimaying. 
\p  
\v 39 De woyaing, xel se woulek tembuing, qe xel yei luzeeng wei mamileeng vi yo ti, inyon xel embei bong sip na bale ghei tiyon wangwei xel teyei nei.  
\v 40 Xel qateiv yis wei anka dalus on teila eivek mamileeng. Me xel tul yis wei xel tup lek qasok wei xel mi ngangi sip angya yo. Woyom xel puw sel lek la bei laweeng e davei dom sip ena lek luzeeng.  
\v 41 Ekom sip la pop lek luzeeng wei mamileeng on ti. Sip nelu yon viing lek inyon om se la, me mamileeng la di leislek sip on demi me wo dembu dembu. 
\p  
\v 42 Xel vevekyeiw tup qayeeng lekti bei nyeis xel xeitueing on dalus amey, enok xel deivek mamileeng me na yasewis dom na pek me na.  
\v 43 Ekom beyeiv wei 100 vevekyeiw embei devind Paulus en e toumendei mapieing, om nale zeyi xel xe woueing nalei yon. Moxo neil wou eti yeiw wei mi yeiplek mamileeng bei xel deivek mamileeng me na yasewis.  
\v 44 De xel valu na zeim lek pelang wei sip myasepu sepu wei dembu yon me gyeip lek me na. Eivek sakwaing wei xa xeip lek pelang eno xa dalus a la nimza lek tembuing. De xa ti se mey. 
\c 28  
\s1 Paulus la dei lek tembuing nayak Malta 
\p  
\v 1 Xa lam ewo nimza lek mamileeng nenyawes, de xa woulek bei tembuing nayak ne xel mi taxe bei Malta.  
\v 2 Xel wei tembuing nayak on talex xel xe laleind vineing wou xa. Om xel vev nenyex wou xa de qou xa dalus me na la bei xa na mendei wou nenyex en nambei inye luing om wo nityuweing.  
\v 3 Paulus qeku nenyex qendu ti, me li lek nenyex on mapu, nenyex laxwou myeiy nilul ti om lam qateiv newou lek e mema me milek.  
\v 4 Xel xomaxoneing wei beyeeng on yei myeiy milek Paulus mema, om xel neil wouma bei, “Tambiy tine beind inye moux wei mi leis xel o ti, om moxo pek me lam veil mamileeng, om anutu wei mi wong myaveweeng lox eno embei e se mendei mapieing.”  
\v 5 Ekom Paulus bimexe mema is myeiy teila eivek nenyex, de moxo se axe myavanei ti.  
\v 6 Xel xomaxoneing on di axe bei tyek e mema buklek o detei lutika me na mey, ekom xel axe enden de xel se yei lulti wo nol wou e, om xel pelipek laleind dom neil embei moxo yon anutu ti. 
\p  
\v 7 Inyon tembuing ti dei yeip paviy beyeeng tiyon, tambiy ti lei Publias xe tembuing on me e yon gyovaxa wei tembuing nayak on. Moxo qou xa me la eivek beeng me mi yeiteyei xa wo nimzayang teyei lek bouk yal.  
\v 8 Moxo ma vanei ti wong om di yeip lek zek, en gying wong me e di beipek gyand. Paulus la lalei en embei na gyei e, loxyus en ingwei e zeimema, moxo li mema lek e me wong e wo nimza.  
\v 9 Ka lul tine belup, xel dalus wei tembuing nayak on, wei vanei wong xel eno lam wou e me moxo wong xel dalus wo nimzalek.  
\v 10 Xel wo xeindlala en xa me wo nimza wou xa is ambei nyon, de gyeik ingwei xa bei na veil xel me nana, eno xel wong lulul wei ma veil xa eno wou xa. 
\s1 Paulus la tyip Rom 
\p  
\v 11 Xa mindei eivek tembuing nayak on teyei lek dentouk qes yal, woyom xa la lek sip wei toungale eivek tembuing nayak on gyeik bouk wei laweeng ngandoung on. Inyon Aleksandlia xe sip. Lek sip nelu xel toung tenu wei anutu Sus neu papyeng o, anutu Kasto me Poluks.  
\v 12 Xa la tyip beyeeng Silakyus, me na dei inyon teyei lek bouk yal.  
\v 13 Me nanghei inyon eno xa qou sip me na la tyip Regiam. De yanyeing eno laweeng wei xonei yo lam tyip, de lek bouk yal eno xa la tyip Puteoli.  
\v 14 Nanghei inyon xa xei limiyeiw valu de xel qou xa me xa la dei sounda qes ti is xel. Dekakom xa la Rom.  
\v 15 Xa limiyeiw nanghei inyon eno ngo bei xa di lam, om xel lam anghei inyon me la Beyeeng Vateivek wei Apias, me Xomek Yal wei Vateivek eno is. Paulus yei xel moux tine, om wong dange wou Anutu, me lalei qou nikanzek.  
\v 16 Ka xa la tyip Rom, seyap lenghek lek Paulus bei e venaxow na mendei eivek xomek ti, me xel vevekyeiw mi yei e teyei. 
\s1 Paulus neil xoulek nanghei Rom 
\p  
\v 17 Ka bouk yal la veil moxo taxe xel gyovaxa dalus wei Yudayeiw wei toundei nanghei Rom. Gyeik xel la qekuma eno Paulus neil wou xel: “Xam lingyeiw, a se wong lulti lek xe xe xel xomaxoneing ne o lek xe bundyeiw xe kwa, qe xel zeimaxoun ay eivek Yerusalem me toung a la eivek Rom memend.  
\v 18 Xel Rom ngo a xe qayeeng ekom xel se yei sewokeing ti eivek ay bei xel nyeis a mey. Om xel embei tul a na bandaing.  
\v 19 Ekom Yudayeiw pesek, Om a ning sakwaing nge ma dom tyek Sisa na ngo a xe qayeeng, inye se nambei ambei bo qayeeng en a maxow xe xel xomaxoneing ne.  
\v 20 En qes tine a teling bei ghei wang me baluk is wang. En nambei a wongis me na mi axe lul tiwei xey Israel dalus na mi toung mendghalus wou yo. Qes tine om xel tup ay angya sen.” 
\p  
\v 21 Xel neil eloum, “Xa se qou qapiya ti wou Yudayeiw en wang, me limyeiw ti se lam anghei inyon me neil qayeeng ti wou xa en wang.  
\v 22 Ekom xa bei ngo qayeeng wou wa venaxow en wa xe woueing nalei, en xa woulek bei xomaxoneing lek tembuing sapa di byex qayeeng lek qendu tine.” 
\p  
\v 23 Xel beyal bouk ti dekalekom xel la dei is Paulus, de xel ngenong lam wou Paulus nanghei beyeeng wei toundei lek o. Satiboukeing me ela soukeing eno moxo neil qayeeng qes me neilteyei wou xel en tete lalei wei Anutu yo me neil nikanzek wou xel en Yesu eivek Petieing wei Mose me xel poropetyeiw o.  
\v 24 Xel valu qou qayeeng wei e neil o, ekom xel valu eno se wongis.  
\v 25 Xel pyalek ama me xel embei na veil Paulus gyeik e neil e xe qayeeng tiwei yus o: “Laweeng Vambuing luk zonghek wou xam bumimyeiw gyeik e neil eivek poropet Yesaya mya yo: 
\q1  
\v 26 “‘Wang na wou xel xomaxoneing tine me na neil wou xel, 
\q1 “Tyek xam a mi ngo qayeeng lumama 
\q2 ekom tyek xam se ngowou qes, 
\q2 tyek xam a mi gwei lumama ekom tyek xam seng gweiwou lulti.” 
\q1  
\v 27 En xel xomaxoneing tine laleind wo nikanzek 
\q2 me xel nenyend wo qatu om xel se ngo wou qayeeng, 
\q2 me xel mend tuzeyi. 
\q1 Enok xel gyei nangya mendghalus, 
\q2 me na ngo eivek nenyend, 
\q2 me boulek eivek laleind 
\q1 de pekwi xow, me a bong xel bo nimzalek.’ \rq Yesaya 6:9-10\rq* 
\p  
\v 28-29 “Nambei nyon ambei xam ghe boulek bei Anutu vind xe veil meyeing eno la wou xel amba is, me tyek xel a ngo!” 
\p  
\v 30 Lek vakovek qes yuw dalus eno Paulus mi dei eivek xomek wei e maxow mi xouv wou xomek ma yo. Me mi wo xeilala bei na qou eti yeiw wei lam en embei nam gyei e yo.  
\v 31 Moxo se mi yaleeng en neileing Anutu xe tete lalei teyei me xelti se mi nale zeyi e, qe mi teyoxe xel en Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu Kilisi.